\id ACT - Mbula NT with Gen, Exo, Ruth, Psa, Pro, and Jonah [mna] -Papua New Guinea 1996 (DBL 2015)
\h Uraata Kizin Ŋgoŋana
\toc1 Uraata Kizin Ŋgoŋana Ki Yesu
\toc2 Uraata Kizin Ŋgoŋana
\toc3 Ŋgo
\mt1 Uraata Kizin Ŋgoŋana Ki Yesu
\c 1
\p 
\v 1-3 O Tiopilus, sua mi uraata mataana kan boozomen ta muŋgu Yesu ikam, ta aŋbeede se ro tio mataana kana. \f + \fr 1:1-3 \ft Ro mataana kana tana, ina uruunu ambaiŋana ta Lukas ibeede.’ Sua mi uraata kini tana imar imar ma Anutu ikami ma isala pa saamba mini. Mi iŋgi be aŋseeŋge sua tio pa sua mi uraata kini pakan. Indeeŋe tau Yesu imeete mi imaŋga mini, mi aigule tomtooru ta iparto i tana na, ni ila iwedet kizin ŋgoŋana kini ta itunu ipeikat zin na. Mi izzwe itunu pizin pa zaala boozo. Pa isombe zin tire kati. Naso tiute kat tau ni imaŋga kek. Mi izzo zin pa peeze ki Anutu, mi ikam ma Bubuŋana Potomŋana iso zin pa uraata pakan tomini. \f*\x + \xo 1:1-3 \xt Lu 1:1+, 9:51, 24:13+; Yo 20:19+; 1Kor 15:5+\x*
\p 
\v 4 Aigule ta na, ni ziŋan timbotmbot mi tikanan kini, mi ni iur sua pizin ma iso: “Kozo kezem Yerusalem loŋa pepe. Kombot mi kazza. Pa koroŋ ta Tamaŋ imbuk sua pa, ta iŋgi be iur ŋonoono i. Ka sua ta nio aŋso ma keleŋ kek.\x + \xo 1:4 \xt Lu 24:49; Yo 14:16+; Ŋgo 2:33\x*
\v 5 Yoan, ni ikam yok men pizin tomtom. Mi niom na, molo som to Anutu ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana ma isalakaala yom.”\x + \xo 1:5 \xt Lu 3:16\x*
\s1 Yesu isala pa saamba
\r (Mk 16:19-20; Lu 24:50-53)
\p 
\v 6 Tana zin wal ta ziŋan Yesu timbotmbot na, tiwi i. Tiso: “Biibi, parei? Iŋgi nol tabe pamender yam Israel mini be amkam peeze pa toono i?”\x + \xo 1:6 \xt Mika 4:8; Lu 24:21\x*
\p 
\v 7 To Yesu ipekel kwon ma iso: “O, uraata tina ka nol, ina imbot la Tamaŋ itunu leleene. Pa ni ta imboro. Mi ina niom koroŋ tiom be kuute na som.\x + \xo 1:7 \xt Mk 13:32+; 1Tes 5:1+\x*
\v 8 Mi keleŋ. Bubuŋana Potomŋana isombe imar ma isalakaala yom, toinabe kakam mburaana, mi kamaŋga mi kosoyaara uruŋ pizin tomtom be kopombol sua tio. Ko kakam isu Yerusalem muŋgu, mana kapa pa Yudea, to kala pa Samaria, mi kala karao lele pakaana ta boozomen.”\x + \xo 1:8 \xt Lu 24:47+; Ŋgo 2:1+\x*
\p 
\v 9 Yesu iposop sua tana, to tizem ruumu mi tisala pa lele mbukuunu Olib. Tirre i, mi miiri tieene izukkaali, mi Anutu ikami ma isala pa saamba.\x + \xo 1:9 \xt Mk 16:19; Lu 24:50+\x*
\v 10 Matan izalla be tirre kinkiini i, mi molo som na, wal ru tipet kizin ma ziŋan timendernder. Mburu kizin kokouŋan men. Timaŋga na tiso:\x + \xo 1:10 \xt Lu 24:4\x*
\v 11 “O niom tomtom ki Galilea, parei ta kemendernder mi motoyom izalla pa saamba? Keleŋ. Yesu ta Anutu ikami ma izem yom mi isala pa saamba a, kaimer ni kola imiili mini ma isu ta kembena.”\x + \xo 1:11 \xt Mt 26:64; 1Tes 4:16; Tur 1:7\x*
\s1 Matias ikel Yudas
\p 
\v 12 To tizem abal Olib, mi timiili mini ma tisala pa Yerusalem. (Lele mbukuunu tana imbot kolouŋana pa Yerusalem. Sombe tasala, na irao aigule potomŋana ka pai.)\x + \xo 1:12 \xt Lu 24:52\x*
\v 13-14 Tipet kar na, tisala ruumu leleene kor kana ta tiluplup zin pa i. Zin ta tiŋgi: Petrus ziru Yoan, mi Yems, Andreas, Pilip, Tomas, Patolomai, Matai, Yems toro ta Alpai lutuunu i, Simon (ni igabgaaba zin wal ta tisombe tikam malmal pa Rom mi tiziiri zin pa Israel na), mi Yudas ta Yems lutuunu na. Ziŋan Maria ta Yesu naana i, mi moori pakan, mi Yesu tiziini bizin tomini. Zin tana koroŋ to tiparluplup zin mi tizuŋzuŋ.
\p 
\v 15 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana na, aigule ta, zin wal ta titoto Yesu i tilup zin. Zin ko kembei tomto lamata tomoota (120). To Petrus imaŋga mi iso ta kembei.
\v 16-19 Iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, kere. Muŋgu, Yesu ipeikat Yudas mi itiŋan tawwa mi takamam uraata ki Merere tiŋgi. Tamen ni isu mi iwe zaala pa Yesu ka koi bizin, ta tikami. To ikam mbulu kini sananŋana tana ka pat, mi isu iŋgiimi toono pakaana pa. To ila itop su toono, mi ipetepaala kopoono ma koponkopon ipet. Mi zin Yerusalem kan ta munŋaana men tileŋ, tabe tipaata toono tana la zitun kalŋan ma tiso Akeldama. (Zaana tana ka uunu ta kembei ‘Toono ki siŋ.’) Mbulu tana ka sua, muŋgu Bubuŋana Potomŋana iswe la ki Dabit.\x + \xo 1:16-19 \xt Mbo 41:9; Mt 27:3+; Yo 6:70+\x*
\v 20 Pa mboe suŋŋana kana ta ki Dabit iso ta kembei:
\q1 Muriini ta ni imbotmbot pa na, ko bilim.
\q1 Tomtom sa ko imbotmbot pa som.\x + \xo 1:20 \xt Mbo 69:25\x*
\m Mi sua lwoono toro iso ta kembei. Iso: “Kozo tomtom toro ikam muriini mi ikeli pa uraata.”\x + \xo 1:20 \xt Mbo 109:8\x* Sua tana iur ŋonoono kek. Pa Merere sua kini ta boozomen bela iur ŋonoono.
\v 21-22 Tana tomtom sa bela imar mi iŋgal yam ma munŋoyam mini. Naso amap ma ampombol sua pa maŋgaŋana ki Yesu. Tana tere tomtom kiti sa tau igabgaaba iti, mi itiŋan Yesu tawwa. Indeeŋe tau uraata ki Yoan pa yok kamŋana, mi imar imar ma aigule ta Anutu ikami ma izem ti, mi isala pa saamba mini.”\x + \xo 1:21-22 \xt Lu 24:48+\x*
\p 
\v 23 Petrus iso sua tana, to tiur wal ru: Yosep Barsabas ta zaana toro Yastus na, mi Matias.
\v 24 Tipamender ziru zan makiŋ to, tisuŋ. Tiso: “O Merere, nu ute leleyam lup kek. Tana wal ru ti, so yam pa tomtom iŋgoi ta itum roogi\x + \xo 1:24 \xt Yo 2:25; Tur 2:23\x*
\v 25 be ikam Yudas muriini, mi iwe ŋgoŋana ku mi ikam uraata pu. Pa Yudas ta ipizil ndemeene pa uraata ku, mi imeete ma ila lene pa muriini tau nu ur pini pataaŋa kek na.”
\v 26 To tikam ma Matias zaana ipet. Tabe Matias ikam Yudas muriini, mi iwe ŋgoŋana ki Yesu, mi iŋgal zin laamuru mi ta ma ila imun mini.
\c 2
\s1 Bubuŋana Potomŋana isu
\p 
\v 1 Indeeŋe aigule ki Pentekos \f + \fr 2:1 \ft Pentekos, ina suŋŋana biibi ta kizin Yuda. Zin tilup zin pa Pasoba, mi aigule tomtooru laamuru ilae, to Pentekos ipet.\f* na, zin urlaŋana kan timap ma tilup zin ma timbotmbot.\x + \xo 2:1 \xt Kam 23:16\x*
\v 2 Mi molo som na, tileŋ koroŋ kembei ta miiri biibi i. Imbul ki saamba, mi isu ma izeebe ruumu leleene ta timbotmbot pa i.\x + \xo 2:2 \xt Ezek 37:9+; Yo 3:8\x*
\v 3 To tire koroŋ kembei ta you miaana ipet, mi imureege ma isala tomtom tataŋa uten ma ikot zin.\x + \xo 2:3 \xt Kam 3:2; Mt 3:11\x*
\v 4 Tana Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe zin wal tana lup, mi iparaurau kwon ma tiso sua ila karkari kalŋan.\x + \xo 2:4 \xt Mk 16:17; Yo 7:37+, 14:16; Ŋgo 4:31, 10:44+, 19:6\x*
\p 
\v 5 Indeeŋe tana, zin Yuda boozo ta timbotmbot leŋaleŋa irao lele pakaana ta boozomen na, zin tila timbotmbot Yerusalem tomini. Zin wal ki titoto mbulu ki Anutu.
\v 6 Timbotmbot mi tileŋ la pa, to timokor la pataaŋa. Mi zin wal ta Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe zin na, sua kizin ikam ma iwal biibi tau ŋgar kizin imap. Pa tileŋleŋ kat la pa zitun kalŋan tau.
\v 7 Tabe kwon itaanda mi tikamam ŋgar boozo. Tiso: “Wai, a niom, wal tiŋgi tikam parei kembei? Zin iŋgi sa Galilea kan men.
\v 8 Mi parei ta iti tomtom tataŋa teleŋleŋ zin tizzo sua lala itundu kalŋanda kat kembei?
\v 9 Iti tamar pa lele pakaana ki Partia, Midia, mi Elam, mi Mesopotamia, Yudea mi Kapadosia, mi Pontus ma Asia,
\v 10-11 mi Pirigia ma Pampilia, mi Aikuptu, mi lele pakaana ki Libia ta kolouŋana pa Kairini na, mi Krit mi Arabia. Mi tomtom kiti pakan timar pa Rom tomini. Mi zin Rom kan na, pakan zin Yuda ŋonoono. Mi pakan na, zin wal ta titooro zin ma tiwe Yuda i. Tamen sua ta wal taiŋgi tikamam pa Anutu uraata kini bibip, ta iti tamap teleŋleŋ la itundu kalŋanda.”
\v 12 Tana zin iwal tana kwon taanda lup. Pa tikankaana pa mbulu tiŋgi. Mi tiparwwi zin ma tiso: “Wai, iŋgi parei?”
\v 13 Mi pakan na, tikam seŋge pizin ma tiso: “Ou, niom iwal, iŋgi sa tiwin na.”
\s1 Mos ta Petrus ikam pizin iwal biibi
\p 
\v 14 Petrus ziŋan zin ŋgoŋana laamuru mi ta timbotmbot, mi imaŋga na iso ma kalŋaana biibi. Iso: “Niom Yuda mi niom wal boozomen ta kombotmbot Yerusalem i, kuŋgun talŋoyom pio, mi nio ko aŋso yom pa mbulu tiŋgi ka uunu.\x + \xo 2:14 \xt Mt 16:19\x*
\v 15 Niom koso zin wal tiŋgi tiwin. Mi iŋgi zoŋ ise zen. Lak, winŋana sa, tiwinin pa mazwaana ta kembei? Som.\x + \xo 2:15 \xt 1Tes 5:7\x*
\v 16 Keleŋ. Mbulu ti ka sua, ta Anutu kwoono Yoel iso ta muŋgu kek. Mi iŋgi buri iur ŋonoono i. Sua ta kembei:
\q1 
\v 17 Anutu iso: Indeeŋe mazwaana kaimer kana ma uraata tio iso ipet kat mat, \f + \fr 2:17 \ft Mazwaana kaimer kana imaŋga pa meeteŋana mi maŋgaŋana ki Yesu. Mi ko ila ila ma toono swoono. Mi ka kilalan biibi na uraata ki Bubuŋana Potomŋana.\f*
\q1 na nio kola aŋkam Bubuŋoŋ ma isalakaala tomtom ta munŋaana men.
\q1 To lutuyom bizin ma lutuyom moori bizin ko tiwe nio kwoŋ mi tiso kalŋoŋ pizin tomtom.
\q1 Mi zin naŋgaŋ kaibiim ko tikeenetondo.
\q1 Mi Anutu ko iswe koroŋ pakan pizin kolman ila miuŋana.\x + \xo 2:17 \xt Yesa 44:3; Ezek 39:29; Yo 7:37+\x*
\q1 
\v 18 Mi zin mbesooŋo mi mbesooŋo moori tio ta kembena.
\q1 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana na, nio ko aŋkam Bubuŋoŋ ma isalakaala zin.\x + \xo 2:18 \xt Ŋgo 21:9\x*
\q1 
\v 19 Mi nio ko aŋkam uraata bibip ma ipet sala maŋaanaŋana,
\q1 mi aŋkam mos mburanŋan isu toono tomini.
\q1 Ko kembei ta siŋ, you, mi you kakoi ta buk ma ise i.
\q1 
\v 20 Pa zoŋ kola iyaara mini som, mi lele zugut. Mi puulu mataana ko isiŋsiŋ.
\q1 Uraata tana kola ipet muŋgu, mana nol biibi ki Merere be iswe mburaana ma ipet kat mat.\x + \xo 2:20 \xt Mt 24:29+, 27:45\x*
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Mi wal boozomen ta so titaŋroro Merere be iuulu zin, na ni ko ikamke zin ma timbot ambai.\x + \xo 2:21 \xt Yoel 2:28+; Ŋgo 4:12; Ro 10:13\x*
\p 
\v 22 “Tana niom tomtom ki Israel, keleŋ sua tiŋgi. Uraata mburanŋan mi mos bibip ta Yesu ki Nasaret ikam la mazwoyom na, niom kuute lup kek. Uraata ta Anutu ipomboli ma ikam, ina iswe i kembei: Ni Anutu iŋgo i.\x + \xo 2:22 \xt Yo 5:36\x*
\v 23 Anutu, ni itunu ŋgar kini mi iur Yesu pataaŋa kek be ima nomoyom. Tanata niomŋan zin Rom kan tau titoto tutu som na, kupuni ma imeete sala ke pambaaraŋana.\x + \xo 2:23 \xt Yesa 53:10; Ŋgo 4:28\x*
\v 24 Tamen meeteŋana irao ikisi na som. Pa Anutu itatke i pa meeteŋana mburaana, mi iwiti ma burup ma imaŋga pa naala.\x + \xo 2:24 \xt Lu 24:5; Ŋgo 3:15\x*
\v 25 Ka sua, Dabit iso ta muŋgu kek. Pa iso:
\q1 Nio aŋre Merere imbotmbot kereŋ uunu totomen.
\q1 Ni imbotmbot raama yo mi ikiskis yo. Tana kosa sa ko irao ikam yo ma aŋtop na som.
\q1 
\v 26 Iŋgi tabe ikam yo ma leleŋ ambai kat,
\q1 mi aŋso sua raama menmeen yo.
\q1 Ŋonoono, nio ko aŋmeete. Pa nio tomtom toono koŋ.
\q1 Tamen kopoŋ rru som. Iŋgi aŋmbotmbot mi aŋurur motoŋ pu men tau.
\q1 
\v 27 Pa nu irao zem yo ma aŋmeete mi aŋsula Andewa be aŋbot na som.
\q1 Nu irao zem mbesooŋo ku potomŋana ma ibuuzu na som.
\q1 
\v 28 Nu patooŋo yo pa zaala ki mbotŋana mata yaryaaraŋana.
\q1 Mi nu ko kam yo ma aŋbot su kerem uunu, mi kam ma leleŋ ndabok men.\x + \xo 2:28 \xt Mbo 16:8+\x*
\b
\p 
\v 29 “O atoŋan mi tiziŋan. Nio leleŋ be aŋso kat yom pa tumbundu Dabit. Ni imeete ma titwi i ta muŋgu kek. Ma naala kini ta imbotmbot men kar ti.\x + \xo 2:29 \xt 1Kin 2:10; Ŋgo 13:35+\x*
\v 30 Tamen Dabit, ni Anutu kwoono. Mi ni iute tau Anutu imbuk sua mbolŋana pini be kaimer to iur popoŋana kini sa ma iwe king kembei ni itunu.\x + \xo 2:30 \xt 2Sam 7:12+; Mbo 89:3+, 132:11\x*
\v 31 Ni ire mbulu tabe ipet pa kaimer i. Tanata iso pa maŋgaŋana ki Mesia, mi iso Anutu ko irao izemi ma imeete mi isula Andewa be imbot na som. Mi irao izemi ma ibuuzu na som.\x + \xo 2:31 \xt Mbo 16:10\x*
\p 
\v 32 “Mi Yesu ta amzzo yom pini i, ta Anutu iwiti ma burup ma imaŋga mini pa naala. Niam ta boozomen ti amre kat pa motoyam, tanata ampombolmbol ka sua.
\v 33 Ni, Anutu ipakuri, mi iuri ma imbot la namaana woono. Mi Tamaana ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana pini kek. Ito itunu sua kini mbukŋana tau. Bubuŋana tana, ta Yesu kadoono ikam ma isalakaala yam, mi iŋgi kere mi keleŋ i.\x + \xo 2:33 \xt Yo 14:26; Pil 2:9\x*
\v 34 Mi Dabit itunu na, isala saamba som. Tamen ni iso ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 Merere iso pa Biibi tio ta kembei:
\q1 Mar mbulem su ta nomoŋ woono i
\q1 
\v 35 ma irao aŋkoto kom koi bizin ma mburan imap kat,
\q1 mi kumbum ise ŋguren.’\x + \xo 2:35 \xt Mbo 110:1\x*
\b
\p 
\v 36 “Tana niom Israel ta munŋaana men, keleŋ kat. Yesu ta kupuni ma imeete sala ke pambaaraŋana, ta Anutu iuri ma iwe Merere mi Mesia.”
\s1 Wal boozomen tiurla
\p 
\v 37 Tomtom tileŋ la pa sua tana ma ambai som. Pa sua iŋgal zin. To tisu na tiso pa Petrus bizin. Tiso: “Wai toyamŋan, kenako amkam parei?”\x + \xo 2:37 \xt Ibr 4:12\x*
\p 
\v 38 Petrus ipekel kwon ma iso: “Kozo kamap kotooro leleyom, mi kakam yok pa Yesu Krisi zaana. Naso sanaana tiom ila ne, mi ni ipomoozo yom ma ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana piom.\x + \xo 2:38 \xt Mk 16:16; Lu 24:47; Ŋgo 3:19\x*
\v 39 Pa sua mbukŋana ti, iŋgi ima pa niom Israel niomŋan lutuyom bizin, mi zin iwal karkari ta timbot lele molo na tomini. Pa wal boozomen ta sombe Merere Anutu kiti iboobo zin na, sua mbukŋana tiŋgi imar pizin.”\x + \xo 2:39 \xt Yesa 57:19; Yo 10:16; Ŋgo 14:27; Ep 2:13+\x*
\p 
\v 40 Petrus iso sua tiŋgi men som. Kwoono imbol pizin pa sua boozomen. Pa isombe ikam zin ma tiurla ki Krisi. Tana iso pizin ma iso: “Motoyom iŋgal mi kuru zaala pa ituyom be kombot ambai. Pa iŋgi kombot la wal sananŋan lelen. Kokena niomŋan kala leyom.”\x + \xo 2:40 \xt Ga 1:4; Pil 2:15\x*
\v 41 Aigule tana na, zin tau tiurla Petrus kalŋaana, mi tikam yok mi tila tigaaba zin wal urlaŋana kan na, zin ko kembei munŋaana tel (3,000) ma iŋgi.
\v 42 Mi zin tiurur kat lelen pa sua kizin ŋgoŋana ki Yesu, mi tiluplup zin pa suŋŋana mi kini kanŋana.
\s1 Mbulu kizin wal mataana kan ki Krisi
\p 
\v 43 Zin ŋgoŋana ki Yesu tikamam uraata bibip mi titortooro mos boozo. Tabe tomtom ta boozomen tire mi timoto kan. Pa tire kat Anutu mburaana tau.\x + \xo 2:43 \xt Ŋgo 5:12; 2Kor 12:12\x*
\v 44 Mi zin urlaŋana kan tiluplup zin, mi tiparkamam zin ma ambai. Tomtom sa irao kwoono imbol pa koroŋ kini sa be iwe itutamen lene i na som. Koroŋ kizin ta munŋaana men, ta tiparrai pizin men.\x + \xo 2:44 \xt Lu 12:33, 18:22; Ŋgo 4:32+\x*
\v 45 Pa tikamam mburooŋo pa koroŋ kizin, mi tiparrai pizin pakan ta len som i. Tabe zin ta boozomen len koroŋ irao.\x + \xo 2:45 \xt 2Kor 8:13\x*
\v 46-47 Mi aigule ta boozomen tilala ma tiluplup zin su Urum Merere kwoono. Mi tiparluplup zin la ruumu kizin kizin pa suŋŋana mi kini kanŋana. Mi tikanan kini raama lelen ambai men, mi tiwidit Anutu zaana. Paso, tiur kat lelen pini. Tana tomtom timap ma lelen pizin. Mi zin wal ta Merere ikamam uraata pizin be ikamke zin na, ni ipaŋgutŋguutu zin ikot aigule ta boozomen, ma tilala tigabgaaba zin wal urlaŋana kan.
\c 3
\s1 Petrus iurpe tomtom kumbu kaamaŋana ta
\p 
\v 1 Aigule ta, zoŋ mataana ikam tel na, Petrus ziru Yoan tisala pa Urum Merere. Pa suŋŋana rou kana be imaŋga.
\v 2 Ziru tiwwa ma tisala na, tomtom kaamaŋana ta, tikami ma tiuri su urum kwoono ta tipaata be Kataama Kwoono ta Ambaiŋana Kat na. Tomtom tana, naana ipeebi na, ni ta kembeaŋana. Tana aigule ta boozomen tiziŋziŋi ma timar, mi tiuri mi imbotmbot. Beso tomtom timar be tiloondo pa urum na, izarra namaana pizin pa le koroŋ.
\v 3 Ikamam ta kembea, mi ire Petrus ziru Yoan tila mabe tilela. To isuŋ ziru pa le pat.
\v 4 Ziru tigeede su pini, mi Petrus iso: “Motom mar!”
\v 5 Tana tomtom imbot mi iur mataana pizin. Pa indemeere iso ko tikam le koroŋ sa.
\p 
\v 6 Tamen Petrus iso pini. Iso: “A barau, pat silba mi gol na, leŋ sa som. Mi koroŋ ta, ta imbotmbot i. Iŋgi be aŋkam pu. Nio aŋso pu pa Yesu Krisi ki Nasaret zaana: Maŋga mi pa!”\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Ŋgo 14:10\x*
\p 
\v 7-8 To iteege su pa namaana woono mi iwiti. Beso burup na imaŋgaŋga to, siŋ iloondo pa kumbuunu uranuran, mi iyamaana kembei kuliini ikam pirik. Ipa ma ila ri, to ilulu i raama menmeeni biibi, mi ipakurkur Anutu zaana, mi ziŋan tilela pa urum.\x + \xo 3:7-8 \xt Ŋgo 5:15+, 9:34+, 14:8+; Yems 5:14+\x*
\v 9 Wal matan la na, tire ni iwwa mi ipakurkur Anutu ma ikamam.
\v 10 Mi tikilaali kembei ni ta muŋgu imbotmbot Kataama Kwoono ta Ambaiŋana Kat, mi izarra namaana pa le pat. Tabe timurur pa mbulu ta ipet pini na, mi kwon itaanda. Tikam ŋgar pini ma tirao som.
\s1 Mos ta Petrus ikam su Urum Merere kwoono
\p 
\v 11 Tomtom tana isou kiskis Petrus ziru Yoan ma ziŋan timbotmbot, mi iwal biibi tilonloondo ma tila kizin ta Pooto ki Salumo a. Pa timurur pa mos ta ipet na.
\v 12 Petrus ire zin, to iso pizin. Iso: “O niom Israel, parei ta kumurur pa uraata tiŋgi mi kegeede yam? Tomtom ti, niam amkami ma ipa pa ituyam mburoyam, som mbulu tiam sa ta ndabokŋana i na som.
\v 13 Keleŋ kat. Anutu ki tumbundu bizin, Anutu ki Abaraam, Isak mi Yakop, ina ni ikam mbesooŋo kini Yesu ma isala saamba kek be ikam zaana biibi. Mi Yesu tana, ta ikam mbulu tiŋgi. Ni ta kakami ma ila be tipuni na. Pilatus ire i ma iso izemi. Mi niom koso: ‘E-e. Niam leleyam pini som. Puni ma imeete.’\x + \xo 3:13 \xt Kam 3:6; Lu 23:18+\x*
\v 14 Kere. Tomtom potomŋana mi ndeeŋeŋana, ta niom leleyom pini som. Mi tomtom sananŋana ta ipunun zin tomtom, ta koso pizin ma tiputke i mi ima tiom na.\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Lu 23:18+\x*
\v 15 Tana ni ta mbotŋana mata yaryaaraŋana katuunu i, ta niom kupuni ma imeete. Tamen ni, Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga mini pa naala. Niam tiŋgi amre kat ki motoyam. Tanata ampombolmbol ka sua i.\x + \xo 3:15 \xt Lu 24:48; Ŋgo 1:8, 2:24,32+\x*
\v 16 Mi kosa sa som. Yesu zaana tau. Waende ti, niom kuute pataŋana kini kek. Mi ni iurla mi ipase pa Yesu zaana, tanata ikami ma niom ta boozomen kere ni niini ndabok.\x + \xo 3:16 \xt Lu 17:19; Ŋgo 4:10\x*
\p 
\v 17 “O atoŋan ma tiziŋan, nio aŋute. Ina niomŋan zin bibip tiom kikilaala Yesu som, tanata kakam mbulu tana pini.\x + \xo 3:17 \xt Lu 23:34; Ŋgo 13:27; 1Kor 2:8; 1Tim 1:13\x*
\v 18 Mi ina zaala ki Anutu tau. Ni itunu ipazal, bekena sua kini boozomen ta muŋgu iso la ki kwoono bizin na iur ŋonoono. Sua tana iso ta kembei: Mesia kini ko ire yoyouŋana biibi.\x + \xo 3:18 \xt Mbo 22; Yesa 53:5+; Lu 24:26,44; Ŋgo 2:23; 1Pe 1:10+\x*
\v 19 Tana niom kere be kipizil ndemeyom pa mbulu tiom sananŋana, mi kotooro yom, mi kimiili ma kala ki Anutu. Naso ni imus sanaana tiom mi ila ne. Mi niom so kakam ta kembei, inako Merere ipayaryaara yom,\x + \xo 3:19 \xt Ŋgo 2:38\x*
\v 20 mi iŋgo Mesia ta ni itunu iuri piom na ma imiili mini.\x + \xo 3:20 \xt Ŋgo 1:11; 1Tes 4:16\x*
\v 21 Pa ni bela imbotmbot men ta saamba a ma irao mazwaana tabe Anutu iurpe koroŋ ta boozomen ma ambai mini. Ito sua kini mbukŋana ta iso la ki kwoono bizin ta muŋgu kek na.\x + \xo 3:21 \xt Mt 19:28; Ro 8:19+; 2Pe 3:13\x*
\v 22 Pa Mose iso ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 Merere Anutu tiom ko ipamender tomtom tiom sa ma iwe kwoono kembei ta nio i. Mi niom kozo keleŋ la kalŋaana pa koroŋ ta munŋaana men.
\v 23 Mi sombe tomtom sa ileŋi som, nako Anutu ipambiriizi i ma ila lene kat. Kokena igaaba wal kini.\x + \xo 3:23 \xt Lo 18:15+; Ŋgo 7:37\x*
\b
\p 
\v 24 “Tana kere. Pa muŋgu ta Anutu kwoono Samuel mi imar na, Anutu kwoono bizin tiso sua pa mazwaana ta tiŋgi.\x + \xo 3:24 \xt Lu 24:27\x*
\v 25 Iŋgi matamur ki Anutu kwoono bizin, ta imar kiti tomtom ta popoŋana kizin i. Pa sua mbukŋana kini ta ni ikam la ki tumbundu bizin, ta iŋgi iur ŋonoono piti i. Motoyom iŋgal sua ta muŋgu iso pa Abaraam na. Isombe
\q1 Popoŋana ku ko iwe zaala be kampeŋana biibi ise kizin wal boozomen ta timbotmbot su toono na.\x + \xo 3:25 \xt Un 12:3, 18:18, 22:18; Ga 3:8\x*
\b
\p 
\v 26 “Tana kere. Anutu ipei mbesooŋo kini Yesu ma burup ma imaŋga mini pa naala kek. Mi ni isombe ipumuuŋgu kampeŋana kini piom. Tanata iŋgi ikam Yesu uruunu ma imar piom muŋgu, bekena ikam yom ma kipizil ndemeyom pa mbulu tiom sananŋana.\x + \xo 3:26 \xt Ŋgo 13:46, 22:21; Ro 1:16\x*
\c 4
\s1 Tipamender Petrus ziru Yoan
\p 
\v 1 Petrus ziru Yoan tizzo sua pizin tomtom, mi zin patoronŋana kan pakan ziŋan biibi kizin menderŋan ta timborro Urum Merere i, mi zin sadusi pakan timar.
\v 2 Timar raama keten malmal kat pa Petrus ziru Yoan. Pa ziru tikamam sua pizin tomtom mi tizzo ta kembei: Wal ta so tisekap la ki Yesu, nako timaŋga mini pa naala.\x + \xo 4:2 \xt Mt 22:23; Ŋgo 17:18\x*
\v 3 Mi rorou kek. Tana tila ma tikiskis zin, mi tiur zin lela ruumu sanaana pataaŋa be tinaama sua. Ziru be timbot tana, mi tikeene ma aigule toro.
\v 4 Mi zin tomtom tau tileŋ sua kizin na, boozomen tiurla. Tabe tila tigaaba zin ta muŋguŋan na, to zan isala kat. Zin tomtom tirao kembei munŋaana lamata (5,000).
\p 
\v 5 Aigule toro na, zin peeze kan kizin Yuda, ziŋan zin mboroŋan mi zin ŋgarŋan ki tutu tilup zin su Yerusalem.
\v 6 Mi bibip kizin wal patoronŋana kan ta Anas, Kaipas, Yoan, mi Alisande na, mi wal kizin pakan, ziŋan tau.
\v 7 Timbotmbot, mi tikam Petrus ziru Yoan ma timar na, tipamender ziru ila keren uunu. To tiwi zin ma tiso: “Ai, niomru kakam uraata ti pa asiŋ zaana mi mburaana?”\x + \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 21:23\x*
\p 
\v 8 To Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe Petrus, mi imaŋga to iso pizin. Iso: “Niom peeze koyom mi niom mboroŋan.
\v 9 Parei? Koozi niom kosombe kiwi yam pa mbulu ambaiŋana tau ipet pa tomtom kaamaŋana ti, mi zaala tau ni niini ambai, ta koboobo yam i?
\v 10 Nakena niom ta boozomen keleŋ kat. Mi niom men som. Zin Israel ta munŋaana men. Iŋgi kosa sa som. Mi Yesu Krisi ki Nasaret ta kupuni ma imeete sala ke pambaaraŋana, mi Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga pa naala na. Ina ni zaana mi mburaana, ta ikam ma niom kere tomtom kaamaŋana taiŋgi niini ambai mi imendernder la motoyom i.\x + \xo 4:10 \xt Ŋgo 3:13+\x*
\v 11 Yesu ta muŋgu tibeede ka sua ta kembei:
\q1 Pat ta niom wal tau kowwo ruumu na, motoyom repiili mi kipiri lae lene na, pat tamen tana, ta ko tipamender ruumu sala ma imbol.\x + \xo 4:11 \xt Mbo 118:22; Mt 21:42\x*
\b
\p 
\v 12 “Ni itutamen ta ulaaŋa kiti. Sombe turu ulaaŋa la ki tomtom toro sa, ina tarao tendeeŋe som. Pa tomtom ta tirao toono ti, na sa zaana irao iuulu kat iti ma tombot ndabok na som. Pa Anutu iur ni itutamen.”\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Mt 1:21; Yo 14:6; Ŋgo 10:43; Ro 10:13\x*
\p 
\v 13 Timbotmbot mi tire Petrus ziru Yoan timoto som mi tizzo katkat sua, to timurur pizin. Pa tiute zin tomtom kar kan men. Tila skul biibi som. Tana tikilaala zin kembei ziŋan Yesu tiwwa tau.
\v 14 Mi tire tomtom ta tiurpe i ma niini ambai i, ziŋan timender ma timbotmbot, tabe len sua sa som mi timaane men.
\v 15 To tiser Petrus ziru Yoan pa lupŋana kizin ma tipera mat, mi zin be tiso kan sua.
\v 16 Mi timaŋga na tiparwi zin. Tiso: “Lak, iŋgi kozo ko takam parei pizin? Pa mos biibi ta ziru tikam na, ina ipet kat mat, mi iwal biibi ta timbot Yerusalem i tiute lup kek. Tana iti tosombe takam be tawatkaala, nako takam ma tarao som.\x + \xo 4:16 \xt Yo 11:47\x*
\v 17 Mi bela tupunmeete sua tiŋgi ma imborene kat. Kokena irak ma wal pakan tileŋ mi tiurla. Kozo takam sua pamotoŋana pizin mi tepeteke zin be tiso sua pa tomtom sa pa Yesu zaana mini pepe.”
\p 
\v 18 Tiso makiŋ, to tiboobo Petrus ziru Yoan ma tile mini na, kwon imbol pizin be tikam sua sa pizin tomtom pa Yesu zaana mini pepe.\x + \xo 4:18 \xt Ŋgo 5:28,40\x*
\v 19 Tamen ziru tipekel ma tiso: “Wai, kena niom ituyom kitiiri. Ko parei? Amleŋ la niom kalŋoyom, som Anutu kalŋaana? Mbulu iŋgoi ta indeeŋe pa Anutu mataana?\x + \xo 4:19 \xt Ŋgo 5:29\x*
\v 20 Pa koroŋ biibi ta niam amre mi amleŋ kek. Tana iŋgi irao amaane na som. Ko amzzo men ta kembei.”
\p 
\v 21 Tiso ta kembei, tabe zin bibip tisu ma tise pizin, mi tikam sua pamotoŋana pizin mini. Mana tizem zin ma tila. Tana zin bibip tana tiru zaala be tiseeze matan ma som. Pa iwal timap tire uraata tana ma lelen ambai mi tipakur Anutu pa.
\v 22 Pa tomtom kaamaŋana ta mos tana ipet pini ma niini ndabok na, ndaama kini ilip pa tomtooru kek.
\s1 Suŋŋana kizin wal urlaŋana kan
\p 
\v 23 Petrus ziru Yoan tiyooto na, kaŋkaŋ ma tila ki waen bizin, mi tiso zin pa sua ta zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan mi zin mboroŋan tikam pizin na.
\v 24 To waen bizin tileŋ na, tilup lelen mi tikam suŋŋana ila ki Anutu ta kembei. Tiso: “O Merere, nu ta mburom keskeezeŋom mi koroŋ imap katuunu. Nu ur saamba mi toono, mi tai raama koroŋ boozomen men ta timbot pa.\x + \xo 4:24 \xt Kam 20:11\x*
\v 25 Itum Bubuŋom Potomŋana ta ikam peeze pa tumbuyam Dabit ta mbesooŋo ku na, ma iso ta kembei:
\q1 Parei ta zin karkari keten malmal mi kalŋan izalla?
\q1 Wal matan munŋan timburmbuuru sorok paso?
\q1 
\v 26 Zin king ki toono ziŋan zin peeze kan tilup zin,
\q1 mi tikam kumbun be ziŋan Merere mi Mesia kini tiporou.\x + \xo 4:26 \xt Mbo 2:1+\x*
\m 
\v 27 “Mi iŋgi sua tiŋgi iur ŋonoono kek. Pa nu itum roogo mbesooŋo ku potomŋana Yesu, mi uri ma iwe Mesia. Tamen Erot ziru Pilatus ziŋan zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mi zin Israel, ta tilup zin su kar biibi ti mi tipuni ma imeete.\x + \xo 4:27 \xt Lu 23:7+\x*
\v 28 Mi timaŋga ma tikam mbulu ti na, itoptop la zaala tau nu itum lelem iur pa pataaŋa kek be ipet ta kembena.\x + \xo 4:28 \xt Ŋgo 2:23\x*
\v 29 Merere, sua pamotoŋana ta tikamam piam i, nu leŋ kek. Tana pombol niam mbesooŋo ku be amoto pepe, mibe amender mbolŋana pa sua ku kamŋana.\x + \xo 4:29 \xt Ŋgo 3:13, 13:46; Ep 6:19+; Pil 1:14\x*
\v 30 Swe mburom mi urpe zin meteŋan mi kam mos bibip pakan ma ipet pa mbesooŋo ku potomŋana Yesu zaana.”
\p 
\v 31 Tisuŋ makiŋ, to kembei ta yeŋyeeŋge itok pa lele tau tilup zin pa i, mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe zin ta boozomen. Tana timoto som, mi timender mbolŋana pa Anutu sua kini soyaaraŋana.\x + \xo 4:31 \xt Ŋgo 2:2+\x*
\s1 Zin urlaŋana kan tiparlup lelen
\p 
\v 32 Zin urlaŋana kan ta munŋaana men lelen mi ŋgar kizin iwe tamen. Mi tomtom sa irao kwoono mbol pa koroŋ kini sa be iwe itutamen lene i som. Koroŋ kizin ta munŋaana men, ta tiparrai pizin men.\x + \xo 4:32 \xt Lu 12:33, 14:33; Lu 18:22; Ŋgo 2:44+\x*
\v 33 Mi uraata kizin ŋgoŋana ta tipombolmbol sua pa maŋgaŋana ki Merere Yesu na, mburaana biibi. Mi kampeŋana biibi imbotmbot raama zin urlaŋana kan ta boozomen.
\v 34 Mi tomtom kizin sa imbot ŋoobo som. Pa zin ta len toono mi ruumu na, tiurur ŋgomo pa. Beso tikam ka pat,
\v 35 to tikam ma tiur la kizin ŋgoŋana. Toinabe zin tirai pizin wal tau len koroŋ som mi timbot ŋoobo i.\x + \xo 4:35 \xt 2Kor 8:13+\x*
\p 
\v 36-37 Tikamam ta kembei, tana tomtom ta ki mutu Saiprus, zaana Yosep, ni tomini iur ŋgomo pa toono kini. To tiŋgiimi, mi ikam ka pat ma ila iur la kizin ŋgoŋana. Yosep tana, ni uunu ipet la ki Lebi. Mi zin ŋgoŋana tileele zaana be Panabas. (Pisis Panabas ka uunu ta kembei: ‘Tomtom ki ipombolmbol zin tomtom’.)\x + \xo 4:36-37 \xt Ŋgo 9:27, 11:22,30, 13:2\x*
\c 5
\s1 Mbulu pakaamŋana ki Ananias ziru kusiini Sapira
\p 
\v 1 Tomtom toro, ni zaana Ananias. Mi kusiini zaana Sapira. Ni ziru tomini tiur ŋgomo pa toono kizin pakaana, mi wal tiŋgiimi.
\v 2 Tamen ziru tisu mi tikam pakaamŋana. Pa pat ta tisombe tiur ma iwe Anutu lene na, tiruutu pakaana ma imbot pizin. Mi pakaana men, Ananias ikam ma iur la kizin ŋgoŋana, mi iso: “Is. Iŋgi pat munŋaana ta ti.” \x + \xo 5:2 \xt Yos 7:1-26\x*
\p 
\v 3 Tamen Petrus ileŋ na, iso pini. Iso: “Wai, Ananias. Parei ta nu zem Tomtom Sanaana ma izeebu, mi ruutu pat pakan? Parei? Nu so kam be pakaam Bubuŋana Potomŋana? \x + \xo 5:3 \xt Lo 23:21+; Lu 22:3\x*
\v 4 Indeeŋe ta nu kam ŋgomo pa toono ku tana zen, ina nu koroŋ ku. Mi kaimer ma tomtom tiŋgiimi mi kam ka pat, ina tomini koroŋ ku men. Nu itum ta mboro. Mi sokorei ikamu ta lelem iur pa mbulu ta kembena? Ina nu kam pakaamŋana piam tomtom som. Ina nu kam pa Anutu tau.” \x + \xo 5:4 \xt Mt 23:27+\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ananias ileŋ men sua tiŋgi mi imalaala. Itop su ma kup. Beso tomtom tileŋ uruunu na, motoŋana biibi ikam zin lup.
\v 6 To naŋgaŋ timar ma tizuki pa kawaala, mi tisiŋi ma tila titwi i.
\p 
\v 7 Timbot ma moloŋana ri, mana Ananias kusiini ile. Mi mbulu ta ipet pa Ananias na, ni iute som.
\v 8 Ile na, Petrus imaŋga mi iwi i. Iso: “Ai, nu so lak. Nu niomru kusim Ananias, toono ka ŋgomo munŋaana men ta ti?” Moori ipekel ma iso: “E, ŋgomo ta tina.”
\p 
\v 9 To Petrus iso pini. Iso: “Lak, parei ta niomru kulup leleyom mi koso kotoombo Merere Bubuŋana? Leŋ. Wal ta titwi kusim ta timbotmbot kataama ndemeene i. Mi nu ko tisiŋu ma pera tomini.”
\p 
\v 10 Lak molo? Moori imalaala ma ila ituti su Petrus kumbuunu uunu ma kup. Naŋgaŋ tile ma tire i kup su ma imbotmbot, to tiroŋrooŋgi ma tiyooto, mi tila titwi sula waene zilŋaana uunu.
\v 11 Uraata ti ipet ma lupŋana ki Krisi ziŋan zin wal pakan tileŋ, to motoŋana biibi ikam zin lup.
\s1 Zin ŋgoŋana titooro mos bibip pakan
\p 
\v 12 Yesu ŋgoŋana kini timbotmbot mi titortooro mos mi uraata bibip boozomen pizin tomtom. Mi zin urlaŋana kan na, tiluplup zin se pooto ki Salumo ta imbot Urum Merere zilŋaana na. \x + \xo 5:12 \xt Ŋgo 2:43; 2Kor 12:12\x*
\v 13 Mi tomtom tila ma tigabgaaba zin sorok na som. Pa timoto. Tamen iwal biibi na, matan ise kizin mi tiwidit urun.
\v 14 Tabe moori ma tomooto na, iwal ma iwal kat ta tiurla ki Merere, mi tila tigabgaaba zin ma tiwe boozo.
\v 15 Mi uraata boozomen ta iwedet. Tabe tomtom tikamam zin meteŋan kizin izze ke poŋana ma mi kizin, mi tikamam zin ma tilala zaala. Pa tikam ŋgar ta kembei: Sombe Petrus ipa ma ila igarau zin, mi so kunuunu men isalakaala zin, toinabe mburaana iyooto pini, mi iuulu zin ma nin ndabok. \x + \xo 5:15 \xt Mt 9:21, 14:36; Ŋgo 19:12\x*
\v 16 Mi kar ta timbot kolouŋana pa Yerusalem na, ta kembena. Tikamam zin meteŋan kizin ma wal kizin pakan ta bubuŋana sananŋan tipasansaana zin na, mi tilala Yerusalem. To timokor men la kizin ŋgoŋana, mi zin tiurpe zin ma nin ambai lup. \x + \xo 5:16 \xt Mt 8:16\x*
\s1 Zin bibip kizin Yuda tiseeze zin ŋgoŋana matan
\p 
\v 17 Zin ŋgoŋana tikamam ta kembena, tabe biibi kizin wal patoronŋana kan, ziŋan gaabaŋana kini boozomen ta zin sadusi na, ŋgar sananŋana izeebe zin ma matan mburmbur mi keten malmal kat pizin ŋgoŋana. Paso, tire uraata kizin ilonloondo raama mburaana.
\v 18 Tabe timaŋga, to karau lae pizin, mi tizeebe zin lela ruumu sanaana. \x + \xo 5:18 \xt Ŋgo 4:3\x*
\p 
\v 19 Mi mbeŋ na, aŋela ki Merere ta ila, to isol ruumu sanaana ka kataama pizin, mi ikam zin ma tiyooto ma tipera mat. \x + \xo 5:19 \xt Mbo 34:7, 146:7; Ŋgo 12:7+, 16:26\x*
\v 20 To iso pizin. Iso: “Kala ta Urum Merere kwoono, mi koso kat zin tomtom pa mbotŋana popoŋana ti ka zaala.”
\p 
\v 21 Tana berek su na, tiloondo pa Urum Merere, mi timaŋga ma tikam sua pizin tomtom. Tito sua ta tileŋ kek na. Tikamam mi, biibi kizin patoronŋana kan ziŋan zin gaabaŋana kini, tiboobo zin peeze kan kizin Israel ziŋan zin mboroŋan ta boozomen ma timar be tilup zin. Tilup zin ma timbotmbot, mi tiŋgo menderŋan pakan ma tila ruumu sanaana be tikam zin ŋgoŋana.
\v 22 Beso tiwwa ma tilela ruumu sanaana na, matan ru zin ma som. Tana timiili ma tila lupŋana, to tisotaara zin.
\v 23 Tiso: “Wai, niam amla ruumu sanaana na, ka kataama kotkaalaŋana, mi zin ta timborro kataamaŋan i, timendernder. Tamen amkaaga kataama ma amlela na som. Tomtom som.”
\v 24 Biibi kizin menderŋan ta timborro Urum Merere i ziŋan bibip kizin patoronŋana kan tileŋ sua sotaaraŋana tiŋgi na, tikam ŋgar boozo. Tiso: “Wai, iŋgi kozo ko parei?”
\p 
\v 25 Be molo som na, tomtom ta imar mi isotaara zin. Iso: “A, niom na kombotmbot? Mi zin wal ta kezeebe zin lela ruumu sanaana, ta tikamam sua pizin tomtom ta Urum Merere kwoono a.”
\v 26 Biibi kizin menderŋan ileŋ sua tana na, imaŋga mi iyo zin tomtom kini, to pai. Kaŋkaŋ pataaŋa ma tila be tikam zin. Tamen ruŋgun kembei malmal mi tila tikam zin som. Pa timoto kan. Kokena zin iwal biibi timaŋga pizin, mi tipun zin pa pat.
\p 
\v 27-28 Tila tikam zin ŋgoŋana makiŋ, to timiili ma tila mi tipamender zin la zin bibip matan. Mi biibi kizin patoronŋana kan iyaamba zin. Iso: “Kapaata to tana zaana ndabok! Niom talŋoyom som? Niam kwoyam imbol piom kek. Irao koso zin tomtom pa tomtom tana pepe. Mi iŋgi kosoyaara uruunu ma irao Yerusalem kek. Parei? Niom koso kakam be kuur siŋ kini ka kadoono ise tiam?” \x + \xo 5:27-28 \xt Mt 23:35, 27:25; Ŋgo 4:18\x*
\p 
\v 29 Petrus ziŋan ŋgoŋana pakan tipekel kwon ma tiso: “Niam ti amrao amto sorok sua ki tomtom sa na som. Bela indeeŋe Anutu ŋgar kini to amto. \x + \xo 5:29 \xt Ŋgo 4:19; Ga 1:10; 1Tes 2:4\x*
\v 30 Keleŋ. Yesu ta niom kupuni ma imeete sala ke pambaaraŋana, ta Anutu ki tumbundu bizin ipei i ma imaŋga mini kek. \x + \xo 5:30 \xt Ga 3:13\x*
\v 31 Mi ipakuri mi iuri la itunu namaana woono, mi iwe koroŋ imap katuunu kek. Mi ni ulaaŋa kiti. Tana ni ta ko itooro iti Israel, mi ireege sanaana kiti ma ila ne. \x + \xo 5:31 \xt Mk 16:19; Lu 24:47+; Ŋgo 2:38, 3:19\x*
\v 32 Mi niam tiŋgi amre kat uraata kini, tanata ampombolmbol koroŋ tiŋgi ka sua. Mi niam men som. Bubuŋana Potomŋana tomini ipombolmbol sua ti. Ni, Anutu ikami pizin tomtom ta boozomen ta titoto sua kini na.” \x + \xo 5:32 \xt Lu 24:48; Yo 15:26+\x*
\s1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ki Gamaliel
\p 
\v 33 Zin tileŋ sua tana, to keten ibeleu kat ma tiso tipun zin ŋgoŋana ma timetmeete ma tila len pataaŋa.
\v 34 Tamen tomtom ta ki lupŋana tana, zaana Gamaliel. Ni tomtom zaanaŋana kizin ŋgarŋan ki tutu. Mi zin iwal tau matan izze kini. Imaŋga to iso pa waene bizin. Iso: “Ai, kakam wal tina ma tipera mat muŋgu.”
\v 35 Zin ŋgoŋana tipera, to ni iso pa lupŋana tana. Iso: “Niom Israel, keleŋ. Kumbuulu zin loŋa pepe. Timbot mi iti takam kat ŋgar muŋgu, tona tuur len zaala sa.
\v 36 Motoyom imiili pa Teudas. Ndaama pakan ta ila kek na, ni imar ipet, mi izzo pa itunu be ni tomtom toro. Ma tomtom tau sorok som (400), ta tila tito i. Lak, koozi imbotmbot i? Som. Tipuni ma imeete, to naŋgaŋ kini tikam pirik, mi kosa sa som.
\v 37 Ni imar ila, to kaimer ma mazwaana ta tikam tomtom zan na, Yudas ki Galilea imar ipet, mi ipese zin tomtom ma tito i, mi tila be tiziiri gabman ki Rom. Tamen ni tomini, tipuni ma imeete, mi tomtom kini tisu ma tiwe paŋaeŋae sorok.
\v 38 Tana koozi, nio leleŋ be aŋsope yom ta kembei: Wal tina, kumbuulu zin pepe. Kezem zin ma tila. Pa takankaana pa ŋgar mi uraata kizin. Sombe ki toono, nako tikam ma som. \x + \xo 5:38 \xt Mt 15:13\x*
\v 39 Tamen sombe uraata ti imar pa Anutu, na niom ko karao be kokoto zin na som. Tana kere yom. Kokena niomŋan Anutu koporou.” \x + \xo 5:39 \xt Lu 21:15\x*
\p 
\v 40 Sua ki Gamaliel ikam ma titooro ŋgar kizin. Tana tiboobo zin ŋgoŋana ma tilela mini, to tibalis zin, mi tiŋgalsek pizin be tila mi tiso zin tomtom pa Yesu zaana mini pepe. To tizem zin ma tila.
\v 41 Zin ŋgoŋana tizem lupŋana mi tila na, lelen ambai kat ma menmeen zin biibi. Paso, tire ta kembei: Sombe tomtom tipamiaŋ zin, mi tibaada pataŋana pa Yesu zaana, ina kembei pakurŋana. \x + \xo 5:41 \xt Mt 5:10+; Ŋgo 14:22; Pil 1:29; 1Pe 4:13\x*
\p 
\v 42 Mi uruunu ambaiŋana soyaaraŋana na, tizem risa som. Aigule ta boozomen tikamam sua pizin tomtom su Urum Merere kwoono. Mi tilala ruumu kizin tomtom tomini ma tizzo zin bekena tiute: Yesu, ni Mesia.
\c 6
\s1 Tiur wal lamata mi ru be tiuulu zin ŋgoŋana
\p 
\v 1 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana, zin wal ta titoto Yesu i timasak ma tiwe boozo. To zin Yuda tau tizzo Grik kalŋan i, tisu mi tikam sua boozo pizin wal tau tizzo Iburu kalŋan i. Tiso: Kini raiŋana mi koroŋ reegeŋana ta gorgori tikamam na, tirre zin noroŋa kizin Yuda ta tizzo Grik i som.
\v 2 Tabe zin ŋgoŋana laamuru mi ru tiboobo wal boozomen ta titoto Yesu i ma tilup zin, mi tiso pizin. Tiso: “Niom toŋmatiziŋ tiam, kere. Sombe amzem sua ki Anutu soyaaraŋana, mi amboro kini ma koroŋ raiŋana, ko Anutu leleene ambai? Som.
\v 3 Tana niom kaparre yom, mi kuur leyom tomtom lamata mi ru sa tau urun ambaimbaiŋan, mi len ŋgar ambaiŋana, mi Bubuŋana ikamam peeze pizin. To amur zin ma timender pa uraata taiŋgi. \x + \xo 6:3 \xt 1Tim 3:2+; Tit 1:6+\x*
\v 4 Mi niam ti, nako ambot kat pa suŋŋana mi ambesmbeeze pa Merere pa sua kini soyaaraŋana.” \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Ro 1:9\x*
\p 
\v 5 Wal ta boozomen tileŋ ma titiiri sua ta zin ŋgoŋana tipiri na, mi tiyok pa. To tiur Setepan (ni Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe kati mi urlaŋana kini imbol kat), mi Pilip, Prokorus, Nikeno, Timon, Pamenas mi Nikolas ta ki kar Antiok na. (Nikolas ti, naana ma tamaana Yuda som. Mi ni itoori ma iwe Yuda.)
\v 6 Mi tikam wal lamata mi ru tana ma tila kizin ŋgoŋana, to zin tiur naman sala uten ma tisuŋ pizin bekena tiur zin pa uraata. \f + \fr 6:6 \ft Wal lamata mi ru ta tiur zin pa uraata na, zin ta boozomen tizzo Grik kalŋan. Pa pisis kizin na, kizin Grik.\f* \x + \xo 6:6 \xt Ŋgo 13:3; 1Tim 4:14\x*
\p 
\v 7 Mi mazwaana tana, Anutu sua kini mburaana ma ila pizin tomtom boozomen. Tabe zin wal ta titoto Yesu i tiwe boozo kat su Yerusalem. Mi zin patoronŋana kan ta kembena, tomtom kizin boozo tileŋ la sua mi tiurla. \x + \xo 6:7 \xt Ŋgo 12:24, 19:20\x*
\s1 Titeege Setepan
\p 
\v 8 Setepan, ni tomtom tau Merere mburaana mi kampeŋana kini biibi imbotmbot se kini. Tana itortooro uraata mburanŋan mi mos bibip ma tomtom tire. \x + \xo 6:8 \xt Ŋgo 2:43\x*
\v 9 Tamen zin Yuda pakan ki lupŋana ta, ta timbotmbot. Wal tana, muŋgu tiwe mbesooŋo pizin tomtom pakan. Tamen buri na, tomtom sa imboro zin mini som. Mi timar pa kar Kairini, mi kar Aleksandria, mi lele pakaana ki Silisia, mi lele pakaana ki Asia. Timaŋga mi ziŋan Setepan tiparzooro pa sua.
\v 10 Tamen tirao i som. Pa Bubuŋana Potomŋana ipazalzali pa sua ta ni izzo pa Anutu ŋgar kini. \x + \xo 6:10 \xt Lu 21:15\x*
\v 11 To tiru zaala pini, mi tipese tomtom pakan ma tila mi tiso sorok sua pakaamŋana ta kembei. Tiso: “Niam ti amleŋ Setepan ipiri sua repiiliŋana pa Mose, mi Anutu tomini.” \x + \xo 6:11 \xt Mt 26:59+\x*
\p 
\v 12 Tikam sua ta kembei, tabe tikuru zin ŋgarŋan ki tutu mi zin mboroŋan ziŋan iwal biibi lelen ma timaŋga mi titeege Setepan. To tila mi tipamenderi la lupŋana biibi kizin wal peeze kan matan.
\v 13 Mi tisokere zin tomtom ma timaŋga mi tipombol sua pakaamŋana pa Setepan. Tiso: “To ti, gorgori iwirri sua sananŋana pa Urum Merere potomŋana tiŋgi mi tutu ki Mose. Izemzem som.
\v 14 Pa niam amleŋi isombe Yesu ki Nasaret, kola ireege urum ti ma isu lene, mi itooro mbulu mi tutu ta Mose ikam piti na tomini.” \x + \xo 6:14 \xt Mt 5:17; Mk 14:57+; Yo 2:20+; Ŋgo 7:49\x*
\p 
\v 15 Beso zin peeze kan tau timbutul pa lupŋana tana tileŋ ta kembei na, timap ma tikor matan pa Setepan. Mi tire ruŋguunu na, kembei ta aŋela i.
\c 7
\s1 Sua ki Setepan
\p 
\v 1 To biibi kizin patoronŋana kan iwi Setepan ma iso: “Lak, sua ta tiso na, ŋonoono?”
\s1 Anutu ipet ki Abaraam isu lele pakaana ki Mesopotamia
\p 
\v 2 Mi Setepan ipekel kwoono ma iso: \f + \fr 7:2 \ft Sua ki Setepan na, ka uunu ru. Ta na, Zin Yuda tikam ŋgar biibi kat pa toono kizin mi urum kizin ta imbot Yerusalem. Tamen Anutu imbot lele tana men som. Lele swoi ta wal kini timbot pa na, na ni imbotmbot raama zin. Mi uunu toro na, ta muŋgu mi imar, zin Yuda timbel Anutu kwoono bizin zooroŋana.\f* “O atoŋan mi tamaŋan, kuŋgun talŋoyom mi keleŋ sua tio ti. Muŋgu kat, indeeŋe tamanda Abaraam ila itu su kar Aran zen, mi imbotmbot men ta Mesopotamia na, Anutu ta azuŋka katuunu na ila ipet kini,\x + \xo 7:2 \xt Un 11:31\x*
\v 3 mi iso pini ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 Zem toono ku ramaki wal ku, mi maŋga ma la pa toono tabe aŋso u pa i.\x + \xo 7:3 \xt Un 12:1\x*
\b
\p 
\v 4 “Tana Abaraam izem lele pakaana ki Mesopotamia ta toono kizin Kaldia na, mi ila itu su kar Aran. Tamaana imeete mi kaimer mana, Anutu iso pini mini, to isiri i ma imar lele ta buri tombotmbot pa i.\x + \xo 7:4 \xt Un 12:4+\x*
\v 5 Mi Abaraam, Anutu ikam toono pakaana risa ma iwe lene kat i na som. Tamen imbuk sua pini be ikam toono tiŋgi pini mi popoŋana kini tabe tipet pa kaimer i. Ŋonoono, mazwaana tana, Abaraam ipeebe pikin sa zen. Tamen Anutu ikam sua mbukŋana tana pini.\x + \xo 7:5 \xt Un 12:7, 17:8; Ibr 11:13\x*
\v 6 Mi Anutu isope i tomini ta kembei:
\q1 Kaimer popoŋana ku ko tiwe leembe pa lele toro. Mi lele tana ka tomtom bizin ko tikam zin ma tiwe len mbesooŋo, mi tiseseeze matan ma irao ndaama 400.\x + \xo 7:6 \xt Un 15:13+; Kam 12:40\x*
\m 
\v 7 Tamen kaimer to nio kola aŋur kadoono pa toono tana ka tomtom bizin mi aŋpokot mbulu kizin, mi aŋkam zin popoŋana ku ma tizem lele tana, mi timiili ma timar mini be tisuŋ pio isu toono ti.\x + \xo 7:7 \xt Kam 3:12\x*
\p 
\v 8 “Mi Anutu iur reeteŋana ma iwe kilalan pa sua ta imbuk la ki Abaraam na. Tana Abaraam ipeebe Isak mi imbot pa kozolwoono lamata mi tel, to ireeti. To Isak ipeebe Yakop mi ireeti. Mi Yakop ta kembena. Ipeebe lutuunu bizin laamuru mi ru na, ireete zin tomini. Mi zin tina ta tiwe undu bizin.\x + \xo 7:8 \xt Un 17:10+, 35:18\x*
\s1 Anutu imbotmbot raama Yosep isu Aikuptu
\p 
\v 9 “Yakop lutuunu bizin tana timbot ma matan mburmbur pa Yosep, to toŋgomooni ma ila Aikuptu mi iwe mbesooŋo su tana. Tamen Anutu imbotmbot raami,\x + \xo 7:9 \xt Un 39:2,21+\x*
\v 10 mi itatke i pa pataŋana kini ta munŋaana men. Mi ikam ŋgar ambaiŋana pini. Tabe king kizin Aikuptu leleene pini, to iuri ma ikam peeze pa ruumu kini ramaki koroŋ kini ta boozomen mi toono biibi ta Aikuptu a tomini.\x + \xo 7:10 \xt Un 41:37+\x*
\p 
\v 11 “To peteele biibi ipun zin Aikuptu ta boozomen ziŋan zin Kanaan ma timbot ŋoobo kat. Ikam ma tumbundu bizin tiru kan kini ma maŋaanakaala zin.\x + \xo 7:11 \xt Un 41:54, 42:1+\x*
\v 12-13 Yakopbi imbotmbot mi ileŋ kembei kini wit imbot ta Aikuptu a, to isu na iŋgo lutuunu bizin ma tisula Aikuptu be tiŋgiimi kan kini. Tikam kini makiŋ to, timiili ma tila ki taman mini. Ina pai kizin mataana kana. Timbot to tisula mini pa Aikuptu ma iwe ru pa. Indeeŋe tana, Yosep iswe itunu pizin. Tabe king kizin Aikuptu, ni tomini iute Yosep wal kini.\x + \xo 7:12-13 \xt Un 42:1+, 45:1-16\x*
\v 14 Tona Yosep iso la pa tamaana mi toono ma tiziini bizin be tiyauyau mi timar kini. Zin wal ta tisula na, zin tomto tel lamoro mata (75).\x + \xo 7:14 \xt Un 45:9+, 46:26+\x*
\v 15 Tana Yakopbi isula Aikuptu, mi ziŋan lutuunu bizin ta timetmeete su ta tiŋga.\x + \xo 7:15 \xt Un 46:1+, 49:33\x*
\v 16 Mi titwi zin isu Aikuptu som. Tikam zin, mi timiili ma tila pa kar Sekem, mi titwi zin sula naala ta Abaraam iŋgiimi la ki Amor lutuunu bizin na.\x + \xo 7:16 \xt Un 23:3+, 33:18+, 50:7+\x*
\s1 Mose
\p 
\v 17 “Tumbundu bizin ta timbot Aikuptu na, timasak ma tiwe boozo kat to, sua mbukŋana ta Anutu ikam la ki Abaraam na, ka nol igarau be Anutu ikam ma iur ŋonoono.\x + \xo 7:17 \xt Kam 1:7\x*
\v 18 To king toro imaŋga ma ikam peeze pa Aikuptu. Mi ni ikam ŋgar pa Yosep som.
\v 19 King tina imaŋga ma ikam pakaamŋana pa tumbundu bizin, mi iseeze kat matan. Mi iur sua mbolŋana pizin be tikam lutun bizin popoŋan ta buri tipeebe zin i, mi tizem zin ma timboren bekena timetmeete ma tila len.\x + \xo 7:19 \xt Kam 1:9+\x*
\p 
\v 20 “Indeeŋe gorgor tana na, Mose tipeebi ma isu. Ni pikin kaibiim, mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kini. Tuyeete bizin tikam peŋ pini ma irao puulu tel,\x + \xo 7:20 \xt Kam 2:2; Ibr 11:23\x*
\v 21 to tizemi su yok kezeene, mi king lutuunu moori kadoono ikami ma iwe lene, mi ila imborro i.\x + \xo 7:21 \xt Kam 2:3+\x*
\v 22 Mose itum ma iwe tomtom, mi ikam ŋgar kizin Aikuptu ma imap. Mi ni tomtom mburaanaŋana, mi sua kini tomini mburaanaŋana.
\p 
\v 23 “Imbotmbot ma ndaama kini tomtooru, to ikam ŋgar be ila ilou zin wal kini Israel.\x + \xo 7:23 \xt Kam 2:11+; Ibr 11:24+\x*
\v 24 Ila to ire tomtom ta ki Aikuptu ipunun sorok tomtom ta ki Israel. Tana iloondo ma ila na ilae ki Israel tana, mi ipun Aikuptu tana ma kup bekena ipokot mbulu kini.
\v 25 Mi iso ko wal kini tikilaala kembei ni, Anutu ipeikati be ikamke zin pa pataŋana kizin. Tamen som.
\p 
\v 26 Aigule toro na, Israel ru tiporrou. Mi Mose ila ma ire zin, to itoombo be ipeteke zin mibe ilup lelen. Tana iso pizin ma isombe: ‘Wai, niomru na sa toŋmatiziŋ na! Kaparpun yom ma kembena paso?’\x + \xo 7:26 \xt Kam 2:13+\x*
\v 27 Tamen ni ta namaana imuuŋgu pa malmal na, imaŋga to ipusuk Mose ma ilae zilŋaana mi iso: ‘Nu tina, asiŋ iuru be we biibi piam mi urpe pataŋana tiam?
\v 28 Parei? Nu so pun yo kembei ta neeri kam pa Aikuptu tana na?’
\v 29 Mose ileŋ sua tana, to imaŋga na iko ma ila lele molo ta kizin Midian. Ila iwe leembe isu tana, mi imbot ma iwoolo, mi ipeebe pikin tomooto ru.\x + \xo 7:29 \xt Kam 2:15+\x*
\p 
\v 30 “Ndaama tomtooru tomen imap ma ila, mi kaimer to aŋela ta ila ipet kini su lele bilimŋana ta imbot igarau abal Sinai na. Imar kembei you miaana ta ibilbil lela ke matanmatanŋana leleene.\x + \xo 7:30 \xt Kam 3:1+\x*
\v 31 Mose mata kunduunu ikam you, mi imurur. To iso ipa ma ila kolouŋana be ire kat. Som, mi ileŋ Merere kalŋaana.
\v 32 Isombe:
\q1 Iŋgi nio Anutu ki tumbum bizin tau. Nio Anutu ki Abaraam, Isak, mi Yakop.\x + \xo 7:32 \xt Kam 3:6\x*
\m Mose ileŋ to motoŋana biibi ikami, mi iturke mataana.
\p 
\v 33 Mi Merere iso pini mini. Iso: “Kinke kumbum keteene. Pa toono ta nu mendernder pa i, ina potomŋana.
\v 34 Leŋ. Nio aŋre zin Aikuptu kan tiseeze zin wal tio Israel matan ma timbot ŋoobo kat. Tiŋiizi kizin aŋleŋ kek. Mi pataŋana kizin, nio aŋute ma imap. Tanata iŋgi aŋsu be aŋtatke zin la zin Aikuptu naman. Mi nu mar. Pa nio aŋsombe aŋgo u be miili ma la pa Aikuptu.”\x + \xo 7:34 \xt Kam 3:5+\x*
\s1 Zooroŋana kizin Israel buriŋana som. Ta muŋgu mi imar
\p 
\v 35 “Ina Mose tina, ta muŋgu lelen pini som mi tisombe: ‘Nu tina, asiŋ iuru be we biibi piam mi urpe pataŋana tiam?’ Mi tomtom tamen ta tina, ta Merere itunu iŋgo aŋela ma ila ipet kini su lele bilimŋana, mi iuri be ikam peeze pizin Israel, mibe iwe tun.
\v 36 Mi ni tina, ta ikam zin ma tizem Aikuptu, mi itortooro uraata bibip mi mos boozomen isu Aikuptu, mi Tai Siŋsiŋŋana, mi lele bilimŋana ma irao ndaama tomtooru.\x + \xo 7:36 \xt Kam 7:11,14-17; Mbo 105:27\x*
\v 37 Mi ni tina, ta iso pizin Israel ma iso:
\q1 Kaimer, Anutu ko iur tomtom tiom sa be iwe kwoono kembei ta nio i.\x + \xo 7:37 \xt Lo 18:15; Ŋgo 3:22\x*
\b
\p 
\v 38 “Mose ziŋan tumbundu bizin, ta tiwe lupŋana ki Anutu isu lele bilimŋana na. Mi ni ziru aŋela, ta tizzo sua sala abal Sinai na, mi ikam sua mata yaryaaraŋana mi iso zin Israel pa, ta imar imar ma iti takamam i.\x + \xo 7:38 \xt Kam 19:1–20:17\x*
\p 
\v 39 “Tamen tumbundu bizin lelen be tileŋ la Mose kalŋaana som. Titit sua kini, mi lelen be timiili pa Aikuptu.
\v 40 To tisu mi tiso pa Aron. Tiso:
\q1 Urpe lende merere pakan be timuuŋgu piti, mi tiso iti pa zaala. Pa tizim Mose ta ikam ti ma tezem Aikuptu ma tamar taiŋgi na, amkankaana pini. Ko kosa sa ikami ma ila ne kek.\x + \xo 7:40 \xt Kam 32:1+, 32:23\x*
\m 
\v 41 “To timaŋga na tiurpe merere pakaamŋana ma ruŋguunu kembei ta makau lutuunu. Mi tiyyo zin koroŋ ma tikam patoronŋana be tipakur koroŋ tau zitun tiurpe pa naman na, mi menmeen zin pa.\x + \xo 7:41 \xt Mbo 106:19\x*
\v 42 Tana kaimer Anutu ipizil ndemeene pizin, mi izem zin ma timbeeze pa pitik ma puulu ramaki koroŋ boozomen ta timbot saamba na irao zitun lelen ma ŋgar kizin. Ka sua imbot la sua ta muŋgu Merere kwoono bizin tibeede na. Isombe:
\q1 O niom Israel, ndaama tomtooru ta kawwa isu lele bilimŋana mi kakamam zin mbili ma koroŋ pa patoronŋana na, kakam sa pio? Som.\x + \xo 7:42 \xt Mbo 81:12; Yer 19:13\x*
\q1 
\v 43 Pa leleyom imbot molo pio. Tanata kuurpe merere pakaamŋana Molok muriini,
\q1 mi kiziŋziŋ ramaki merere pakaamŋana Repan ta pitik i kunuunu.
\q1 Ina merere tiom tina ta ituyom kuurpe bekena kelek kumbuyom pizin.
\q1 Tana iŋgi ko aŋmaŋga piom, mi aŋziiri yom ma kala kewe paŋaeŋae sorok pa lele molo ta imbot Babilon mbuleene kat.
\s1 Muŋgu zin Israel len urum ŋonoono sa som
\p 
\v 44 “Indeeŋe tau tumbundu bizin tiwwa isu lele bilimŋana na, tiwwa raama beeze potomŋana ta iswe kembei Merere, ni imbotmbot raama zin. Beeze tana, Merere itunu ipatooŋo Mose pa, mi kwoono imbol pini be ito ka mos ta ire sala abal na mi ipo kat.\x + \xo 7:44 \xt Kam 25:9,40, 26:30; Ibr 8:5\x*
\v 45 Tumbundu bizin tiziŋziŋ beeze tana ma tila, to kadoono isu ki lutun bizin. Tila tipet toono Kanaan to, Anutu iziiri ka tomtom bizin ma tila len, mi Yosua ikam zin Israel ma tila tikam len. Mi beeze tana imbot imbot ma indeeŋe gorgor tau king Dabit ikamam peeze pizin Israel na.\x + \xo 7:45 \xt Yos 3:14+, 18:1, 23:9\x*
\v 46 Dabit, Anutu leleene pini. Tana imaŋga to iwi ten Anutu ki Yakop. Beso iyok, to iurpe le muriini sa be imbotmbot pa.\x + \xo 7:46 \xt 2Sam 7:1+; Mbo 132:1+\x*
\v 47 Tamen ni itunu ipo urum sa som. Lutuunu Salumo ta ipo.\x + \xo 7:47 \xt 1Kin 6:1+\x*
\p 
\v 48 “Tamen Anutu kor kana kat, ni imbotmbot lela ruumu tau tomtom tiwwo pa naman i som. Pa Anutu kwoono ta iso ta kembei:\x + \xo 7:48 \xt Ŋgo 17:24\x*
\q1 
\v 49 Merere iso: Saamba, ina nio muriŋ peeze kana.
\q1 Mi toono, ina kumbuŋ muriini.
\q1 Mi ruumu soŋana ta koso kopo pio i?
\q1 Som leŋ lele tau be aŋmbormbooreŋ pa i iŋgoi?\x + \xo 7:49 \xt Yesa 66:1+; Mt 5:34+\x*
\q1 
\v 50 Som. Pa koroŋ ta munŋaana men tiŋgi, nio ituŋ ta aŋur zin.”
\b
\p 
\v 51 To Setepan iso pizin wal ta tipamenderi na ta kembei. Iso: “Niom tina kapa kat ki tumbuyom bizin. Pa niom zorzooroŋoyom, mi ŋgar tiom imbol kat. Reeteŋana ŋonoono ta ki lelende i, na niom kuute risa som. Pa motoyom munŋoyom, mi talŋoyom pampamŋoyom kembei zin wal ta tiute Anutu som i. Gorgori kozorzooro Bubuŋana Potomŋana.\x + \xo 7:51 \xt Kam 32:9; Lo 10:16; Yesa 63:10; Ro 2:28+\x*
\v 52 Kere. Anutu kwoono bizin ta boozomen, tumbuyom bizin tizem tasa? Som. Anutu kwoono bizin ta muŋgu tisoyaara sua pa Tomtom Ndeeŋeŋana tabe imar na, tipun zin ma timap. Beso itunu imar na, ta kembena. Niom kusu kuuri la ka koi bizin naman, mi kupuni ma imeete.\x + \xo 7:52 \xt Mt 23:31+; Lu 13:34; 1Tes 2:15\x*
\v 53 Ŋonoono. Tutu ta aŋela tiwe zaala pa ma isu na, niom kakam kek. Tamen koto som.”\x + \xo 7:53 \xt Kam 20:1; Ŋgo 7:38; Ga 3:19; Ibr 2:2\x*
\s1 Tipun Setepan ma imeete
\p 
\v 54 Tileŋ sua tana, to ipas kat keten mi tikarut zurun pini.
\v 55 Tamen Setepan, ni Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe kati, mi mataana sala saamba to, ire Anutu azuŋka kini biibi, mi ire Yesu imendernder la Tamaana namaana woono.\x + \xo 7:55 \xt Mk 16:19; Lu 22:69\x*
\v 56 To iso: “Kere. Nio aŋre saamba ikaaga, mi Tomtom Lutuunu, ni imendernder la Anutu namaana woono!”\x + \xo 7:56 \xt Mbo 110:1; Ro 8:34; Kol 3:1; Ibr 12:2\x*
\p 
\v 57 Aa, iŋgi tileŋ sua koroŋŋana ri tiŋgi, tabe orooro biibi isala, mi tizeeze talŋan, mi borok ma tila.
\v 58 To tiyaaru tataati ma tila mi tizem kar na, tikor naman pini pa pat. Mi zin wal ta tipombol sua pakaamŋana pa Setepan na, tizun mburu kizin mat kana, mi tila tindou su naŋgaŋ kaibiim ta kumbuunu uunu. Zaana Saul.\x + \xo 7:58 \xt Ŋgo 22:20; Ibr 11:37\x*
\v 59 Pat itoptop zalla Setepan ŋwaana, mi ni isuŋ. Iso: “O Merere Yesu, kam kunuŋ.”\x + \xo 7:59 \xt Mbo 31:5; Lu 23:46\x*
\v 60 To iŋgun kumbuunu, mi kalŋaana biibi ma iso: “O Merere, sanaana tau tikam pio i, na pokot pepe. Reege pizin.” Iso ta kembei, mi itop su ma kup.\x + \xo 7:60 \xt Mt 5:44; Lu 23:34\x*
\c 8
\s1 Saul iseeze zin urlaŋana kan matan
\p 
\v 1 Saul, ni imbot mi ire meeteŋana ki Setepan na, iyok pa men tau.
\p Mi indeeŋe aigule tana na, timaŋga be tikam malmal tau musaana som pa lupŋana ki Krisi ta imbot Yerusalem a. Tiseeze kat matan, tabe tiko papirik lup ma tilala pa Yudea ma Samaria ma. Mi zin ŋgoŋana men ta timbotmbot Yerusalem.\x + \xo 8:1 \xt Ŋgo 1:8, 11:19\x*
\v 2 Mi Setepan na, wal pakan ta titoto Anutu mbulu kini na, titwi i. Mi timbel tiŋiizi pini.
\v 3 Mi Saul, ni imaŋga pa lupŋana ki Krisi, mi isombe ipambiriizi zin ma timap kat. Tana isinin zin ruumu, mi iyaaru tataata zin tomooto ma moori ma ilala iurur zin lela ruumu sanaana.\x + \xo 8:3 \xt 1Kor 15:9; Ga 1:13,23; Pil 3:6; 1Tim 1:13\x*
\s1 Pilip ikam uraata isu Samaria
\p 
\v 4 Zin tau tiko papirikŋan i, na tiwwa mi tizzoyaryaara uruunu ambaiŋana pizin tomtom isu kar ta boozomen ta tila pa i.
\v 5 Tana Pilip ta kembena, ni isula pa kar biibi ki Samaria, mi izzoyaryaara Krisi uruunu isu tana.\x + \xo 8:5 \xt Ŋgo 6:5, 21:8\x*
\v 6 Iwal biibi tileŋ sua ta ni izzo, mi tire mos ta itortooro, to timap tiŋgun talŋan pini.
\v 7 Pa bubuŋana sananŋan tiŋarakrak mi tiyotyooto pizin tomtom boozomen. Mi wal kaamaŋan ma narapeŋan boozomen, ta ni iurpe zin ma nin ambai lup.\x + \xo 8:7 \xt Mk 16:17+\x*
\v 8 Tana zin tomtom ki kar tana menmeen zin biibi kat.
\s1 Simon ta tomtom ki naborou
\p 
\v 9 Kar tana, tomtom ta imbotmbot. Zaana Simon. Mi ni ikamam naborou. Tabe zin Samaria kan tire i ma kwon itaanda pini. Mi ni ipakurkur itunu ma kembei ta ni tomtom biibi sa.\x + \xo 8:9 \xt Ŋgo 13:6+\x*
\v 10 Ikam ma zin tomtom ta boozomen timokorkor la kini. Wal zanŋan mi zin sorrokŋan tomini. Mi tizzo ta kembei. Tiso: “Wai, to ti, ni mburaana kembei Anutu itunu. Ko ikam Anutu ruŋguunu ma iŋgi?”
\v 11 Mi naborou kini ta gorgori ikamam na, tomtom tire ma kwon itaanda pa. Tana tizemzemi som.
\v 12 Tamen Pilip izzoyaryaara sua pa uruunu ambaiŋana, mi Anutu peeze kini, mi Yesu Krisi zaana, to tomtom tiurla mi tikamam yok. Zin tomooto mi moori tomini.\x + \xo 8:12 \xt Ŋgo 2:38\x*
\v 13 Mi Simon tomini, iurla mi ikam yok. Indeeŋe tana mi ila na, izemzem Pilip risa som kat. Itoto i ila kena. Itoto i ila kena. Pa Pilip itortooro uraata bibip ma koroŋ boozo. Tabe Simon irre ma kwoono itaanda.
\p 
\v 14 Beso zin ŋgoŋana ta timbotmbot Yerusalem na, tileŋ kar Samaria uruunu kembei tikan la Anutu sua kini kek, to tiŋgo Petrus ziru Yoan ma tisula be tire zin.
\v 15 Ziru tisula ma tipet, to tisuŋ pa Anutu be ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana pizin wal popoŋan ta tiurla.
\v 16 Pa tomtom kizin sa ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana zen. Tikam yok men pa Merere Yesu zaana bekena tiwe lene.
\v 17 Tana Petrus ziru Yoan tiur naman isalakaala zin, mi tikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana.\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Ŋgo 2:4, 19:1+\x*
\p 
\v 18 Simon ta tomtom ki naborou na, ire zin ŋgoŋana naman izalakalkaala zin tomtom mi tikamam Bubuŋana, to iur sorok pat ila kizin mi iso:
\v 19 “Aiss, nio ti aŋso aŋgiimi mburoyom tina. Beso tomtom sa imar mi nomoŋ isalakaali, tonabe ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana.”
\p 
\v 20 Tabe Petrus imaŋga na iso pini. Iso: “Wai Simon, koroŋ ta Anutu itunu leleene mi ikam piti sorok, ta nu su mini ma sombe ŋgiimi pa pat? Na nu ko la lem raama pat silba ku tana.\x + \xo 8:20 \xt Mt 10:8; Ŋgo 2:38\x*
\v 21 Nu tina, itiŋan temender pa uraata tiŋgi som. Pa lelem mi ŋgar ku indeeŋe pa Anutu mataana som.\x + \xo 8:21 \xt Mbo 78:37; Ep 5:5\x*
\v 22 Tana tooro lelem, zem ŋgar ku sananŋana tina, mi toombo ten ma suŋ pa Merere. Mi re. Ko ireege sanaana ku, o som?
\v 23 Pa nio aŋre u kembei lelem bok pa mbulu ki motom berber, mi sanaana ikis katu kek.”\x + \xo 8:23 \xt 1Tim 6:9; Ibr 12:15\x*
\p 
\v 24 To ŋgar ki Simon ipet, mi isu na iso: “Wai, kena niomru kusuŋ pa Merere pio. Kokena sua tiom tana iur ŋonoono pio.”
\p 
\v 25 Petrus ziru Yoan tipombol sua ki Merere mi tiso zin Samaria kan pa makiŋ, to timiili ma tisala mini Yerusalem. Ziru tiwwa ma tila na, tikamam uruunu ambaiŋana pizin kar pakan ki Samaria ta timbot zaala zilŋanzilŋan. Ta kembei, mi tila tuŋ la Yerusalem.
\s1 Pilip ikam uruunu ambaiŋana pa biibi ta imar pa lele pakaana ki Etiopia
\p 
\v 26 To Merere aŋela kini ta, ipet ki Pilip mi iso: “Maŋga ma sala pa Yerusalem. Tona to zaala ta ipa pa lele bilimŋana ma isula pa kar Gaza na.”
\v 27 Pilip ileŋ sua ti, to imaŋga pa pai. Ila zaala lwoono na, ise ki tomtom ta, ni imar pa lele pakaana ki Etiopia. \f + \fr 8:27 \ft Etiopia, ina lele pakaana ta ki Aprika. Mi imbot molo kat pa Yerusalem.\f* Mi tomtom tana, ni zaana biibi. Imborro pat mi koroŋ zanŋan ki Kandake, ni moori ta imborro lele pakaana ki Etiopia na. \f + \fr 8:27 \ft Tomtom tina, tipal lembeene ma isu. Pa mazwaana tana tikamam mbulu ta kembei pizin tomooto ta tikamam uraata pa king ma kwin. Kokena timbuulu moori kizin sa. Buk Lo 23:1 iso wal ta kembei irao tigaaba Anutu wal kini pa suŋŋana kizin som. Tamen sua ti iswe kembei Anutu iyok pizin wal ta kembei raraate kembei ta wal pakan.\f*\x + \xo 8:27 \xt Mbo 68:31, 87:4\x*
\v 28 Tomtom tana isala pa Yerusalem pa suŋŋana, mi suŋŋana tana imap. Tana ni mbuleene sala karis kini, mi iŋgi be imiili mini pa kar kini i. Karis ikowo, mi ni iwatwaata sua ta muŋgu Anutu kwoono Yesaya ibeede na.
\v 29 Pilip ise kini, to Bubuŋana iso pini. Iso: “Koŋuru karis tiŋga ma la kolouŋana.”
\p 
\v 30 To Pilip iloondo ma ila karis uunu. Ila na, ileŋ tomtom tana iwatwaata ro ta Yesaya ibeede na. Tana Pilip iwi lae pini. Iso: “Ai, sua ta watwaata na, ute ka uunu?”
\p 
\v 31 Mi ni ipekel kwoono ma iso: “Wai, aŋute ko aŋute be parei? Bela tomtom sa iso yo pa.” To iso pa Pilip ma isala kini ta karis a.
\v 32 Mi sua lwoono ta tomtom tana iwatwaata na, iso ta kembei:
\q1 Ni kembei sipsip ta tikami be tipuni.
\q1 Mi imaane kembei sipsip lutuunu ta iur niini mi tipup rumuunu na.
\q1 Pa iso sua sa som.
\q1 
\v 33 Ni, tipasomi mi tipamenderi.
\q1 Mbulu ta tikam pini na, indeeŋe som.
\q1 Mi ni le tomtom sa be imender pini som.
\q1 Asiŋ ko ipit mbol pa popoŋana kini? Som.
\q1 Pa swoono ko imap karau men.”\x + \xo 8:33 \xt Yesa 53:7+\x*
\p 
\v 34 Tana biibi kizin Etiopia isu to iwi lae pa Pilip. Iso: “A, nu so yo lak. Sua tiŋgi, Anutu kwoono tana iso pa itunu, som iso pa tomtom toro sa?”
\v 35 Tona Pilip kwoono ila pa sua tana, mi iso seeŋge ma ila, mi izzo i pa uruunu ambaiŋana ki Yesu. [
\v 36 Tilala ma tindeeŋe yok ta, to biibi tana isu na iso: “Mi parei pio? Irao aŋkam yok? Pa yok ta, ta tamar i.”\x + \xo 8:36 \xt Ŋgo 2:38, 10:47\x*
\v 37 Pilip ipekel kwoono ma iso: “Nu sombe ur lelem imap ila ki Merere, ina ta tina. Rao kam yok.” Ni ipekel kwoono ma iso: “E, nio aŋurla. Yesu Krisi, ni Anutu lutuunu.”]
\p 
\v 38 To ikam ma karis imender ma imbot, mi ziru Pilip tisula yok ma Pilip ikam yok pini.
\v 39-40 Ziru tizem yok ma tise, to biibi tana ire Pilip mini som. Pa Merere Bubuŋana, ta iwiti ma ila iuri su kar Asdot. Tana Pilip iwwa pa kar ta boozomen ki lele pakaana tana, mi izzo uruunu ambaiŋana pizin ma ila ipet kar Sisarea. Mi biibi tana, ni imiili ma ila kar kini raama menmeen i biibi kat.\x + \xo 8:39-40 \xt Ŋgo 21:8\x*
\c 9
\s1 Yesu itooro Saul
\r (Ŋgo 22:3-16, 26:9-18)
\p 
\v 1-2 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana, ŋgar sananŋana izebzeebe men Saul, mi ni ikamam sua pamotoŋana pizin wal ta titoto Merere na. Pa isombe ipun zin ma timetmeete lup. Imbot ma som, mi ikam ŋgar. Iso: “O, nio ko aŋla kar Damaskus tomini. Beso aŋdeeŋe tomtom pakan ta titoto zaala ki Yesu isu tana, to aŋyo zin ma timar ta Yerusalem i.” Tana ila ma ire biibi kizin patoronŋana kan, mi iwi i be ibeede sua yokŋana pini. To ikam ma ila be lupŋana kizin Yuda ta timbot kar Damaskus na tire. Naso zaana imbot mat pa uraata kini.
\p 
\v 3 Saul imbel pai. Ila ila ma igarau kar Damaskus na, azuŋka tau imbot saamba mi ikelyaara su pini ma kembei ta lele ikimit i.
\v 4 Tabe itop su toono, mi ileŋ sua ta kembei: “Saul, Saul, parei ta nu noknok motoŋ seezeŋana?”
\p 
\v 5 Saul ipekel ma iso: “O biibi, nu asiŋ?” To pekelŋana imar. Iso: “Iŋgi nio Yesu ta nu seseeze motoŋ na. \x + \xo 9:5 \xt 1Kor 15:8\x*
\v 6 Maŋga ta buri mi lela kar, to leŋ sua pa mbulu tabe kam i.”
\p 
\v 7 Mi zin wal ta ziŋan Saul tiwwa na, len sua som. Timbot mi tire men. Pa tileŋleŋ sua ta imarmar, mi tire tomtom sa som.
\v 8 Saul burup ma imaŋga na, irao ire lele som. To titeegi mi tilela kar Damaskus.
\v 9 Ni mataana ipis ma imbot pa aigule tel. Mi mazwaana tana, ikan kini sa som, iwin yok sa som.
\p 
\v 10 Kar Damaskus na, tomtom ta tau itoto Yesu i, ni imbotmbot. Zaana Ananias. Ni ikeenetondo, mi ileŋ Merere iso sua pini ma iso: “Ananias o!” Ananias iso: “Oi Merere, nio aŋbotmbot i!”
\p 
\v 11 To Merere iso pini. Iso: “Maŋga mi la pa zaala ta tipaata tisombe Zalŋana na. La to, lela ruumu ki Yudas mi wi pa tomtom ta ki kar Tasus, zaana Saul. Pa izuŋzuŋ a.
\v 12 Iŋga ikeenetondo u, mi ire u pa ma la kini mi nomom isalakaali, to mataana ikam pak mini.”
\p 
\v 13 To Ananias iso: “Mi Merere, tomtom tina, wal boozo tiso uruunu ma aŋleŋ kek. Wal ku potomŋan ta timbot Yerusalem a, ni ikamam mbulu sananŋan boozomen pizin. \x + \xo 9:13 \xt Ŋgo 8:3\x*
\v 14 Mi zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan tiuri ma zaana be ikam mbulu raraate men pizin wal tau tizuŋzuŋ pa nu zom isu kar ti tomini.”
\p 
\v 15 Tamen Merere iso pini ma iso: “Soom. La. Pa tomtom tana, nio ituŋ aŋpeikati be ikam uraata tio, mibe iswe zoŋ ila ki zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i, mi zin king, mi zin Israel matan tomini. \x + \xo 9:15 \xt Ŋgo 26:16+; Ro 1:5; Ga 1:15+; 1Tim 1:12\x*
\v 16 Mi pataŋana tabe ibaada pa nio zoŋ kana, ina nio ituŋ ko aŋso i pa.” \x + \xo 9:16 \xt Lu 21:12+; Ŋgo 20:23; 2Kor 6:4+, 11:23+; 2Tim 2:9\x*
\p 
\v 17 To Ananias ila mi kaŋkaŋ ma ilela ruumu ki Yudas. Ilela na, iur namaana ru isala Saul ŋwaana, mi isombe: “O tiziŋ Saul, Merere Yesu, ta nu mar pa zaala mi ni ipet ku na, ni isombe nu re lele mini mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebu. Tanata iŋgo yo ma aŋmar i.”
\v 18 Molo som na, koroŋ ta ipakaala Saul mataana na, ikam pok mi itop su. To ire lele mini. Mi isu na ikam yok pataaŋa. \x + \xo 9:18 \xt Ŋgo 2:38\x*
\v 19 Kaimer ma ikan kini, to mburaana imiili mini. To ziŋan zin wal ki kar Damaskus ta titoto Yesu i, timbot su Damaskus pa aigule pakan.
\s1 Saul imaŋga pa sua soyaaraŋana isu Damaskus
\p 
\v 20 Saul inamnaama som. Imaŋga pataaŋa na ilelala lupŋana murin kizin Yuda, mi izzoyaryaara sua ta kembei: Yesu, ni Anutu Lutuunu.
\v 21 Tabe zin wal tau tileŋ i na, timap timurur pini. To tisu mi tiso ta kembei: “Wai, to ta koroŋ mi ikamyaryaara zin wal ta tizuŋzuŋ pa Yesu zaana isu Yerusalem, ta iŋgi isu mi iso mini kembei? Iti toso ko imar be iyo zin wal ki kar tiŋgi ta titoto Yesu i, ma tila kizin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan ta Yerusalem a.” \x + \xo 9:21 \xt Ŋgo 9:2+; Ga 1:23\x*
\p 
\v 22 Anutu ipombolmbol Saul ma sua kini mburaanaŋana kat. Tabe ikam ma zin Yuda ta timbotmbot Damaskus mi tileŋi na, tiru zalan pa sua. Pa izzo pa sua muŋguŋana ta iur ŋonoono ise ki Yesu. Tana sua kini iswe kat ta kembei: Yesu, ni Mesia. \x + \xo 9:22 \xt Ŋgo 5:42, 17:3, 18:5\x*
\p 
\v 23 Zin Yuda timbot ma aigule boozomen ilae, to tisu mi timbuuru kana.
\v 24 Mbeŋ ma aigule tizaŋzaaŋi su ta zaala kwoono. Beso tire i, to tipuni ma imeete. Tamen tiŋgal Saul talŋaana pa kiizi kizin tana,
\v 25 mi mbeŋ ta na, wal pakan ta titoto Yesu i, tiuri sula tiigi, mi tipabeleu i pa siiri ndemeene, mi titu i ma isula. \x + \xo 9:25 \xt 2Kor 11:32+\x*
\s1 Saul ila Yerusalem
\p 
\v 26 To Saul iko ma ila pa Yerusalem. Ila ipet to, isombe igaaba zin wal tau titoto Yesu i. Mi zin tiurla kembei ni itoori ma iwe Yesu lene i na som. Tana timoto i lup. \x + \xo 9:26 \xt Ga 1:17+\x*
\v 27 Tamen Panabas, ni iwe zaala pini. Ikami ma ila kizin ŋgoŋana, mi iso zin pa mbulu ta pet pa Saul na. Iso: ‘Saul ila ma Merere ipet kini isu zaala lwoono, mi iso sua pini. To Saul ila Damaskus, mi imender mbolŋana, mi ikam sua pizin tomtom pa Yesu zaana. Imoto som.’ \x + \xo 9:27 \xt Ŋgo 4:36; 1Kor 9:1, 15:8\x*
\v 28 Tileŋ sua tana, to lelen ambai pa Saul, mi ni igabgaaba zin ma ziŋan timbotmbot ta Yerusalem. Mi ni imender mbolŋana kat, mi iwwa pa Yerusalem, mi ikamam sua pizin tomtom pa Yesu zaana.
\v 29 Ni ziŋan zin Yuda ta tizzo Grik kalŋan i tiparzorzooro pa sua, to timaŋga na tiso tikam be tipuni ma imeete.
\v 30 Tamen zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi tileŋ sua tana, to tikami ma tisula kar Sisarea, to tiuri ma ila lene pa kar kini Tasus.
\p 
\v 31 Tona lupŋana ki Krisi ta timbot irao lele pakaana ki Yudea, Galilea, mi Samaria na, timbot ambai. Kosa sa imbuulu zin mini som. Mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana ipombolmbol zin, mi timototo Merere mi titoto mbulu kini. Tana timasaksak ma tiwe boozo. \x + \xo 9:31 \xt Ŋgo 2:41+, 4:32+\x*
\s1 Petrus iurpe tomtom narapeŋana ta isu kar Lidda
\p 
\v 32 Petrus, ni izzu ma izze pa lele ta boozomen. Aigule ta na, isula kar Lidda be ilou Anutu wal kini potomŋan ta timbot tana.
\v 33 Ila ipet na, indeeŋe tomtom narapeŋana ta, zaana Aineas. Ni ra, imbel keeneŋana. Pa ikeene pa ndaama lamata mi tel kek.
\v 34 Petrus ila ire i, to iso pini. Iso: “Aineas, Yesu Krisi iurpe u ma nim ndabok. Maŋga mi lek murim.” Iso ta kembei mi Aineas burup ma imaŋga pataaŋa. \x + \xo 9:34 \xt Ŋgo 3:6, 14:8+, 28:8+; Yems 5:14+\x*
\v 35 Zin Lidda kan mi Saron kan ta munŋaana men na, tire i, to titooro lelen mi tiurla ki Merere.
\s1 Petrus ipei moori ta ma imaŋga mini isu kar Yoppa
\p 
\v 36 Kar Yoppa na, moori ta itoto Yesu i imbotmbot, zaana Tapita. (Tipaata pisis tana ila Grik kalŋan, tisombe Dorkas.) Ni ikamam uraata ambaimbaiŋan boozomen mi iuluulu zin wal tau timbot ŋoobo pa kan kini ma len mburu ma. Tana welu kini ambaiŋana kat. \x + \xo 9:36 \xt 1Tim 2:10, 5:10; Tit 3:8\x*
\v 37 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana, ni mete ikami ma imeete. Tana tiurpe i, mi tiuri sala ruumu leleene ta imbot kor na ma imbotmbot.
\v 38 Kar Lidda mi Yoppa na, tipargarau zin. Tana zin wal ta titoto Yesu i tileŋ kembei Petrus imar imbotmbot Lidda, to tiŋgo wal ru ma tila, mi tisotaari pa mooribi tau. Tiso: “Aiss Petrus, niam leyam pataŋana ta, ta amar i. Parei? Ko irao mar ma itiŋan tala ta buri?”
\p 
\v 39 To ziŋan Petrus tila. Tipet kar na, tikam Petrus ma isala ruumu leleene ta imbot kor na. Per sala na, zin noroŋa ra, tila ma tiliu i. Mi titaŋtaŋ, mi tiso i pa mburu ta Tapitabi imbotmbot mata yaryaara mi ikamam pizin na.
\v 40 Petrus isu na iser zin wal ta timbot ruumu leleene na, ma tiyooto lup. Tiyooto makiŋ na, iŋgun kumbu mbukuunu mi isuŋ. To itoori ma kereene ila ki uri mi iso pini. Iso: “Tapita, maŋga!” \x + \xo 9:40 \xt Mk 5:41+; Lu 7:14; Yo 11:43+; Ŋgo 20:9+\x*
\p Molo som na, moori mataana ikam pak, mi ire Petrus. To imaŋga mi mbuleene su.
\v 41 Petrus iteege su pa namaana mi iwiti ma imaŋga imender, to iboobo zin noroŋa mi Anutu wal kini ma timar na, tire Tapita mataana iyaara mini ma imbotmbot.
\v 42 Uraata ti uruunu irak ma irao kar biibi Yoppa. Tabe tomtom boozo tiurla ki Merere.
\v 43 Mi Petrus, ni izem kar Yoppa loŋa som. Ila ki Simon tau ikamam uraata pa buzur kulin na, ma ziru timbot pa mazwaana ri.
\c 10
\s1 Konili iso la pa Petrus be imar
\p 
\v 1 Kar Sisarea na, tomtom ta imbotmbot, zaana Konili. Ni biibi ta kizin malmal kan ta timar pa toono Itali na. Imborro tomtom tomto lamata.
\v 2 Mi ni Yuda som. Tamen ziŋan wal boozomen ta timbot ruumu kini na, timototo Anutu mi titoto mbulu kini, mi tigabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin. Mi ni ikamam sorok koroŋ boozo pizin Yuda ta timbot ŋoobo i. Mi ni tomtom ki izuŋzuŋ pa Anutu totomen.
\p 
\v 3 Aigule ta na, zoŋ mataana ikam kembei tel, mi ni ikeenetondo. Mi ire kat aŋela ki Anutu ta imar kini mi iboobi. Iso: “Konili o!”
\p 
\v 4 Konili igeedi mi imoto. Imbot ma som mi iso: “Biibi, parei?”
\p Mi aŋela iso pini. Iso: “Suŋŋana ku ramaki mbulu ku ambaiŋana ta uluulu zin sorrokŋan i, na Anutu ire kek. Mi mataana iŋgalŋgal mi leleene ambai pa kembei ta patoronŋana ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 10:4 \xt Tur 8:4\x*
\v 5 Kar Yoppa na, tomtom ta imbotmbot, zaana Simon Petrus. Ŋgo wal pakan ma tila kini be tikami.
\v 6 Imbotmbot ki Simon toro ta ikamam uraata pa buzur kulin na. Ruumu kini imbot ta tai a.”\x + \xo 10:6 \xt Ŋgo 9:36\x*
\p 
\v 7 Aŋela iso sua tana makiŋ, to izemi mi ila lene. To Konili iboobo mbesooŋo kini ru ta tikamam uraata pa ruumu kini na, mi tomtom kini malmal kana ta tau imbesmbeeze pini. Tomtom tana, ni tomini itoto mbulu ki Anutu.
\v 8 Konili iso zin pa mbulu boozomen ta ipet na makiŋ, mana iŋgo zin ma tila pa kar Yoppa.
\s1 Petrus ikeenetondo
\r (Ŋgo 11:5-14)
\p 
\v 9 Aigule toro, zoŋ mataana ikam kembei palakuutu na, zin tel tana tiwwa ma tigarau kar Yoppa. Indeeŋe tana, Petrus isala pa pooto ta imbot ruumu uteene na be isuŋ.
\v 10 Imbotmbot ma peteli, to iso ikan ka kini. Tikamam uraata pa ka kini, mi ni isu na ikeenetondo.
\v 11 Mataana isala na, ire saamba ikaaga mi koroŋ kembei ta kawaala biibi i, timbuk tumbuntumbun paŋ, mi titu ma isu.
\v 12 Mi buzur matakiŋa ta tisula kawaala tana. Kar kan, su kan, koroŋ karraŋan, mi zin man ta tirrie sala maŋaanaŋana na.
\v 13 Molo som na, ileŋ sua ta kembei: “Petrus, maŋga, pun zin mi kan.”
\p 
\v 14 Mi Petrus iso: “E-e Merere, irao aŋkan na som kat. Pa muŋgu muŋgu mi imar na, kwoŋ iteege koroŋ sa ta kembei pasa zen. Koroŋ pakan tina ambai pa kanŋana som. Pa tutu iŋgalsek pa.”\x + \xo 10:14 \xt Wkp 11:1+\x*
\p 
\v 15 To ileŋ sua mini ma iwe ru pa. Iso: “Koroŋ ta Anutu itunu ikam ma iwe ŋgeezeŋana na, nu re kembei sananŋana pepe.”\x + \xo 10:15 \xt Mk 7:14+; Ro 14:14-20; 1Tim 4:3+\x*
\v 16 Iso ta kembei pa tel, mi kawaala imiili ma isala mini pa saamba.
\p 
\v 17 Petrus imaŋga ma ikamam ŋgar boozo pa koroŋ ta ire na, mi tomtom tel ta Konili iŋgo zin na, timar mi tindeeŋe Simon ruumu kini ma timender su kataama kwoono.
\v 18 To tiwi ma tiso: “Simon ta zaana toro Petrus na, imbotmbot, som som?”
\p 
\v 19 Petrus ikamam ŋgar pa koroŋ ta ire na, mi Bubuŋana iso pini. Iso: “Simon, tomtom tel tiru u a.
\v 20 Maŋga ma sula re zin. Mi lelem iwe ru pepe. La gaaba zin ma niomŋan kala. Pa iŋga nio aŋgo zin ta timar na.”
\v 21 Tana Petrus isula kizin to iso: “Nio ta ituŋ ti. Mi parei ta kamar kuru yo?”
\p 
\v 22 To tiso: “Konili ta imborro zin malmal kan tomto lamata i, ni iŋgo yam ta amar i. Ni tomtom ndeeŋeŋana, mi imototo Anutu mi itoto mbulu kini. Tana Yuda ta boozomen timap tiwidit uruunu. Neeri ŋonoono, ni ikeenetondo mi ire aŋela potomŋana ta ipet kini. Mi iso pini be iboobu ma la ruumu kini, mi kam sua pakan pini ma ileŋ.”
\v 23 Petrus imaŋga na ikam zin ma tilela pa ruumu tau ni imbotmbot pa i.
\s1 Petrus ila ki Konili
\p Tikeene ma aigule toro to, ziŋan Petrus timaŋga ma tila. Mi zin toŋmatiziŋ pakan ta ki kar Yoppa i tomini tigaaba zin.
\v 24 Tiwwa ma tila ma aigule toro to tipet Sisarea. Mi Konili, ni iyogeege zin wal kini mi waene bizin pakan tomini, mi ziŋan tinamnaama zin ma timbotmbot.
\v 25 Petrus ila mabe iloondo pa ruumu, mi Konili ila to itop su kumbuunu uunu bekena ipakuri.
\v 26 Tamen Petrus ipeteke i ma iso: “Wa, kam kembena paso? Maŋga! Pa nio iŋgi tomtom raraate kembei ta nu na.” To iwiti ma imaŋga.\x + \xo 10:26 \xt Ŋgo 14:15; Tur 19:10, 22:8+\x*
\p 
\v 27 Ziru tizzo sua ma tilela na, Petrus mataana pokpok pizin iwal biibi ta tilup zin ma timbotmbot.
\v 28 To iso pizin. Iso: “Ou, niom kuute lup kek. Niam Yuda, tutu tiam imender ta kembei. Zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i na, irao amgaaba zin som, amgarau zin som. Tamen Anutu, ni iso yo kek ta kembei: Irao aŋur ŋgalseki pa tomtom sa na som. Mi irao aŋso tomtom sa, ni sananŋana pa Anutu mataana na som.\x + \xo 10:28 \xt Ŋgo 15:8+; Ep 2:11+\x*
\v 29 Tana sua tiom ila, mi iŋgi aŋmar i. Aŋkam zooroŋana som. Lak, parei?”
\p 
\v 30 Konili iso: “Wai! Mi nio ti, uriiza, zoŋ mataana ikam tel kembei ta buri na, aŋzuŋzuŋ su ruumu tio ti. Mi molo som na, aŋre tomtom ta. Mburu kini milmilŋana. Imar imender su kereŋ uunu mi iso:
\v 31 ‘Konili o, suŋŋana ku, Anutu ileŋ kek. Mi mbulu ku ambaiŋana ta uluulu zin sorrokŋan na, ni mataana iŋgalŋgal.\x + \xo 10:31 \xt 1Kor 15:58; Ibr 6:10\x*
\v 32 Tana ŋgo wal pakan ma tila kar Yoppa be tikam Simon ta zaana toro Petrus na. Imbotmbot ki Simon toro ta ikamam uraata pa buzur kulin na. Ruumu kini imbotmbot ta tai a.’
\v 33 Tanata aŋgo zin tomtom ma tima ku karau men. Ma iŋgi mar ma ambai kat. Mi niam munŋoyam ta amar amlup yam su taiŋgi pa Anutu mataana. Tana sua ta munŋaana men tau Merere iur ma ku be kam piam na, so ma amleŋ.”
\s1 Zaala ikaaga pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i
\p 
\v 34 To Petrus imaŋga mi iso: “Oo, buri na, ŋgar tio ipet mi aŋkilaala i. Ŋonoono kat. Merere, ni iur leleene pizin wal pakan, mi wal pakan som na som.\x + \xo 10:34 \xt Mt 16:19; Ro 2:11; Ep 6:9; 1Pe 1:17\x*
\v 35 Ni iur leleene pizin wal ta boozomen. Tana tomtom ta sombe imoto i, mi ikamam mbulu ta indeeŋe men pa ni mataana, na ta tina. Ni, Merere leleene pini.\x + \xo 10:35 \xt Ro 2:10+; 1Kor 12:13; Ga 3:28; Ep 3:6; Kol 3:11\x*
\v 36 Ŋonoono, uruunu ambaiŋana ta iso iti pa zaala tabe itiŋan Anutu taparlup ti ma tewe tamen pa i, na Anutu ipumuuŋgu piam Israel. Zaala tana imbot la uraata ki Yesu Krisi. Mi ni Merere kizin tomtom ta boozomen.\x + \xo 10:36 \xt Ro 10:12; Ep 2:14; Kol 1:20; Tur 17:14\x*
\p 
\v 37-38 “Mi uraata biibi tau ipet ma irao lele pakaana ki Yudea na, niom ko keleŋ sa kek. Indeeŋe tau Yoan ikamam sua pizin tomtom pa yok kamŋana na, Yesu ki Nasaret, ni imaŋga pa uraata kini isu Galilea. Ni, Anutu iroogi mi iuri pa uraata kini. Pa isilou i pa Bubuŋana Potomŋana, mi ipomboli pa itunu mburaana. Tanata izzu ma izze pa uraata ambaimbaiŋan, mi iurpewe wal boozomen ta Tomtom Sanaana mburaana ikototo zin na. Pa ni, Anutu imbotmbot raami tau.\x + \xo 10:37-38 \xt Yesa 61:1\x*
\p 
\v 39 “Uraata kini boozomen ta ikamam su lele pakaana ki Yudea mi Yerusalem na, niam ti amre kat pa motoyam. Tanata ampombolmbol ka sua. Uraata kini tana, ta ikam ma tipuni ma imeete sala ke.\x + \xo 10:39 \xt Ŋgo 2:32, 5:30\x*
\v 40 Tamen aigule iwe tel pa, to Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga mini pa naala, mi ipatooŋi pizin tomtom pakan ma tire kati.
\v 41 Mi indeeŋe ta ni imaŋga pa naala na, ila ipet kizin iwal boozo som. Niam men ta ipet tiam mi amre i, mi niamŋan amkan kini. Pa Anutu ipeikat yam ta muŋgu kek be amender pa sua kini mi ampombol.\x + \xo 10:41 \xt Lu 24:36+\x*
\v 42 Mi ni itunu iur sua piam be amsoyaara sua pizin Israel ta kembei: Ni, Anutu iuri be itiiri zin tomtom pa mbulu kizin, mibe iur kadoono pizin. Zin ta matan yaryaaraŋan, mi wal meeteŋan tomini.\x + \xo 10:42 \xt Mt 28:19+; Ŋgo 17:31; Ro 14:9+; 2Kor 5:10\x*
\v 43 Mi Anutu kwoono bizin ta boozomen, sua kizin ipombol sua kini ma iso ta kembei: Wal boozomen ta so tiurla kini, inako ni iwe zaala pizin be Anutu ireege sanaana kizin.”\x + \xo 10:43 \xt Yesa 53:5; Ro 10:9; 1Yo 2:2,12\x*
\s1 Anutu ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i
\p 
\v 44 Petrus izzo sua tana, mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana tau isu ma isalakaala wal ta boozomen ta tileŋleŋ sua i.
\v 45-46 Zin Yuda pakan ta tiurla ki Krisi mi ziŋan Petrus timar na, tire Bubuŋana isalakaala zin wal tana, mi tileŋ zin tizzo karkari kalŋan mi tipakurkur Anutu, to timurur mi tisombe: “Wai, wal tiŋgi, zin Yuda som. Mi iŋgi Anutu ikam pizin ta kembei tomini?”\x + \xo 10:45-46 \xt Mk 16:17; Ŋgo 2:4, 11:15; Ga 3:14\x*
\p 
\v 47 To Petrus isu mi iso: “Asiŋ irao iŋgalsek pizin wal ti be tikam yok? Som. Zin iŋgi tikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana raraate kembei ta iti.”\x + \xo 10:47 \xt Ŋgo 15:8+\x*
\v 48 Tana Petrus iso pizin ma tikam yok pa Yesu Krisi zaana. Kaimer mana tibiigi Petrus ma ziŋan timbot pa aigule pakan.
\c 11
\s1 Petrus isope zin Yerusalem kan pa uraata kini
\r (Ŋgo 10:9-44)
\p 
\v 1 Zin ŋgoŋana ziŋan zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi ta timbotmbot irao lele pakaana ki Yudea na, tileŋ zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i urun kembei zin tomini tikan la Anutu sua kini kek.
\v 2 Tabe Petrus isala Yerusalem na, zin tau timbolmbol pa tutu ki Mose mi reeteŋana na, tiyyo kwon pini.
\v 3 Tiso: “Petrus o, nu tina la ma niomŋan zin wal ta tireete zin som na, kakanan kini isu ruumu kizin, na?”
\p 
\v 4 Petrus imaŋga to isinin mbulu boozomen ta ipet pini na. Iso:
\v 5 “Keleŋ, nio ti aŋbotmbot ta kar Yoppa, mi aŋzuŋzuŋ. Mi aŋkeenetondo, mi motoŋ sala na, aŋre koroŋ kembei ta kawaala biibi i. Timbit tumbuntumbun paŋ mi titu ma isu. Isu isu ma isu ta kereŋ uunu i.
\v 6 Mi motoŋ isula kawaala leleene na, aŋre buzur matakiŋa. Kar kan, su kan, pakan ta tikarra i, mi man ta tirrie sala maŋaanaŋana i tisula ma bok.
\v 7 Molo som na, aŋleŋ kalŋaana ta iso ta kembei: ‘Petrus o, maŋga! Pun zin, mi kan.’
\p 
\v 8 “To aŋso: ‘E-e Merere, irao aŋkan na som kat. Pa muŋgu muŋgu mi imar na, koroŋ ta kembei isula kopoŋ pasa zen. Koroŋ pakan tina ambai pa kanŋana som. Pa tutu iŋgalsek pa.’\x + \xo 11:8 \xt Wkp 11:1+\x*
\p 
\v 9 “To sua imbot saamba mi isu ma iwe ru pa. Iso: ‘Koroŋ ta Anutu itunu ikam ma iwe ŋgeezeŋana na, nu re kembei sananŋana pepe.’\x + \xo 11:9 \xt Mk 7:14+; Ro 14:14-20; 1Tim 4:3+\x*
\v 10 Iso ta kembei pa tel, to koroŋ ta boozomen imiili ma isala mini pa saamba.
\p 
\v 11 “Molo som na, tomtom tel ki kar Sisarea ta tiŋgo zin pio na, timar timender ruumu tau nio aŋbotmbot pa i, ka kataama kwoono.
\v 12 Mi Bubuŋana iso pio be leleŋ iwe ru pepe, mibe aŋgaaba zin ma niamŋan amla. Zin toŋmatiziŋ lamata mi ta ti tomini. Niamŋan amla mi amlela tomtom tana ruumu kini.
\v 13 To ruumu katuunu imaŋga na iso piam ta kembei. Ni ire aŋela ta ila ipet kini su ruumu kini mi iso: ‘Ŋgo wal pakan ma tila kar Yoppa be tikam Simon ta zaana toro Petrus na ma imar.
\v 14 Pa ni ko ikam sua piom. Mi sua kini ko iwe zaala pu mi wal boozomen ta timbot ruumu ku na be Anutu ikamke yom.’
\p 
\v 15 “Tana aŋmaŋga be aŋso sua, mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana isu ma isalakaala zin. Ikam raraate kembei tau mata popoten ikam piti na.
\v 16 To motoŋ iŋgal Merere kalŋaana ta isombe: ‘Yoan ikam yok pizin tomtom. Mi niom, nako kakam Bubuŋana Potomŋana ma isalakaala yom.’\x + \xo 11:16 \xt Mt 3:11; Ŋgo 1:5\x*
\v 17 Kere. Muŋgu iti tuurla ki Merere Yesu Krisi, mi Anutu ikam Bubuŋana piti. Mi ni ikam koroŋ pizin wal tana raraate men kembei ta ikam piti na. Kena nio asiŋ ta aŋrao be aŋzooro Anutu? Pa koroŋ tiŋgi imar pa ni itunu tau.”\x + \xo 11:17 \xt Ŋgo 10:47, 15:8+\x*
\p 
\v 18 Tileŋ ta kembei to, timbuulu sua pini mini som. Mi tipakur Anutu zaana ma tiso: “Ŋonoono kat. Anutu, ni ipomoozo zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i tomini, mi ikam zin ma titooro lelen, bekena tikam mbotŋana ta ki Anutu i.”\x + \xo 11:18 \xt Ro 10:12+, 15:9,16\x*
\s1 Lupŋana ki Krisi ta imbot su kar Antiok
\p 
\v 19 Indeeŋe tipun Setepan mi imar na, wal ki Krisi tibadbaada pataŋana biibi pa sua ki Merere. Tana timureege, mi tiko kiŋakiŋa pa lele pakaana ki Ponisia, mutu Saiprus, mi kar Antiok. Tiwwa na, tikamam sua pizin Yuda men.\x + \xo 11:19 \xt Ŋgo 8:1,4\x*
\v 20 Mi tomtom kizin pakan ta timar pa mutu Saiprus mi lele pakaana ki Kairini na, tila pa kar Antiok, to tiso zin Grik tomini pa uruunu ambaiŋana ki Merere Yesu.
\v 21 Mi tiwwa raama Merere mburaana, tana iwal biibi ki kar tana tiurla ki Merere mi titooro lelen.\x + \xo 11:21 \xt Ŋgo 13:1+, 14:26+, 18:22+\x*
\p 
\v 22 Uraata ti uruunu ila ipet ta Yerusalem mi lupŋana ki Krisi tileŋ, to tiŋgo Panabas ma ila kar Antiok be ire zin.\x + \xo 11:22 \xt Ŋgo 8:14+\x*
\v 23 Ila ma ipet na, ire kampeŋana biibi ki Anutu ta imbotmbot se kizin, tana menmeeni pa. Mi ipombolmbol zin iwal ma izzo pizin be tiur lelen imap ila ki Merere mi tikiskis urlaŋana kizin.\x + \xo 11:23 \xt Ŋgo 14:22\x*
\v 24 Pa Panabas, ni tomtom ambaiŋana. Urlaŋana kini imbol kat, mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe kati. Mi mazwaana tana, wal boozomen tiurla ki Merere mi tigaaba wal kini.\x + \xo 11:24 \xt Ŋgo 2:41, 4:36+\x*
\p 
\v 25 To Panabas ila Tasus be iru Saul.\x + \xo 11:25 \xt Ŋgo 9:27,30\x*
\v 26 Iru i iru i ma indeeŋi to ikami ma ziru timiili ma tila mini pa kar Antiok. Mi ndaama munŋaana tina, Panabas ziru Saul ziŋan lupŋana ki Krisi ta imbot kar tana na tiparluplup zin. Mi ziru tikamam sua pizin iwal biibi. Zin Antiok kan ta titoto Yesu i, ta mata popoten mi tomtom tiwatwaata zin be ‘Kristen.’\x + \xo 11:26 \xt 1Pe 4:16\x*
\p 
\v 27 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana na, Merere kwoono bizin pakan timbot Yerusalem mi tisula kar Antiok.
\v 28 To tomtom kizin ta, zaana Agabus, Bubuŋana ipazali mi imaŋga to ipityaara sua pa peteele biibi tabe isu pa toono ta boozomen. (Peteele tana ipet indeeŋe Klodias iwe Kaisa mi imborro lele.)\x + \xo 11:28 \xt Ŋgo 21:10\x*
\v 29 To zin wal ta titoto Yesu i, tilup zin mi tikam naman ikot zin be tiuulu zin toŋmatiziŋ kizin ta timbotmbot lele pakaana ki Yudea na. Tikam irao zitun pat kizin.\x + \xo 11:29 \xt Ro 15:26; 1Kor 16:1; 2Kor 8:1+, 9:1\x*
\v 30 Tikam ta kembei to, tikam seŋgeeri kizin se ki Panabas ziru Saul. Mi ziru tikam ma tila tiur la kizin mboroŋan ta timbot Yerusalem na.\x + \xo 11:30 \xt Ŋgo 12:25\x*
\c 12
\s1 Tiseeze zin urlaŋana kan matan mini
\p 
\v 1 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana na, king Erot \f + \fr 12:1 \ft Sua ki Merere iso pa tomtom boozo ta zan Erot. Indeeŋe Yesu isu na, Erot mataana kana ikamam peeze pizin Israel. Ni ta ipun zin pikin ki Betelem ma timetmeete. Mi ni lutuunu zaana Erot tomini. Lutuunu tana, ta ipun Yoan ma imeete, mi igaaba Kaipas mi Pontius Pilatus ma tipun Yesu. To isu mini pa Erot ta iwe tel pa. Sua pakaana ti iso pa Erot tana. Ni Erot mataana kana tumbuunu. Erot ta iwe tel pa ta ipun Yems ma imeete, mi kaimer motmooto tikani. To ni lutuunu, zaana Erot Agripa, ta kaimer tipamender Paulus ila kereene uunu. Ka mbol imbot la sua pakaana 25:13–26:32.\f* ni imaŋga, mi ikis tomtom pakan ta timbot lela lupŋana ki Krisi i be iseeze matan.
\v 2 Iso ma tikam Yems ta Yoan toono na, mi tiyembut ŋgureene pa buza ma imeete. \x + \xo 12:2 \xt Mt 4:21, 20:22+\x*
\v 3 Mi ire kembei zin Yuda lelen ambai pa uraata tana, tona imaŋga na ikis Petrus tomini. Uraata tina ipet indeeŋe zin Yuda tilup zin be tikan narabu ta ka yis somŋana na. \x + \xo 12:3 \xt Kam 12:15, 23:15\x*
\v 4 Tana Erot ikam Petrus to, ila iuri lela ruumu sanaana. Mi iuri la kizin menderŋan lamoro mata mi ta be matan pini. Zin menderŋan tana na, paŋpaŋa timbot la uunu tataŋa mi tiparpekelkel zin. Pa Erot ikam ŋgar ta kembei. Lupŋana biibi ki Pasoba isombe imap, to ikam Petrus mi ipamenderi ila iwal biibi matan.
\v 5 Tana Petrus, tiuri lela ruumu sanaana ma imbotmbot. Tamen lupŋana ki Krisi, zin tiur lelen imap mi tizuŋzuŋ mbolŋana pa Anutu be iuuli. \x + \xo 12:5 \xt Ro 15:30+; Ep 6:18\x*
\s1 Aŋela itatke Petrus pa ruumu sanaana
\p 
\v 6 Indeeŋe nol tabe Erot ikam Petrus ma iyooto pa ruumu sanaana be ipamenderi na ka mbeŋ na, menderŋan ru timenderkalkaala Petrus, mi ni ikenne su ziru mazwan. Ni, tipo i pa re ru. Mi menderŋan pakan timendernder su kataama kwoono tomini be timboro ruumu sanaana.
\v 7 Molo som na, aŋela ki Merere ta imar. Mi azuŋka kini iyaara lela ruumu sanaana tana leleene. To aŋela ipai Petrus ma iso: “A, maŋga ta buri!” Izzo sua tana, mi re ta tipo Petrus pa na, imet ma isu lene.
\p 
\v 8 To aŋela iso pini mini. Iso: “Ur pus ku mi kumbum keteene ila.” Petrus izeebi pa mburu kini makiŋ, to aŋela iso pini. Iso: “Ur mburu ku mat kana isala regem mi to yo.”
\v 9 Tona Petrus ito i mi ziru tiyooto pa ruumu sanaana. Tamen ni le ŋgar sa pa mbulu ta aŋela ikam pini i som. Iso ko ikeenetondo ma iŋgi.
\v 10 Ziru tila ma tizem menderŋan uunu ta, to tila tizem toro, mana timar kataama mbolŋana ta ila pa zaala kwoono na. Tipa ma timar to, kataama itunu ikaaga sorok, mi ziru tiyooto. Tizem ruumu sanaana mi titoto zaala ma tilala mi molo som na, aŋela izemi. \x + \xo 12:10 \xt Mbo 34:7; Ŋgo 5:19, 16:25+; 2Kor 1:10\x*
\p 
\v 11 To Petrus ŋgar kini ipet mi iso: “O, iŋgi buri na aŋkilaala i. Iŋgi Anutu iŋgo aŋela kini ma imar bekena itatke yo pa Erot namaana mi mbulu boozomen ta zin Yuda tisombe tikam pio i.”
\p 
\v 12 Petrus ikilaala mbulu ta ipet pini to, ikoŋuru ruumu ki Maria, ta Yoan Markus naana na. Ruumu tana leleene na, wal boozomen ta tila tilup zin pa, mi tizuŋzuŋ ma timbotmbot. \x + \xo 12:12 \xt Ŋgo 12:5,25, 15:37+\x*
\v 13 Petrus ila na ipitpit lae pa kataama. To mbesooŋo moori ta, zaana Roda, ila be isol kataama.
\v 14 Som, mi ikilaala Petrus kalŋaana. To menmeeni biibi kat, mi iloondo ma ilela kizin iwal biibi ma iso: “Aleei, Petrus itunu ta imendernder kataama kwoono a!”
\v 15 To zin tiso: “Waa, nu kankaana. Petrus imbot ruumu sanaana leleene.” Mi Roda kwoono imbol ma iso: “Soom, ni tau.” To zin tiso: “Inako aŋela kini ma iŋgi.”
\p 
\v 16 Mi Petrus ni imbotmbot mat men mi ipunun kataama. Beso tisol kataama na, tire i to timurur.
\v 17 To kalŋan izalla. Tamen ni iur namaana pizin be timaane. To ipit mbol pa zaala ta Merere ikami ma iyooto pa ruumu sanaana na. Ipit ma imap, mi iso pizin be tila tisotaara Yems \f + \fr 12:17 \ft Yems ti, ni Yesu tiziini ŋonoono.\f* mi toŋmatiziŋ pakan tomini pa mbulu ta ipet pini na. To izem zin, mi iko ma ila lele toro.
\p 
\v 18 Tikeene ma aigule toro, zoŋ ise na, orooro tau sorok som isala. Pa zin menderŋan tiru Petrus zalaana. Tiso: “To tana ko sokorei ikami?”
\v 19 Erot ileŋ sua tana, to iso pizin menderŋan be tila tiru i. Tamen tiru i ma som. To iwisese zin. Iwi zin ma som to, iur sua mi tikam zin ma tila be tiur kadoono pizin. Mana kaimer to Erot imaŋga na izem lele pakaana ki Yudea, mi isula imbot kar Sisarea.
\s1 Meeteŋana ki Erot
\p 
\v 20 Erot, ni keteene malmal kat pa kar ru, Tiro mi Sidon. Tana kar ru tana tilup zin mi tila be tire i. Paso tiŋgimgiimi kan kini ta king lele kini a. Mi timoto: Kokena ni iruutu pizin. Tana tila na loŋa mi tikam Blastus leleene. Pa Blastus tana, ni imborro king ruumu kini. Mana tila ki Erot itunu be ziŋan tiparurpe lelen. Tiso sua kizin ma ileŋ, to iur nol pizin be ipekel kalŋan.
\p 
\v 21 Indeeŋe nol tana ipet na, Erot izeebi pa mburu milmilŋana ki king, mi ila imbutul sala sua urpeŋana muriini be ikam sua pizin tomtom.
\v 22 Mi zin tomtom ta tileŋleŋ la pa kalŋaana na, kalŋan zalla ma tizzo: “To iŋga tomtom som. Iŋga ko Anutu tau!”
\v 23 Tizzo na molo? Merere aŋela kini ituti ma kaŋ kuruŋ su. Pa ipakur itunu ma isombe ikam Anutu muriini mi zaana ilip. Tana motmooto tikan ketenketen ma imeete.
\s1 Panabas ziru Saul timiili pa Antiok
\p 
\v 24 Mi Merere sua kini na, mburaana mi ila ma ila. \x + \xo 12:24 \xt Ŋgo 6:7, 19:20; Kol 1:6\x*
\v 25 Mi Panabas ziru Saul na, tiposop uraata kizin isu Yerusalem makiŋ to, tikam Yoan Markus mi ziŋan timiili ma tisula mini pa kar Antiok. \x + \xo 12:25 \xt Ŋgo 11:29+, 12:12\x*
\c 13
\s1 Tiur Panabas ziru Saul pa uraata
\p 
\v 1 Lupŋana ki Krisi ta imbot su kar Antiok na, Merere kwoono bizin pakan mi zin tau tipaute zin tomtom pa sua ki Merere na, ta zan tis: Panabas, Simion ta tipaati be Aigap na, Lusius ta imar pa lele pakaana ki Kairini na, Manaen ta muŋgu iwe Erot toroono na, mi Saul.
\v 2 Aigule ta na, tiŋgalsek zitun pa kini kanŋana bekena timbot kat pa suŋŋana. Tizuŋzuŋ, mi Bubuŋana Potomŋana iso pizin ta kembei. Iso: “Kozo kuur Panabas ziru Saul be tikam uraata ta aŋroogo zin pa na.”\x + \xo 13:2 \xt Ŋgo 9:15; Ro 10:15; Ep 3:7+; 1Tim 2:7\x*
\v 3 Tana tisuŋ mi kaimer, to tiur naman salakaala zin, mi tiur zin ma tila.\x + \xo 13:3 \xt Ŋgo 6:6, 14:26\x*
\s1 Saul ziru Panabas tila mutu Saiprus
\p 
\v 4 Tana Bubuŋana Potomŋana iŋgo Panabas ziru Saul ma tila pa uraata. Tisula kar Selusia, to tikam wooŋgo mi tikwai ma tila pa mutu Saiprus.
\v 5 Tilela kar Salamis, to tilala lupŋana murin kizin Yuda mi tizzoyaryaara Anutu sua kini. Mi Yoan Markus, ni igaaba zin tomini be iuulu zin pa uraata.\x + \xo 13:5 \xt Ŋgo 13:13, 15:37+\x*
\p 
\v 6 Tiwwa pa mutu tana ma timar tipet kar biibi Papos. Tipet Papos, to tindeeŋe Yuda ta. Ni tomtom naborouŋana mi ipakamkaam kembei ni Anutu kwoono. Zaana Bar-Yesu.\x + \xo 13:6 \xt Ŋgo 8:9+\x*
\v 7 Mi ni igabgaaba Sergius Paulus ta ni biibi mi imborro mutu tana. Sergius Paulus, ni tomtom ŋgarŋana, mi leleene be ileŋ sua ki Anutu. Tabe iso la pa Panabas ziru Saul be timar kini.
\v 8 Tomtom naborouŋana tana zaana toro Elimas. Pisis tana ka uunu ta kembei: ‘tomtom yaambaŋana.’ Mi ni izorzooro ziru kwon. Pa leleene be biibi ki mutu tana iurla ki Krisi pepe.
\v 9 To Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe Saul, ta tipaata zaana toro be Paulus na, mi igeede la pa tomtom naborouŋana tana,
\v 10 mi iso: “Hai, nu tina ta urur koi pa mbulu ndeeŋeŋan ta munŋaana men. Mi mbulu pakaamŋan ta boozomen na, nu rao pa kat. Tomtom Sanaana lutuunu ta nu na! Nu pandelndel zin tomtom pa zaala ndeeŋeŋana ki Merere paso? Ŋiizi na zem mbulu ku tana?\x + \xo 13:10 \xt Mt 13:38; Yo 8:44; 1Yo 3:8\x*
\v 11 Iŋgi be re kat Anutu mburaana. Ni ko ipumun motom ma ipis kat ma rao re lele som. Mi ko mbot ta kembei ma risa.”
\p Molo som na, zugut izukkaali ma sik. To isu na izoromrom, mi iru le tomtom sa be iteege namaana mi iuuli.
\v 12 Mi biibi ki mutu tana ire mbulu ta ipet na, to iurla kat. Mi imurur pa sua ki Merere ta tipaute i pa na mburaana.
\s1 Paulus ziru Panabas tila kar Antiok ta Pisidia a
\p 
\v 13 Paulus ziŋan waene bizin tikam wooŋgo isu Papos, mi tikwai ma tila mi tilela kar Perga, ta imbot lele pakaana ki Pampilia na. Timbot tana, mi Yoan Markus izem zin mi imiili ma ila lene pa Yerusalem.\x + \xo 13:13 \xt Ŋgo 13:5, 15:37+\x*
\v 14 To Paulus bizin tizem Perga mi tisala pa kar Antiok ta imbot lele pakaana ki Pisidia na. Timbot ma indeeŋe aigule potomŋana kizin Yuda be keten su, to tilela lupŋana muriini kizin ma mbulen su.
\v 15 Kaimer ma tipaata tutu ki Mose mi sua ki Merere kwoono bizin makiŋ, to zin mboroŋan ki lupŋana muriini tana tiso pa Paulus ziru Panabas. Tiso: “Ou, niom toŋmatiziŋ ru tana, sombe leyom sua sa be kopombol zin wal tiŋgi pa, na koso.”\x + \xo 13:15 \xt Lu 4:16+\x*
\s1 Mos ta Paulus ikam pizin Yuda isu kar Antiok
\p 
\v 16 To Paulus imaŋga imender, mi iur namaana pizin be matan ila kini, mi isu na iso: “O niom tomtom ki Israel mi niom pakan ta komototo Anutu mi kototo mbulu kini na, kuŋgun talŋoyom mi keleŋ!
\v 17 Muŋgu, Anutu kiti Israel, ni itunu ipeikat tumbundu bizin, mi ikam zin ma tiwe lene. Mi indeeŋe mazwaana ta tila tiwe leembe isu Aikuptu na, ni ikam zin ma urun iwe biibi kat, mi iswe mburaana biibi, mi iyaaru zin ma tizem Aikuptu.\x + \xo 13:17 \xt Kam 6:6+, 12:51\x*
\v 18 Mi indeeŋe tau tiwwa isu lele bilimŋana pa ndaama tomtooru na, timbel zooroŋana. Tabe Anutu niini gesges pizin. Tamen ni izem kat zin som, mi mataana pizin.\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Kam 16:8; Nam 14:33+; Mbo 95:10; Ŋgo 7:36\x*
\v 19 Tiwwa ma tipet toono Kanaan to, ni ipambiriizi lele pakaana lamata mi ru ka tomtom bizin, mi iur toono kizin ma iwe zin Israel len.\x + \xo 13:19 \xt Lo 7:1; Mbo 78:55; Ŋgo 7:45\x*
\v 20 Uraata ta boozomen tana ikam ndaama 450, to zin Israel tikam toono Kanaan ma iwe len kat.
\p “Kaimer mana, Anutu iur zin bibip tau len ŋgarŋan i be tikam peeze pizin, mi imar imar ma indeeŋe mazwaana ki Samuel ta Anutu kwoono na.
\v 21 Tona zin tisu na titaŋroro Anutu pa len king. Tana ni iur Saul ta Kis lutuunu na, ma iwe king pizin. Saul tana, uunu kini ipet pa Benyamen. Mi ni imboro Israel pa ndaama tomtooru.\x + \xo 13:21 \xt 1Sam 8:4+, 10:17+\x*
\v 22 Tamen kaimer na, Anutu iziiri i, mi iur Dabit ma ikam Saul muriini. Mi iwit Dabit uruunu ma iso ka sua ta kembei:
\q1 Aa, Dabit ta Yesi lutuunu na, nio leleŋ pini ilip. Pa ni itoto kat leleŋ. Ni ko ito ŋgar tio pa koroŋ ta boozomen.\x + \xo 13:22 \xt 1Sam 13:14, 15:23+, 16:12+; Mbo 89:20\x*
\b
\p 
\v 23 “Imar imar ma Anutu iur Yesu ta iyooto pa Dabit popoŋana kini na, ma iwe ulaaŋa pizin Israel. Ito sua kini mbukŋana tau.\x + \xo 13:23 \xt Mbo 132:11; Lu 1:32\x*
\v 24 Indeeŋe Yesu imaŋga pa uraata kini zen na, Yoan imuuŋgu pini mi ikamam sua pizin Israel ta boozomen be titooro lelen mi tikam yok.\x + \xo 13:24 \xt Lu 3:3\x*
\v 25 Ni ikamam uraata ta Anutu iur la namaana na, mabe imap, to iwi zin. Iso: ‘Ou, niom koso nio asiŋ? Nio ti, tomtom ta kuurur motoyom pini i som. Mi tomtom tana, ni itoto yo ma iwwa i. Nio aŋre ituŋ kembei aŋrao pini risa som kat. Uraata sorokŋana kembei kumbu keteene ka wooro putkeŋana, ina tomini aŋrao aŋkam pini na som. Pa ni ilip kat pio.’”\x + \xo 13:25 \xt Lu 3:16\x*
\p 
\v 26 To Paulus iseeŋge sua kini ma iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, niom ta Abaraam popoŋana kini, mi niom pakan ta komototo Anutu mi kototo mbulu kini na tomini, keleŋ. Sua ta iso pa ulaaŋa tabe imar i, iŋgi imar piti tau.\x + \xo 13:26 \xt Lu 24:47; Ŋgo 2:39, 3:26\x*
\v 27-28 Tamen zin Yerusalem kan ziŋan zin peeze kan kizin tikilaala Yesu som. Ŋonoono, tiwatwaata sua ki Anutu kwoono bizin ikot aigule potomŋan ta boozomen. Tamen tikam ŋgar pa som. Tanata tiseeze sorok Yesu mataana, mi timaŋmaŋ Pilatus, tabe ni iur sua ma tipuni ma imeete. Mi Yesu, ni le uunu sa isaana som. Mi mbulu ta tikam pini, ina ikam ma sua ki Anutu kwoono bizin ta tawatwaata na, iur ŋonoono.\x + \xo 13:27-28 \xt Mt 27:20+; Lu 23:18+; Ŋgo 3:14+\x*
\v 29 Pa mbulu boozomen ta ipet pini na, Anutu kwoono bizin tiso ka sua pataaŋa kek. Tana tikam mbulu ta boozomen tana makiŋ, to tikami ma isu pa ke pambaaraŋana, mi tila tiuri lela naala.\x + \xo 13:29 \xt Lu 23:50+, 24:44; Yo 19:36+\x*
\v 30 To Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga mini.\x + \xo 13:30 \xt Mt 28:6\x*
\v 31 Mi ilala iwedet kizin tomtom tau muŋgu ziŋan tiwwa ta Galilea mi tila tipet Yerusalem na. Wal tana, ta koozi tipombolmbol sua kini, mi tikamam sua pizin wal kiti Israel.\x + \xo 13:31 \xt Yo 20:19+; Ŋgo 1:3, 2:32\x*
\p 
\v 32 “Mi niam tiŋgi amar be amkam uruunu ambaiŋana ti piom. Kere. Sua ta muŋgu Anutu imbuk pa tumbundu bizin, ta iŋgi ikam ma iur ŋonoono piti kek.\x + \xo 13:32 \xt Un 12:3; Ro 1:2, 4:16\x*
\v 33 Pa ni ipei Yesu ma imaŋga pa naala kek. Ka sua imbot la mboe suŋŋana kana ta iwe ru pa. Iso:
\q1 Nio lutuŋ ta nu na.
\q1 Koozi nio aŋwe tomom.\x + \xo 13:33 \xt Mbo 2:7; Mt 3:17; Ibr 5:5\x*
\b
\p 
\v 34 “Tana Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga mini kek. Mi ko irao imeete ma isula mini naala be ibuuzu na som. Ka sua imbot pataaŋa kek ta kembei:
\q1 Nio aŋbuk sua mbolŋana pa Dabit be aŋkampe i pa koroŋ matakiŋa ta ndabokbokŋan mi potomŋan. Mi koroŋ ta boozomen tana, nio kola aŋkam piom.\x + \xo 13:34 \xt Yesa 55:3\x*
\m 
\v 35 “Mi sua lwoono toro iso ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 Nu ko irao zem mbesooŋo ku potomŋana ma ibuuzu na som.\x + \xo 13:35 \xt Mbo 16:10; Ŋgo 2:27,31\x*
\b
\p 
\v 36 “Kere. Dabit, ni imbeeze pa Anutu mi ito ŋgar kini ma irao meeteŋana kini. To titwi i sula ki tumbuunu bizin ma ibuuzu.\x + \xo 13:36 \xt Ŋgo 2:29\x*
\v 37 Tamen ni tau Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga pa naala na, ni irao imeete mini ma ibuuzu na som.
\p 
\v 38-39 “Tana niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, keleŋ! Niam amso kat piom ta kembei: Yesu ta iwe zaala piti be Anutu ireege sanaana kiti. Tana tomtom sa isombe iurla kini, inako Anutu ire i kembei ni tomtom ndeeŋeŋana. Pa sanaana boozomen ta tutu ki Mose irao be iurpe som, mi ikam ti ma tasaana pa Anutu mataana na, Yesu, ni irao iurpe.\x + \xo 13:38-39 \xt Ŋgo 2:38; Ro 3:28; Ga 2:16; 1Yo 2:2,12\x*
\p 
\v 40 “Tana kere yom. Kokena kitit ulaaŋa ta iŋgi Anutu ikam piti, to mbulu ta Anutu kwoono bizin tiso pa na ipet piom. Ka sua imbot ta kembei:
\q1 
\v 41 Niom wal ta kerepiili sua ki Anutu na, kere yom!
\q1 Pa uraata popoŋana tabe aŋkam ma kere i, ko ipa ndel kat.
\q1 Tabe ipet pizin wal pakan mi keleŋ uruunu men, so kuurla som.
\q1 Tana niom ko kwoyom taanda pa mi kakam ŋgar pa ma som, mi kala leyom.”\x + \xo 13:41 \xt Hab 1:5\x*
\b
\p 
\v 42 Paulus iso sua ma imap, to ziru Panabas be tiyooto pa lupŋana muriini. Som mi timaŋga ma tiwi ziru beso aigule potomŋana toro ipet, to timiili mi tiso zin pa sua tana mini.
\v 43 Lupŋana imureege na, zin Yuda ŋonoono, mi wal pakan ta titooro zin ma tiwe Yuda i mi timarmar pa suŋŋana na, boozomen tito ziru ma ziŋan tila. Mi ziru tipombol zin be tikiskis kampeŋana mi muŋaiŋana ki Anutu.\x + \xo 13:43 \xt Ŋgo 11:23, 14:22\x*
\p 
\v 44 Timbot ma aigule potomŋana ipet mini, to kar kan timeke ma timap ma kar putuunu. Pa timar tilup zin be tileŋ sua ki Merere tau.
\v 45 Zin bibip kizin Yuda tire iwal biibi tana tila be tileŋ Paulus ziru Panabas, to matan mburmbur ma tau tisaana kat. Tana timaŋga mi ziŋan Paulus tiparzorzooro pa sua. Mi tiwirri sua repiiliŋan boozo pini.\x + \xo 13:45 \xt 1Tes 2:15+\x*
\p 
\v 46 Tamen Paulus ziru Panabas timoto som. Timender mbolŋana, mi kwon imbol kat ma tiso: “Ina som. Anutu isombe ipumuuŋgu sua kini piom. Tamen iŋgi niom kitit. Pa niom, ina motoyom iŋgal ituyom be kakam mbotŋana ki Anutu ta iseeŋge iseeŋge ma ila na som. Tana iŋgi ko aŋzem yom ma komboreyom, mi amla kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i.\x + \xo 13:46 \xt Mt 21:41; Ŋgo 3:26+, 18:6; Ro 1:16\x*
\v 47 Pa Merere iur sua piam kek ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 Nio aŋur u be la mi ur mat pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i.
\q1 Naso we zaala pa toono ta boozomen be tikam ulaaŋa tio.”\x + \xo 13:47 \xt Yesa 42:6, 49:6; Lu 2:32\x*
\p 
\v 48 Iŋgi sua ti ila ma zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i tileŋ, to lelen ambai kat pa Merere sua kini mi tipakurkur sua tana. Mi zin wal tau Anutu iroogo zin pataaŋa kek be tikam mbotŋana kini na, tiurla.\x + \xo 13:48 \xt Ro 8:29+\x*
\p 
\v 49 Tana Merere sua kini irak ma irao lele pakaana tina.
\v 50 Tamen zin bibip kizin Yuda timaŋga ma tipese zin bibip ki kar tana, ziŋan zin moori zanŋan pakan ta tigabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin. Tona timaŋga pa Paulus ziru Panabas ma tiseeze matan, mi tiser zin pa lele kizin ma tila len.\x + \xo 13:50 \xt 2Tim 3:11\x*
\v 51 Tana ziru titir ululu pa kumbun pizin bekena iwe kilalan pa sanaana kizin, mi tiwwa ma tila kar Ikonium.\x + \xo 13:51 \xt Mt 10:14\x*
\v 52 Mi zin wal ki kar Antiok ta titoto Yesu na, Bubuŋana Potomŋana izeebe zin lup, ma lelen ambai kat.\x + \xo 13:52 \xt Ŋgo 16:34; Ro 14:17; 1Pe 1:8\x*
\c 14
\s1 Paulus ziru Panabas tikam uraata su kar Ikonium
\p 
\v 1 Mbulu raraate men ta ipet su kar Ikonium. Paulus ziru Panabas tila tipet to, tilela lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda, mi tikam sua pizin. Mi sua kizin iŋgal tomtom boozomen ma tiurla ki Yesu. Zin Yuda, mi pakan ta Grik i tomini.
\p 
\v 2 Tamen zin Yuda ta tiurla som na, tikuru zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i lelen. Tabe lelen pizin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi mini som.
\v 3 Tana Paulus ziru Panabas timbot kar tana ma moloŋana ri, mi timender mbolŋana mi tizzoyaryaara Merere uruunu. Mi tipombolmbol sua pa kampeŋana kini. Mi Anutu ipombolmbol sua ta ziru tizzo na, mi ikamam len mburan. Tabe titortooro mos ma uraata bibip pakan ma iwedet. \x + \xo 14:3 \xt Mk 16:20; Ŋgo 5:12; 2Kor 12:12\x*
\v 4 Tana iwal biibi ki kar tana tisu to tiwe ru. Pakaana tilae kizin Yuda, mi pakaana tiyo se ki ŋgoŋana ru tana. \x + \xo 14:4 \xt Lu 12:51+; Ŋgo 28:25\x*
\p 
\v 5 To zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mi Yuda pakan, ziŋan zin bibip kizin tilup lelen be tipasaana ziru, mibe tipun zin pa pat. \x + \xo 14:5 \xt 2Tim 3:11\x*
\v 6 Mi Paulus ziru Panabas talŋan ikam sua ti, to tiko ma tila pa lele pakaana ki Likonia mi timbot kar Listara mi kar Derbe. Mi tilalae pa kar munmun ta timbot kolouŋana na tomini, \x + \xo 14:6 \xt Mt 10:23\x*
\v 7 mi tizzoyaryaara uruunu ambaiŋana pizin.
\s1 Mbulu ta ipet su kar Listara mi kar Derbe
\p 
\v 8 Tomtom kumbuunu sananŋana ta, imbotmbot kar Listara. Irao ipa na som. Ni ta kembeaŋana, mi naana ikami ma isu.
\v 9 Paulus izzo sua na, ni imbutultul mi ileŋleŋ. To Paulus igeede la pini, mi ire kembei ni iurla ma Anutu irao iurpe i. \x + \xo 14:9 \xt Mt 9:28+\x*
\v 10 Tana kalŋaana biibi ma iso: “Ai, nu tana, burup ma maŋga mender.” Tomtom tana inaunau som. Burup ma imaŋga mi iwwa pataaŋa. \x + \xo 14:10 \xt Mk 2:11; Ŋgo 3:6, 9:34, 28:8+; Yems 5:14+\x*
\p 
\v 11 Zin iwal biibi ki lele pakaana ki Likonia na, tire Paulus ikam uraata tana, to kalŋan isala mi tiso la zitun kalŋan ma tiso: “Wai. Iŋgi zin merere kiti, ta tisu ma tiwe tomtom i.” \x + \xo 14:11 \xt Ŋgo 28:6\x*
\v 12 Tona tiboobo merere kizin Grik zaana Zeus, \f + \fr 14:12 \ft Zin Grik, merere kizin boozo. Zin tiurla ta kembei. Zeus, ni merere biibi kat ta ilip pizin merere kizin ta boozomen. Mi Ermes, ni merere toro ta iwe Zeus kwoono mi izzo zin tomtom pa sua kini.\f* ise ki Panabas. Mi Paulus na, tiboobo Ermes zaana pini. Pa Paulus ta imuŋmuuŋgu pa sua.
\v 13 Kar tana zilŋaana na, merere pakaamŋana Zeus urum kini imbotmbot. Tana patoronŋana ka tomtom ta ki urum tina, ni ziŋan zin iwal tikam mbili pakan mi aigau ma timar zaala kwoono be tikam patoronŋana pa Panabas ziru Paulus.
\p 
\v 14 Tamen ziru tikilaala mbulu ta iŋgi be ipet i, to tiraaza mburu kizin, mi wis ma tilela ta iwal biibi lelen.
\v 15 Mi kalŋan biibi ma tiso: “Wai, iŋgi parei ta koso kakam piam ta kembei? Niamru ti, tomtom kembei ta niom na. Iti raraate men tau. Niamru amar be amsoyaara uruunu ambaiŋana piom. Merere tiom soroksorok na, kezem zin ma timboren. Mi kuur leleyom ila ki Anutu ŋonoono ta mata yaryaaraŋana na. Pa ni ta iur saamba, iur toono, iur tai, mi koroŋ boozomen ta timbotmbot pa. \x + \xo 14:15 \xt Un 1:1+; Ŋgo 10:26; 1Kor 8:4; 1Tes 1:9\x*
\v 16 Muŋgu, ni izem zin tomtom ma tiwwa ma tikamam mbulu irao zitun lelen mi ŋgar kizin. \x + \xo 14:16 \xt Mbo 81:12; Ŋgo 17:30; 1Pe 4:3\x*
\v 17 Tamen ni ikewe piti som. Pa ikamam koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan ma imarmar ta gorgori. Ikamam leyom yaŋ ta imbot saamba mi isu, mi iurur gorgor ki mai pa koroŋ ta boozomen. Mi ikamam koyom kini boozo bekena leleyom ndabok, mi menmeen yom pa. Mbulu kini boozomen tana izzwe kembei ni imbotmbot.” \x + \xo 14:17 \xt Mbo 104:27+, 147:8; Mt 5:45; Ŋgo 17:27; Ro 1:20\x*
\v 18 Sua tiŋgi, ziru tiso paso, zin iwal biibi tana ŋgar kizin imbol be tikam patoronŋana sa pa ziru. Mi rimen mi tikam. Tamen ziru tipetekewe zin, tabe tikam som.
\p 
\v 19 To zin Yuda pakan ta timbot kar Ikonium mi kar Antiok ta ki Pisidia na, timar. Timar ma tikuru zin iwal lelen be tizem Paulus bizin mi tilae kizin. To timaŋga na tipun Paulus pa pat, mi tiyaaru tataati ma tila kar zilŋaana. Pa tiso ko imeete kek. \x + \xo 14:19 \xt 2Kor 4:9, 11:25; Ga 6:17; 2Tim 3:11\x*
\v 20 Tamen waene bizin ta titoto Yesu i, tila tiliu i, to ni imaŋga mi ziŋan timiili ma tilela kar mini. Tikeene ma aigule toro to, ziru Panabas timaŋga mi tila pa kar Derbe.
\s1 Ziru timiili pa kar Antiok ta ki Siria na
\p 
\v 21 Paulus ziru Panabas tipet kar Derbe to tizzo uruunu ambaiŋana isu tana. Tikam ma tomtom boozo tiurla mi lelen be tito Yesu. To timiili ma tila kar Listara, to tila kar Ikonium. Mana tila kar Antiok ta ki Pisidia na.
\v 22 Mi tipombolmbol zin wal ta titoto Yesu i mi kwon imbol pizin be tikis kat urlaŋana kizin. Mi tiso pizin ta kembei: “Bela temender mbolŋana mi tabaada pataŋana boozo, to tombot lela peeze ki Anutu mi tala kar kini.” \x + \xo 14:22 \xt Mt 7:14, 16:24; Ŋgo 11:23; 1Tes 3:3+; 2Tim 3:12\x*
\v 23 Ziru tiwwa na, tiurur zin tomtom ma tiwe mboroŋan be tikam peeze pa lupŋana ki Krisi ikot kar tataŋa. Mi tiŋgalseksek zitun pa kini kanŋana mi tizuŋzuŋ, mi tiur zin ila Merere, ta zin tiurla kini i, namaana. To tizem zin. \x + \xo 14:23 \xt Ŋgo 6:6, 13:1+; Tit 1:5\x*
\p 
\v 24 Tipa pa lele pakaana ki Pisidia ma imap. To tila tipet lele pakaana ki Pampilia.
\v 25 Tiso uruunu ambaiŋana isu kar Perga, mana tisula kar Atalia.
\v 26 To tikam wooŋgo su tina, mi tikwai ma timiili ma tila mini kar Antiok. Pa zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi ta timbot kar tana, ta muŋgu tiur Paulus ziru Panabas pa uraata, mi tisuŋ Anutu be ikampe zin mi mataana pizin. Mi iŋgi tila ma tikam uraata ma imap, ta timiili ma timar mini i. \x + \xo 14:26 \xt Ŋgo 13:1+\x*
\p 
\v 27 Tana timar tipet kar Antiok, to ziŋan lupŋana ki Krisi tilup zin mi tiwidit mbol pa uraata ta Anutu ipombol zin pa ma tikam na. Mi tiso pizin ta kembei: Anutu, ni ikaaga kataama pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mi zin tiurla kek.
\v 28 Mi ziŋan waen bizin ta titoto Yesu i ta ki kar tana timbel mbotŋana.
\c 15
\s1 Wal pakan kwon imbol pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i be tito tutu ki Mose
\p 
\v 1 To tomtom pakan timbot Yudea mi tisula kar Antiok. Mi timaŋga ma tizzo pizin toŋmatiziŋ ta ki Krisi i ta kembei. Tiso: “Ai, niom wal ta Yuda somŋoyom i, bela koto tutu mi mbulu ta Mose iur na, mi tireete yom, tona Anutu ikamke yom. Mi sombe koto som, inako Anutu ikamke yom som.”
\v 2 Paulus ziru Panabas tileŋ sua tana na, keten malmal pa. Tabe ziŋan tiparzooro. Timbel sua soŋana. To tilup lelen, mi tiur Paulus ziru Panabas mi waen bizin pakan ta ki Antiok na be tisala Yerusalem, mi tire zin ŋgoŋana pakan ziŋan zin mboroŋan, mi tiurpe pataŋana ti.\x + \xo 15:2 \xt Ga 3:5,10, 5:2+; Pil 3:2+; Kol 2:16+\x*
\p 
\v 3 Tana lupŋana ki Krisi iurpe zaala pizin, mi tiur zin ma tila. Tiwwa pa lele pakaana ki Ponisia ma Samaria, mi tizzotartaara zin toŋmatiziŋ ta timbot tana ta kembei: Wal boozomen ta Yuda somŋan i, titooro lelen mi tiurla ki Merere kek. Tana waen bizin tileŋ ma lelen ambai kat.\x + \xo 15:3 \xt Ŋgo 11:18, 14:27\x*
\v 4 Tila tipet Yerusalem, to lupŋana ki Krisi ziŋan zin ŋgoŋana mi mboroŋan lelen ambai pizin mi tikam zin ma tila ruumu kizin. Mi zin tipit mbol pa uraata ta Anutu ipombol zin pa ma tikam na, mi waen bizin tana tileŋ.
\p 
\v 5 To zin tutu kan pakan tau tiurla ki Krisi na, timaŋga mi tiso: “Som. Ina kembena pepe. Zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i, sombe tiurla ki Krisi, na bela tereete zin mi tuur sua pizin be tito tutu ki Mose, tona ambai.”
\s1 Lupŋana biibi ta ipet su Yerusalem mi iur zaala pizin wal tau Yuda somŋan i
\p 
\v 6 Tabe zin ŋgoŋana mi mboroŋan tilup zin, mi titiiri sua taiŋgi.
\v 7 Tinok sua ma molo, mana kaimer to Petrus imaŋga mi iso: “O atoŋan mi tiziŋan, niom kuute. Anutu, ni ipei kat yo la mazwoyom ta alok kek, mi iŋgo yo ma aŋla kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i bekena aŋkam uruunu ambaiŋana pizin. Mi zin tileŋ na tiurla.\x + \xo 15:7 \xt Mt 16:19; Ŋgo 10:9-44, 11:18\x*
\v 8 Mi Anutu, ni iute iti tomtom lelende lup kek. Tanata ikam Bubuŋana Potomŋana pizin raraate kembei ta muŋgu ikam piti na, bekena iswe kembei ni leleene ambai pizin tomini.\x + \xo 15:8 \xt Ŋgo 10:43+\x*
\v 9 Mbulu ta ni ikam piti mi zin, ina raraate men. Ikam ndelndelŋa som. Pa urlaŋana kizin ta ikam ma Anutu ipus zin ma lelen iŋgeeze.\x + \xo 15:9 \xt Ŋgo 10:43; Ro 10:9+\x*
\v 10 Mi iŋgi parei ta kusu mi koso kuur pataŋana ise kizin wal popoŋan ta titoto Yesu i? Niom kere. Tumbundu bizin ta muŋgu muŋgu mi imar ma isu kiti i, iti tarao be toto kat tutu? Som. Tana kere yom. Kokena kozooro Anutu ŋgar kini, to kapamalmal keteene.\x + \xo 15:10 \xt Lu 11:46; Ga 3:10\x*
\v 11 Ina som. Pa iti tuurla ta kembei: Muŋaiŋana ki Merere Yesu ta ikamke iti. Koroŋ toro sa som. Mi zin ta kembena tomini.”\x + \xo 15:11 \xt Ro 3:24,28; Ga 2:16; Ep 2:5+; Tit 3:4\x*
\p 
\v 12 Wal tana tileŋ, mi timap timaane men. To tiŋgun talŋan pa Panabas ziru Paulus. Pa ziru tiwidit mbol pa mos pakan mi uraata bibip ta Anutu ipombol zin pa ma tikam la zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mazwan na.
\v 13 Tiso makiŋ, to Yems imaŋga mi iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, keleŋ sua tio ti!
\v 14 Merere, ni mataana iŋgalŋgal zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i, mi leleene be ikam zin tomini ma tiwe wal kini bekena tipakur zaana. Sua tiŋgi popoŋana piti som. Indeeŋe ta Simon ila mi ikam sua pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i na, Anutu ikaaga zaala pizin. Ka sua ta ni ila leleene pa kat ma teleŋ kek.\x + \xo 15:14 \xt Ŋgo 15:7+\x*
\v 15 Mi Anutu kwoono bizin tiso sua tamen tau. Pa tibeede sua ta kembei:
\q1 
\v 16 Kaimer to aŋmiili mini.
\q1 Toinabe aŋurpe ruumu ki Dabit ta borok su lene na,
\q1 mi aŋpamender mini.\x + \xo 15:16 \xt Amos 9:11+\x*
\q1 
\v 17 Naso ipei ŋgar kizin tomtom pakan.
\q1 To wal boozomen tau Yuda somŋan ta aŋroogo zin kek be tiwe leŋ, nako tikam kinkiini be tiute yo.
\q1 
\v 18 Sua tiŋgi na, Merere kalŋaana. Itunu iswe ta muŋgu kek.”\x + \xo 15:18 \xt Yesa 45:21\x*
\p 
\v 19 To Yems iso seeŋge. Iso: “Tana nio aŋre ta kembei: Zin wal tau Yuda somŋan mi iŋgi titooro lelen ma tiurla ki Merere i, iti irao tuur pataŋana biibi ise kizin sorok pepe.
\v 20 Miso kembena, na iti bela tebeede ro tasa ila, mi tosotaara zin pa tutu iŋgoi tabe tito i. Tutu ta kembei: Kini ta tipakur zin merere pakaamŋan pa i, na zin irao tikan pepe. Mi siŋ mi buzur siŋŋana ta kembena, irao tikan pepe. Mi tiyaraama zitun: Kokena timolo ula ka tutu.\x + \xo 15:20 \xt Un 9:4; Kam 20:3+; 1Kor 6:18, 8:7+, 10:14+; Ga 5:19+; Ep 5:3; 1Tes 4:3\x*
\v 21 Pa ta muŋgu mi imar na, tutu ki Mose ka tomtom bizin tirao karkari lup. Mi aigule potomŋana ta boozomen na, tiwatwaata tutu tana ilela lupŋana murin kizin Yuda.”
\s1 Ro ta tibeede pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i
\p 
\v 22 To zin ŋgoŋana ziŋan zin mboroŋan mi waen bizin ta boozomen ta timbot lupŋana tana, tilup lelen mi ŋgar kizin, mi tiur tomtom kizin pakan be tiwe kwon, mibe tigaaba Paulus mi Panabas ma ziŋan tisula pa Antiok. Tana tiur Yudas ta zaana toro Barsabas na, mi Silas. Pa ni ziru ta zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi matan ise kizin.
\v 23 Mi tiur ro ila kizin be tikam ma tila. Ro tana, tibeede sua ta kembei ise:
\p “Niam ŋgoŋana niamŋan zin mboroŋan amkam aigule tiam ima piom toŋmatiziŋ tiam ta kombot Antiok, mi Siria, mi Silisia na. Niom ta Yuda som mi kuurla i.
\p 
\v 24 “Niam taiŋgi amleŋ kembei tomtom tiam pakan tima, mi tiso sua pakan ta ikam yom ma leleyom ipata mi kakam ŋgar boozo. Tamen wal tana, niam amgo zin som.
\v 25 Tanata amlup yam, mi niam ta boozomen amyok raraate men be amur tomtom tiam pakan ma tiwe kwoyam, mi amgo zin ma tima i. Mi Panabas ziru Paulus, tomtom kiti ru ta leleyam pizin kat na, ko ziŋan tima.
\v 26 Ziru tana tizem kat zitun pa uraata ki Merere kiti Yesu Krisi, mi tiurur zitun ila zaaba kwoono pa ni zaana.\x + \xo 15:26 \xt Ŋgo 9:23+, 14:19; 1Kor 15:30\x*
\v 27 Tana niam iŋgi amgo Yudas ma Silas be tikam ro ti ma tima. Mi ziru ko tiso pa kwon tomini.
\v 28 Niam taiŋgi, Bubuŋana Potomŋana ta ikam peeze piam mi amyok raraate ta kembei: Niam ko irao amur tutu boozo piom na som. Kokena amkam pataŋana piom. Mi tutu ta tiŋgi:
\v 29 Kini ta tipakur zin merere pakaamŋan pa i, na kakan pepe. Mi siŋ mi buzur siŋŋana ta kembena, kakan pepe. Mi komolo ula ka tutu pepe. Tana sombe kagabiizi ituyom kat pa mbulu ta kembei, na niom ko kakam kat mbulu. Sua ta tana. Ambai. Amzem su ti.”\x + \xo 15:29 \xt Tur 2:14, 20\x*
\s1 Zin Antiok kan lelen ambai pa ro kizin Yerusalem kan
\p 
\v 30 Zin tomtom ta tiŋgo zin i, tisula ma tipet kar Antiok, to ziŋan zin toŋmatiziŋ tana tilup zin mi tiur ro tana ila kizin.
\v 31 Beso tipaata mi tileŋ sua pombolŋana tiŋgi na, lelen ambai kat mi menmeen zin pa.
\v 32 Yudas mi Silas, ziru Merere kwoono bizin. Tana tikam sua boozomen pizin Antiok kan bekena tipombol zin ma timender mbolŋana.
\v 33 Ziŋan timbot pa mazwaana ri, mana kaimer to, zin Antiok kan tiur zin raama lelen ambai, mi timiili ma tisala mini kizin wal ta tiŋgo zin na. [
\v 34 Tamen Silas leleene be imiili som. Tabe ziŋan timbotmbot ta tina.]
\p 
\v 35 Mi Paulus ziru Panabas na, timbotmbot su Antiok ma moloŋana ri. Mi ziŋan waen bizin boozomen tiparluplup zin, mi tikamam sua ki Merere pizin mi tipaute zin pa.
\s1 Paulus ziru Panabas tiparzem zin
\p 
\v 36 Timbotmbot ma Paulus isu to iso pa Panabas. Iso: “Ouo, ituru timiili ma tapa pa karkari, mi tolou waende bizin ta muŋgu tosoyaara sua ki Merere pizin na. Timbot ambai, som som?”
\v 37 Mi Panabas, ni leleene be ikam Yoan Markus ma ziŋan tila.\x + \xo 15:37 \xt Ŋgo 13:5; Kol 4:10; 2Tim 4:11; 1Pe 5:13\x*
\v 38 Tamen Paulus itiiri na, ambai be tikami som. Pa kena so pai mataana kana i ziŋan tipa pa sua, mi tila tila ma uraata imap, so ambai. Mi ina som. Pa indeeŋe ta zin tila Pampilia mi timaŋga be tipa pa sua na, Yoan Markus izem zin, mi ila lene.\x + \xo 15:38 \xt Ŋgo 13:13\x*
\p 
\v 39 Tana ziru tisu ma keten malmal mi tiparzooro pa. Tabe tiparzem zin. Panabas isu na karau pa Markus, to ziru tikam wooŋgo, mi tikwai ma tila pa mutu Saiprus.
\v 40 Mi Paulus, ni ikam Silas. Tana zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi tiur zin la Merere namaana, mi tisuŋ Merere be ikampe zin mi mataana pizin,\x + \xo 15:40 \xt Ŋgo 13:3\x*
\v 41 to Paulus ziru Silas timaŋga ma tila mi tiwwa pa lele pakaana ki Siria ma Silisia, mi Paulus ipombolmbol lupŋana ki Krisi ta timbot lele tana.
\c 16
\s1 Timoti ila ma igaaba Paulus ziru Silas
\p 
\v 1 Paulus ziru Silas tiwwa ma tila tipet kar Derbe, to tila pa kar Listara. Kar tana, naŋgaŋ ta tau itoto Yesu i, ni imbotmbot. Zaana Timoti. Naana, ni Yuda nan. Mi iurla ki Krisi. Mi tamaana na, ni Grik. \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Ŋgo 14:6+; 1Kor 4:17, 16:10; 2Kor 1:19; Pil 2:19+; 1Tim 1:2; 2Tim 1:2\x*
\v 2 Zin toŋmatiziŋ ki Krisi ta timbot kar Listara mi kar Ikonium na, timap tiwidit Timoti uruunu.
\v 3 Tana Paulus leleene be ikami ma ila igaabi ma ziŋan tila pa uraata. Tana iso mi tireeti. Ikam ta kembei paso, zin Yuda boozomen ta timbotmbot lele tana na, zin tiute Timoti tamaana ni Grik. Kokena tiyo kwon pini. \x + \xo 16:3 \xt 1Kor 9:20\x*
\p 
\v 4 Tona Paulus bizin timaŋga mini pa pai. Mi tila ma tiwwa pa kar ta boozomen, mi tizzotartaara waen bizin pa sua kizin ŋgoŋana mi mboroŋan ta timbot Yerusalem na. Mi tipombol zin be tito zin tutu ta zin Yerusalem kan timbol pa. \x + \xo 16:4 \xt Ŋgo 15:28+\x*
\p 
\v 5 Tana zin lupŋana ki Krisi, urlaŋana kizin izze be imbol kat. Mi aigule ta boozomen tomtom popoŋan tiwedet mi tikanan la sua kizin. Tabe timasak ma tiwe boozo. \x + \xo 16:5 \xt Ŋgo 2:42+, 4:32+\x*
\s1 Merere iboobo Paulus be ila mi isoyaara uruunu ambaiŋana pizin Masedonia kan
\p 
\v 6 Paulus bizin tipa pa lele pakan ki Pirigia mi Galesia. Mi tila lele pakaana ki Asia som. Pa Bubuŋana Potomŋana ipeteke zin be tikam sua pizin Asia kan pepe.
\v 7 Tiwwa ma tipet lele pakaana ki Misia, to tiso tilae pa lele pakaana ki Bitinia. Tamen Yesu Bubuŋana iyok pizin som.
\v 8 Tana tipa pa lele pakaana ki Misia men, mi tisula tipet kar Troas.
\p 
\v 9 Mbeŋ ta na, Paulus ikeenetondo, mi ire tomtom ta ki lele pakaana ki Masedonia imendernder. Mi tomtom tana itaŋroro i ma iso: “Nu tana kozo mar ta Masedonia i be uulu yam.”
\v 10 Paulus ikeenetondo makiŋ, to niamŋan \f + \fr 16:10 \ft Sua “niamŋan” ti iswe ta kembei: Indeeŋe Paulus bizin timbot Troas na, Lukas ila igaaba zin.\f* Paulus amaŋga ma kaŋkaŋ pataaŋa be amla pa Masedonia. \f + \fr 16:10 \ft Masedonia, ina lele pakaana ta ki Yurop. Tana indeeŋe Paulus ila ma ikam sua pizin, ina mazwaana mataana kana ta uruunu ambaiŋana ila pa zin Yurop kan.\f* Paso, amkilaala mbulu boozomen ta ipet na ta kembei: Iŋgi Merere iboobo yam be amsoyaara uruunu ambaiŋana pizin wal ta timbot lele pakaana tana.
\s1 Paulus bizin tila kar Pilipai
\p 
\v 11 Niam amse wooŋgo mi le isala, to amzem Troas mi amyembut ma amla mutu Samotaras. Be kozeere mini na, amla sor lela Neapolis.
\v 12 To ampa toono mi amlela ta kar Pilipai. Pilipai, ina kar biibi ta ki lele pakaana ki Masedonia. Mi zin Rom kan ta tiur kar tina. Amla to ambot pa aigule pakan.
\p 
\v 13 Indeeŋe aigule potomŋana kizin Yuda be keten su, to amzem kar biibi, mi amla ta yok kezeene a. Pa ina lele ta zin Yuda tiluplup su pa i be tisuŋ. To mbuleyam su mi amkamam sua pizin moori pakan ta tilup zin su tana.
\v 14 Zin moori tana, kizin ta zaana Lidia. Ni moori ki kar Tiatira. Mi uraata kini ta iŋgomonmoono mburu ta kan mos totoŋan mi ambaimbaiŋan kat. Ni Yuda som. Mi iurla ki Anutu, mi igabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin. Ileŋleŋ sua ki Paulus na, Merere ikam uraata pa leleene ma iurla. \x + \xo 16:14 \xt Lu 24:45; Yo 6:44; Ŋgo 13:48; 2Tes 2:13+\x*
\v 15 Tana ziŋan wal kini ta timbot ruumu kini na, timap ma tikam yok. Mana iso piam. Iso: “Niom sombe kere kembei aŋurla kat ki Merere, na kamar tala ruumu tio.” Itunu imaŋmaŋ yam, to niamŋan amla ruumu kini. \x + \xo 16:15 \xt Ŋgo 16:33, 18:8; 1Kor 1:16\x*
\s1 Tiur Paulus ziru Silas lela ruumu sanaana
\p 
\v 16 Indeeŋe aigule ta na, niam amsombe amla mini pa suŋŋana muriini tana. Tana amla na amse ki moori ta ni mbesooŋo sorok. Moori tana, ni irao iswe koroŋ turkeŋan pakan. Pa bubuŋana sananŋana iru pini tau. Mi pat ta ni ikamam pa uraata kini tana na, sorok som. Mi pat tana, ni ikamam mi iurur la kizin bibip kini.
\v 17 Moori tana ire yam, to itokelkeele yam, mi iboboobo ma iso: “Ai, kere. Wal ti, zin mbesooŋo ki Anutu kor kana kat. Iŋgi timar be tiso yom pa zaala tabe Anutu ikamke yom pa i.” \x + \xo 16:17 \xt Mk 1:24,34\x*
\v 18 Inoknok ta kembei pa aigule boozoŋana ri. Tabe Paulus ileŋ ileŋ ma keteene malmal, to itoori mi iŋasaara bubuŋana sananŋana tana. Iso: “Hai! Nio aŋur sua pu pa Yesu Krisi zaana. Zem moori tina mi yooto ta buri.” To bubuŋana sananŋana iko pa moori pataaŋa. \x + \xo 16:18 \xt Mk 16:17; Ŋgo 5:16, 8:7\x*
\p 
\v 19 To zin bibip ki moori tana keten malmal kat pa Paulus ziru Silas. Pa tire kembei zaala kizin ta tikamam pat pa i, ina imun kek. Tana tikam zin, mi tiyaaru tataata zin ma tila kar keteene be tipamender zin ila zin bibip matan. \x + \xo 16:19 \xt Ŋgo 19:25+\x*
\v 20 Tikam zin ma tila zin peeze kan keren uunu, to tiŋgal sua pizin. Tiso: “Wal tiŋgi, zin Yuda. Mi timar kar kiti ma tikamam mbulu boozo ta ipasaana mboti ki kar. \x + \xo 16:20 \xt Ŋgo 17:6\x*
\v 21 Mi timolo tutu kiti tomini. Pa tipesese zin tomtom be tikam mbulu pakan ta iti Rom kanda irao takam som.”
\p 
\v 22 Iwal biibi tileŋ sua tana to, tigaaba zin mi tiŋa ziru. Zin peeze kan timaŋga na tiso ma tiraaza mburu kizin be tibalis zin.
\v 23 Tona tikam teene mi tibalis zin ma ruŋgun isaana kat. Mana tila tipiri zin lela ruumu sanaana. Mi tiur sua pa menderŋana ta imborro kataama i ta kembei: Sombe ikotkaala kataama, na bela namaana tuŋ pa. \x + \xo 16:23 \xt 2Kor 6:5, 11:23+; 1Tes 2:2\x*
\v 24 Ni ileŋ, to ikam zin mi ipiri zin lela ruumu leleene kat. Mi kumbun ma naman tiloondo pa ke patanpatan ta bibip i, mi tipoŋgeere.
\p 
\v 25 Indeeŋe mbeŋ lukutuunu na, Paulus ziru Silas tizuŋzuŋ mi timbombo mboe pa Anutu. Mi wal pakan ta ziŋan timbotmbot lela ruumu sanaana na, tiŋgun talŋan mi tileŋleŋ zin. \x + \xo 16:25 \xt Mbo 119:62; Ep 5:19\x*
\v 26 Molo som na, toono ikam kat. Yeŋyeeŋge biibi kat itok ruumu sanaana ma ka kataama ta boozomen tikaaga lup. Mi re ma koroŋ ta tiwwo zin pa na, titoptop lup pa naman ma kumbun. \x + \xo 16:26 \xt Ŋgo 5:19, 12:7+\x*
\v 27 Menderŋana ta imborro zin i, ikenne. Beso burup ma imaŋga be mataana ila na, kataama ta munŋaana men, ta kakaagaŋan men. Tana iso ko zin tomtom tiko ma tila len lup kek. Tabe ŋgelbuk ikami, to ipas buza kini, mi iso ikuruumu itunu ma kup.
\v 28 Tamen Paulus loŋa kalŋaana biibi ma iso pini. Iso: “Ai! Pasaana itum pepe. Niam munŋoyam ta ambotmbot i.”
\p 
\v 29 To menderŋana tina iso ma tikam kai imar bekena lele mat. Mi wis ma ila kizin, to itop su Paulus ma Silas kumbun uunu. Pa motoŋana biibi ikami tau.
\v 30 Mana ikam zin ma tiyooto, mi iwi zin. Iso: “Bibip tio, iŋgi ko aŋkam parei mi Anutu ikamke yo ma aŋbot ndabok?” \x + \xo 16:30 \xt Lu 3:10, 10:25; Ŋgo 2:37\x*
\p 
\v 31 Ziru tiso pini. Tiso: “Urla ki Merere Yesu. Naso ni ikamke u mi zin wal ta niomŋan kombot ruumu ku na tomini.” \x + \xo 16:31 \xt Yo 3:16,36, 6:47; 1Yo 5:10+\x*
\v 32 To ziru tikam sua ki Merere pini mi wal boozomen ta ni ziŋan timbot ruumu kini na.
\v 33 Mbeŋ tamen ta tina, ni ikam ziru mi iŋguuru zaaba kwon murinmurin, mi ni ziŋan wal kini ta boozomen tikam yok. \x + \xo 16:33 \xt Ŋgo 2:41, 16:15, 18:8; 1Kor 1:16\x*
\v 34 To ikam Paulus ziru Silas ma tisala tikan kini ta ruumu kini. Mi ni menmeeni kat. Paso, ziŋan wal kini, ta iŋgi tiurla ki Anutu i. \x + \xo 16:34 \xt Ŋgo 13:52; Ro 14:17; Ga 5:22; 1Pe 1:8\x*
\p 
\v 35 Aigule toro, zoŋ ise na, zin bibip ki kar tiŋgo menderŋan pakan ma tila ruumu sanaana mi tiso: “Wal ru tina, kozo zem zin ma tila len.”
\p 
\v 36 To menderŋana ta imborro kataama i, ila ma isotaara Paulus pa sua tana. Iso: “Zin bibip tiso mar ta kembei: Niomru Silas irao kala leyom. Tana iŋgi aŋzem yom i. Niomru kala raama leleyom ambai!”
\p 
\v 37 Tamen Paulus iso pizin menderŋan ta timar na ma iso: “Na na som. Zin bibip tina timolo tutu ki Rom kek. Pa niamru ti, tomtom ki Rom. Mi zin titiiri kat uunu tiam som, mi tibalis yam sorok ila iwal biibi matan. To tipiri yam sorok ilela ruumu sanaana. Mi iŋgi tisu mini ma tiso tiser yam ki keŋana? Irao amleŋ zin na som. Bela zitun timar ta ti, mi tikam yam ma amla.” \x + \xo 16:37 \xt Ŋgo 22:25\x*
\p 
\v 38 To zin menderŋan tila mi tisotaara zin bibip pa sua ki Paulus. Beso tileŋ kembei Paulus ziru Silas, zin tomtom ki Rom, to timoto kan.
\v 39 Tana zitun tila ma ziŋan tiurpe lelen, tona tikam ziru ma tiyooto, mi tiwi zin be tizem kar tana.
\p 
\v 40 Ziru tizem ruumu sanaana mi tila, to kaŋkaŋ pa ruumu ki Lidia. Tila tina to, tindeeŋe toŋmatiziŋ pakan ta ki Krisi i. Mi tipombol zin pa sua pakan, tona tizem zin ma timbot, mi ziru tila len.
\c 17
\s1 Paulus ziru Silas tila ta Tesalonika a
\p 
\v 1 Paulus ziru Silas tipa ma tila pa kar Ampipolis ma kar Apolonia, to tizem mi tila kar Tesalonika. Mi kar tina, lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda ta imbotmbot.
\v 2 Tana Paulus ito mbulu kini, mi ikoŋuru lupŋana muriini tana. Ni imbotmbot kar tina pa wik tel. Mi aigule potomŋan ta boozomen tau zin Yuda keten su pa i, na ni ilelala lupŋana muriini kizin, mi ikamam mos pa Anutu sua kini, mi itomtoombo be ipei ŋgar kizin.
\v 3 Ziŋan wal kar kan tizzo sua, mi ni iwesweeze kat sua ki Anutu ta iso pa Mesia bela ire yoyouŋana mi imeete, to imaŋga mini pa naala. Mi iso sua tana iur ŋonoono se ki Yesu. Tana iso pizin mi iso: “Keleŋ. Yesu ta aŋzzo yom pini i, ni Mesia tau.” \x + \xo 17:3 \xt Lu 24:26,45+; Ŋgo 3:18, 18:28\x*
\v 4 Tomtom kizin pakan tileŋ sua tiŋgi na, tire kembei sua ŋonoono. Tana tila ma tigaaba Paulus ziru Silas. Mi zin iwal biibi ki Grik ta tiurla ki Anutu mi tigabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin i, ziŋan zin moori zanŋan pakan, ta tila tigaaba zin tomini.
\p 
\v 5 Tamen zin Yuda tire iwal biibi timokor la kizin, to matan mburmbur. Tana tila tiyo tomooto sananŋan pakan ta tiwwa len sorok i ma tilup zin, mi timaŋga be tikuru zin kar kan lelen. Be molo som na, orooro biibi isala. To wis ma tila Yason ruumu kini, be tiru Paulus ziru Silas. Beso tindeeŋe zin ma iŋgi, to tiso tikam zin ma tipamender zin ila iwal biibi matan. \x + \xo 17:5 \xt Ŋgo 13:45; Ro 16:21; 1Tes 2:2,16+\x*
\v 6-7 Tamen tila tiru zin ma som. To tiyaaru tataata Yason mi toŋmatiziŋ pakan ta ki Krisi i, mi tikam zin ma tila kizin peeze kan ki kar. Mi kalŋan izalla ma tiso: “Wal ta Yason ikam zin ma tila timbot ruumu kini na, tipa pa lele ta boozomen mi tipesese zin tomtom be tikam mbulu bozboozo. Mi iŋgi buri timar tipet kar kiti i. Wal tana tizorzooro tutu tau biibi itunu ŋonoono ki Rom iur na. Pa tisombe king toro imbotmbot tomini. Zaana Yesu.” \x + \xo 17:6-7 \xt Lu 23:2; Yo 19:12; Ŋgo 16:20\x*
\v 8 Iŋgi tipiri sua tiŋgi ila, to zin iwal biibi ziŋan zin peeze kan ki kar timaŋga ma tikam orooro biibi pa.
\v 9 Tona zin peeze kan tiso pa Yason ziŋan waene bizin ma tikam pat pakan ma ila imbot kizin bekena ipamoto zin. Beso tikam mbulu toro sa mini som, to pat kizin imiili. Tiŋgiimi makiŋ, mana zin peeze kan tizem zin ma tila.
\s1 Paulus ziru Silas tila kar Berea
\p 
\v 10 Timbot ma mbeŋ to, zin toŋmatiziŋ ta ki Krisi i karau men mi tiur Paulus ziru Silas ma tila pa kar Berea. Ziru tila tipet na, kaŋkaŋ ma tila pa lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda.
\v 11 Zin Yuda ki Berea na, ŋgar kizin ambaiŋana. Tiliplip pizin Tesalonika kan. Pa tiŋgun talŋan pa sua, mi lelen ilip be tikam kat ka uunu. Tana aigule ta boozomen tiwatwaata sua ki Anutu, mi titirtiiri sua ta Paulus izzo na: Ko sua kini ŋonoono, som som? \x + \xo 17:11 \xt Yo 5:39\x*
\v 12 Tabe zin Yuda boozo tiurla. Mi zin Grik nan ta zanŋan na, ziŋan tomooto pakan tiurla tomini.
\p 
\v 13 Beso zin Yuda ta ki kar Tesalonika tileŋ Paulus uruunu kembei ikamam Anutu sua kini isu kar Berea tomini na, timar be tikuru zin iwal lelen mi tipese zin.
\v 14 Tamen zin toŋmatiziŋ ta ki Krisi i loŋa men mi tiur Paulus ma ipera lene tai. Mi Silas ziru Timoti na, timbot men Berea.
\v 15 Zin tau tiur Paulus na, ziŋan tipa ma tila ta kar zaanaŋana Atens a. To Paulus iso pizin ta kembei: “Kimiili ma kala mini pa Berea, to koso pa Silas ma Timoti be loŋa timar.”
\s1 Paulus imbot kar biibi Atens
\p 
\v 16 Indeeŋe Paulus imbotmbot Atens mi inamnaama Silas ziru Timoti na, keteene malmal mi leleene ipata biibi kat. Pa irre la pa kar lene na, bok kat pa merere pakaamŋan kunun.
\v 17 Tana ni ilelala lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda, mi ziŋan zin Yuda mi wal pakan ta tiurla ki Anutu mi tigabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin na, tizzo sua. Mi aigule ta boozomen na, ziŋan zin wal ta timarmar pa nol muriini i tomini, ni ziŋan tizzo sua.
\p 
\v 18 Zin wal ŋgarŋan tau tipaute zin tomtom pa ŋgar bibip i, timbot la uunu ru. Ta, tipaata zin be Epikurean. Mi uunu toro na, tipaata zin be Stoik. Ina zin tomini ziŋan Paulus tiparzorzooro. To pakan timaŋga mi tiparso pizin ma tiso: “A, niom kere. To na, iyyo kwoono paso? Ina sa ileŋ la kizin wal pakan, ta izzo na.” Mi pakan tiso: “E-e, iŋgi ko isombe ikam ma tuurla kizin merere sorok ta kizin wal pakan.” Tiso ta kembei paso, Paulus izzo pa uruunu ambaiŋana ki Yesu mi maŋgaŋana kini tau.
\p 
\v 19 Tabe timaŋga mi titeege lae pini, to tikami ma tila pa lupŋana kizin biibi ta zaana Areopagus na. To tiso pini. Tiso: “Lak, niam leleyam be amkam kat sua ta nu zzo pa na.
\v 20 Pa koroŋ pakan ta amleŋ nu zzo i, ina popoŋana piam. Tana leleyam be nu so mini mi amkam kat ka uunu.”
\v 21 Pa zin tomtom ki Atens mi zin leembe ta timbotmbot tana na, re beso tileŋ sua popoŋana sa ta buri ipet i, na irao tilae timaare som. Timap ma kwon itekteege len mi timbombooren.
\s1 Mos ta Paulus ikam pizin Atens kan
\p 
\v 22 To Paulus imaŋga mi imender la lupŋana tana matan mi iso: “O niom tomtom ki Atens, nio aŋkilaala yom kembei niom kosombe kembeeze kat pizin merere ta boozomen.
\v 23 Pa aŋwwa pa kar lene ti, mi aŋrre zin koroŋ tau kuzuŋzuŋ pizin i na, aŋdeeŋe artaal ta. Mi bude ta imbot se i, ina iso ta kembei. Iso: ‘Merere ta niam amute zaana som, ta ampo artaal ti pini.’ Lak, Merere soŋana? Ni tau niom kuute i som mi kuzuŋzuŋ pini i, ta nio aŋzzoyaryaara uruunu piom i.
\p 
\v 24 “Ni Anutu ta iur toono mi koroŋ ta munŋaana men ta timbot pa. Saamba mi toono katuunu ta ni. Mi urum suŋŋana kana ta tomtom zitun tiwwo pa naman na, ni imbotmbot pa som. \x + \xo 17:24 \xt Un 1:1+; Ŋgo 7:48+, 14:15\x*
\v 25 Som ni iru sokorei bekena tomtom tikam pini? Som. Pa ni itunu, ta ikam ma tomtom ta boozomen matan yaryaaraŋan, mi ikam koroŋ ta munŋaana men pizin. \x + \xo 17:25 \xt Mbo 50:10+\x*
\v 26 Muŋgu kat, ni iur tomtom tamen ŋonoono. To tomtom tamen ŋonoono tina, ta tomtom ta boozomen un tipet pini, mi timasak ma tirao toono ta boozomen. Mi muŋgu kek, ni itunu ŋgar kini mi leleene iur pa lele pakaana boozomen tabe tomtom timbotmbot pa. Mi iur len mazwaana be timbot su toono kizin kizin. \x + \xo 17:26 \xt Un 2:7\x*
\v 27 Anutu ikam ta kembena bekena ipei ŋgar kizin tomtom ma tikam kinkiini be tiute i. Mi iti kembei tomtom mata pisŋana ta izoromrom kosa sa be ikam. Tamen Anutu, ni imbot molo pa tomtom sa som. \x + \xo 17:27 \xt Mbo 145:18; Ro 1:20\x*
\v 28 Pa pai kiti mi mboti kiti ta tombot su toono tiŋgi na, iti tombot se kini men tau. Mi ina kembei ta tomtom tiom mboe kan pakan tisombe: ‘Iti ta boozomen na, Ni lutuunu bizin.’ \x + \xo 17:28 \xt Kol 1:17; Ibr 1:3\x*
\p 
\v 29 “Tana sombe Anutu lutuunu bizin iti, na irao takam ŋgar ma toso ni kembei koroŋ kunun ta tomtom tiurpewe pa pat milmilŋan na som. Pa Anutu ŋonoono na, ni kembei merere soroksorok ta tomtom matan iur, mi zitun tikam mos pa naman keteene na som. \x + \xo 17:29 \xt Yesa 40:18+; Ro 1:22+; Ŋgo 19:26\x*
\p 
\v 30 “Ŋonoono, muŋgu zin tomtom kembei matan munŋan ma tiute i som. Tanata Anutu iŋgal matan pa sanaana kizin som. Mi koozi, ni iur sua pizin tomtom boozomen ta timbot irao lele ta munŋaana men be tizem kat mbulu kizin sananŋan mi titooro lelen. \x + \xo 17:30 \xt Lu 24:47; Ŋgo 14:16; Ro 3:25; Tit 2:11+\x*
\v 31 Pa ni itunu iur nol pataaŋa kek be itiiri iwal ta timap timbot su toono ti pa mbulu kizin mi iur kadoono pizin. Mi kadoono tabe ikam pizin i, ko indeeŋe men. Mi tomtom ta, Anutu iuri ma zaana imender pa uraata tana kek. Mi iwal ta munŋaana men tirao be tikilaali paso, ni, Anutu ipei i ma burup ma imaŋga pa naala kek.” \x + \xo 17:31 \xt Mbo 9:8, 96:13; Ŋgo 2:24, 10:42\x*
\p 
\v 32 Indeeŋe ta tileŋ Paulus kwoono la pa sua lwoono tau “burup ma imaŋga pa naala kek” na, tomtom kizin pakan tiseeŋge pini. Mi pakan na, tiso pini ma tiso: “Kozo kaimer to so sua tana mini ma amleŋ.”
\v 33 To Paulus izem zin mi ila.
\v 34 Mi tomtom pakan tiurla, tana tila tigaabi. Zin ta tito i ŋan na, kizin ta zaana Dionisis. Ni tomtom ki lupŋana biibi tana. Mi moori ta, zaana Damaris, ni iurla tomini. Mi zin pakan.
\c 18
\s1 Paulus ikam uraata su kar Korin
\p 
\v 1 To Paulus izem Atens mi ila kar Korin.
\v 2 Ila to indeeŋe Yuda ta. Zaana Akwila. Ni, naana ipeebi su lele pakaana ki Pontus. Mi waene zaana Prisila. Ziru timbot Itali mi timar. Pa Klodias, ta Kaisa ki Rom na, iur sua be zin Yuda ta timbotmbot kar biibi Rom na, timap ma tizem Rom mi tila len. \x + \xo 18:2 \xt Ro 16:3; 1Kor 16:19; 2Tim 4:19\x*
\v 3 Paulus ila be ire ziru, to ziŋan timbotmbot mi tikamam uraata pa mbili kulin ma koroŋ, be tisese ma iwe kembei ta sel. Pa uraata ta ziru waene tikamam, ina Paulus uraata kini tomini be ikam le pat. \x + \xo 18:3 \xt Ŋgo 20:34; 1Kor 4:12; 1Tes 2:9; 2Tes 3:7+\x*
\v 4 Mi aigule potomŋan ta munŋaana men tau zin Yuda keten su pa i na, Paulus ilelala lupŋana muriini kizin, mi ziŋan zin Yuda mi zin Grik tizzo sua. Pa iso ikam zin ma tiurla.
\p 
\v 5 Indeeŋe Silas ziru Timoti tizem Masedonia mi timar tipet na, Paulus izem uraata ta ikamam pa mbili kulin na, mi mataana iŋgalŋgal sua kamŋana men. Ni izzokatkat pizin Yuda ta kembei: Mesia kizin na Yesu tau.
\v 6 Tamen zin tizorzoori mi tiwirri sua sananŋan boozo pini. Tabe itir ululu pa mburu kini ma isu pizin, mi iso la nin. Iso: “Ambai. Mi sombe kala leyom, na niom uunu tiom tau. Mi kuur mar tio pepe. Iŋgi buri be aŋzem kat yom, mi aŋla kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i.” \x + \xo 18:6 \xt Ezek 33:7+; Mt 10:14+; Ŋgo 13:46; Ro 1:16\x*
\p 
\v 7 To izem zin, mi ila imbot ki Titius Yastus. Ni Yuda som. Mi iurla ki Anutu mi igabgaaba zin Yuda pa suŋŋana kizin. Mi ruumu kini igarau lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda.
\v 8 Mboroŋan mataana kana ta ikamam peeze pa lupŋana muriini tana, ni zaana Krispus. Ni ziŋan zin wal ta timbot ruumu kini na, timap tiurla ki Merere. Mi zin men som. Tomtom boozomen ki Korin ta tileŋleŋ sua na, tiurla mi tikam yok. \x + \xo 18:8 \xt Ŋgo 16:15,33; 1Kor 1:14\x*
\p 
\v 9 Mbeŋ ta na, Paulus ikeenetondo, mi ire Merere ipet kini ma iso: “Moto kom pepe, mi maane pa sua pepe. Tekteege sua ta kembena. \x + \xo 18:9 \xt Ŋgo 23:11; 1Kor 2:3\x*
\v 10 Pa nio aŋbotmbot raamu. Mi tomtom sa ko ikam malmal pu be ipasaanu na som. Pa kar ti, iŋgi nio wal tio boozomen ta timbotmbot i.” \x + \xo 18:10 \xt Mt 28:20; Yo 10:16\x*
\v 11 Tana Paulus imbot kar Korin ma irao ndaama ta mi pakaana, mi ikamam sua ki Anutu pizin.
\p 
\v 12 Indeeŋe ta Galio imborro lele pakaana biibi ki Akaia na, zin Yuda tilup lelen mi timaŋga pa Paulus. To tikami ma tila tipamenderi ila Galio mataana.
\v 13 Tila to tiso: “To ti, ni ipandelndel zin tomtom, mi iso ikam be itooro zin ma tito zaala popoŋana pa suŋŋana ta tikamam pa Anutu i. Tana ni ikamam zooroŋana pa tutu ki Rom.”
\p 
\v 14 Paulus be kwoono ikaaga pa sua. Som mi, Galio iso pizin Yuda. Iso: “Niom Yuda keleŋ. Sombe tomtom ti ikam mbulu sananŋana ŋonoono sa tabe kakami ma kamar pa i, so irao aŋleŋ yom mi itiŋan tuurpe.
\v 15 Mi iŋgi niomŋan kaparzooro pa sua mi tutu tiom Yuda men, mi tomtom zan ma koroŋ ta kembei. Tana niom ituyom kuurpe. Pa nio leleŋ be aŋtiiri sua sorok ta kembena som.” \x + \xo 18:15 \xt Yo 18:31; Ŋgo 23:29, 25:18+\x*
\v 16 To iser zin ma tipera mat.
\v 17 To iwal biibi timaŋga pizin mi tipun Sostenes pataaŋa isu sua urpeŋana muriini tana. Pa ni ta imborro lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda isu kar tana. Tikamam na, Galio mataana ila pizin risa som.
\s1 Paulus imiili mini ma ila pa kar Antiok ta Siria a
\p 
\v 18 Paulus ziŋan zin toŋmatiziŋ ki kar Korin timbot ma moloŋana ri, mana iteege naman mi izem zin. Pa isombe imiili ma ila lele pakaana ki Siria mini. Mi Prisila mi Akwila tigaabi. Tizza wooŋgo su kar Kenkrea, mi tipup Paulus ute ruunu ma isu lene. Pa ina iwe kilalan pa sua mbolŋana ta ni imbuk pa Anutu na. Mana wooŋgo ilela be ikam zin. \x + \xo 18:18 \xt Nam 6:18; Ŋgo 21:24\x*
\p 
\v 19-21 Tikwai ma tila tipet kar Epesus, to Paulus ilela lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda ma ziŋan zin Yuda tiparzorzooro pa sua. Zin Epesus kan tiso tiruuti be ziŋan timbot ma moloŋana ri. Tamen ni ipiyar. To iteege naman mi iso pizin. Iso: “Anutu itunu tau. Sombe leleene be aŋmiili ma aŋma tiom mini, nako kena.” Iso ta kembei, mi keŋ se wooŋgo mini be ila pa Sisarea. Mi Prisila ziru Akwila na, timboren Epesus. \x + \xo 18:19-21 \xt Ro 1:10; 1Kor 4:19; Ibr 6:3; Yems 4:15\x*
\v 22 Paulus ila ipet kar Sisarea, to kaŋkaŋ ma isala Yerusalem be ire lupŋana ki Krisi ma ziŋan tiso sua ri. Mana isula mini pa kar Antiok.
\s1 Paulus imaŋga pa pai kini ta iwe tel pa
\p 
\v 23 Ni imbot moloŋana ri isu Antiok, mana imaŋga mini pa pai ma iwwa pa lele pakan ki Galesia mi Pirigia, mi ipombolmbol zin wal ki lele tana ta titoto Yesu i.
\s1 Apolos ikam Anutu sua kini isu kar Epesus mi Korin
\p 
\v 24 Yuda ta, ni imar kar Epesus. Zaana Apolos, mi kar kini Aleksandria. Mi ni tomtom ŋgarŋana mi kwo suaŋana. Mi ikam kat ŋgar pa sua ki Anutu.
\v 25-26 Ni, tipaute i pa zaala ki Merere kek. Tana sua kini ta izzo pa Yesu na, indeŋdeeŋe men. Mi izzo katkat sua raama leleene, mi ikamam sua mbolŋana pizin tomtom. Tamen iute yok kamŋana ki Yoan men. Tana imaŋga be ikam sua lela lupŋana muriini kizin Yuda, mi Prisila ziru Akwila tileŋi, to tikami ma tila ruumu kizin, mi tisope i pa zaala ki Anutu bekena iute kat.
\p 
\v 27 Apolos, ni leleene be ila lele pakaana ki Akaia tomini. Mi zin toŋmatiziŋ ki kar Epesus tiso tipomboli. Tana tibeede ro ta ila kizin Akaia kan ta titoto Yesu i, mi tisotaara zin be tiur matan pini. Beso ila ipet to tikami. Apolos ila ipet Akaia na, iuulu kat zin wal ta Anutu ikampe zin ma tiurla kek na. \x + \xo 18:27 \xt 1Kor 3:6\x*
\v 28 Pa ni izzwe katkat sua ki Anutu pizin tomtom. Mi ziŋan zin Yuda tiparzorzooro ila iwal biibi matan, mi imendernder mbolŋana mi ikototo zin. Tabe ikam ma tomtom tikilaala ta kembei: Yesu, ni Mesia. \x + \xo 18:28 \xt Ŋgo 9:22\x*
\c 19
\s1 Paulus ikam Anutu sua kini isu kar Epesus
\p 
\v 1 Indeeŋe Apolos imbotmbot kar Korin na, Paulus iwwa pa karkari ta timbotmbot abal uteene na, mi ipombolmbol zin urlaŋana kan ma ila ila ma isula kar Epesus. Ila mi indeeŋe wal pakan ta titoto Yesu i,
\v 2 to iwi zin. Iso: “Parei, indeeŋe ta niom kuurla na, kakam Bubuŋana Potomŋana tomini, som som?”\x + \xo 19:2 \xt Yo 7:39; Ŋgo 2:38, 8:16, 10:44\x* Mi zin tipekel ma tiso: “E-e, niam amleŋ sua sa pa Bubuŋana Potomŋana som.”
\p 
\v 3 Paulus iso: “Ambai. Mi yok kamŋana pareiŋana ta tikam piom na?” To tiso: “Yok kamŋana ta ki Yoan na.”\x + \xo 19:3 \xt Mk 1:4; Ŋgo 1:5\x*
\p 
\v 4 Tabe Paulus iso: “Yok kamŋana ki Yoan, ina iwe kilalan pizin wal ta titooro lelen mi tizem sanaana kizin. Mi Yoan iso pizin tomtom be tiurla ki tomtom toro tabe imar pa kaimer na. Mi ina Yesu tau.”\x + \xo 19:4 \xt Mt 3:11+\x*
\v 5 Tileŋ na, tikam yok pataaŋa pa Merere Yesu zaana.
\v 6 Mi Paulus iur namaana isalakaala zin, to Bubuŋana Potomŋana imar isalakaala zin lup. To timaŋga na, tiso sua ila karkari kalŋan, mi tiwe Anutu kwoono ma tiso kalŋaana pizin tomtom.\x + \xo 19:6 \xt Ŋgo 2:4, 8:17, 10:44+\x*
\v 7 Zin tomooto tana ko kembei laamuru mi ru sa.
\p 
\v 8 Mi puulu tel, ta Paulus ziŋan zin Yuda tiparzorzooro pa Anutu peeze kini lela lupŋana muriini kizin. Ni imototo som. Kwoono imbol mi izzokatkat sua. Pa iso ikam zin ma tiurla.
\v 9 Tamen zin pakan na, ŋgar kizin imbol. Tabe tiurla som, mi tipiri sua sananŋana pa Merere zaala kini ila iwal biibi matan. To Paulus izem zin, mi ikam zin wal ta titoto Yesu i ma tila. Mi aigule ta boozomen ziŋan tiluplup zin lela ruumu biibi ki Tiranus, mi tizzo sua.\x + \xo 19:9 \xt 2Kor 6:14+\x*
\v 10 Tikamam ta kembei ma irao ndaama ru. Tabe zin Yuda mi Grik ta timbot lele pakaana biibi ki Asia na, timap tileŋ Merere sua kini.\x + \xo 19:10 \xt Kol 1:6\x*
\s1 Seba lutuunu bizin
\p 
\v 11 Anutu ipombolmbol Paulus ma itortooro mos mburanŋan ma tiwedet. Mos tana tipa ndel kat.\x + \xo 19:11 \xt Ŋgo 5:12+, 14:3; 2Kor 12:12\x*
\v 12 Ikamam ma sombe koroŋ kini riŋariŋa kembei ta kawaala kini pakanpakan na ila ise wal meteŋan, to nin ndabok. Mi zin tau bubuŋana sananŋan tiru pizin na, tiyotyooto pizin ma nin ambai.\x + \xo 19:12 \xt Mk 16:17+; Ŋgo 5:15\x*
\p 
\v 13 Zin Yuda pakan ta tizirziiri bubuŋana sananŋan na, zin timbotmbot i. Mi tiwwa ma tiso tiziiri bubuŋana sananŋan pizin tomtom pa Merere Yesu zaana tomini. Tana tizzo sorok pizin bubuŋana sananŋan ta kembei: “Yesu ta Paulus izzoyaryaara uruunu i, ta nio aŋmender se ni zaana mi aŋur sua piom be koyooto.”\x + \xo 19:13 \xt Mk 9:38\x*
\v 14 Mi Yuda ta, zaana Seba. Ni biibi ta kizin patoronŋana kan na, lutuunu bizin lamata mi ru ta tikamam ta kembei tomini.
\p 
\v 15 Tamen aigule ta na, tikam ta kembei, mi bubuŋana sananŋana ipekel kalŋan ma iso: “Yesu, nio aŋute i. Mi Paulus na, aŋleŋleŋ uruunu. Mi niom tina na, aŋkankaana piom.”\x + \xo 19:15 \xt Mk 1:34\x*
\v 16 To tomtom tau bubuŋana sananŋana izeebi na, imaŋga mi ipun zin ma ruŋgun isaana. Pa mburaana ilip kat pizin. Mi iraraaza mburu kizin ma isu lene lup. To timaŋga na tiko pa ruumu tana ma tila len.
\p 
\v 17 Zin Yuda ma zin Grik ta boozomen ta timbot kar Epesus na, tileŋ urun, to motoŋana biibi ikam zin, mi tiwidit Merere Yesu zaana ma isala ta kor a.
\v 18 Mi wal urlaŋan boozomen timar ma tizzwe mbulu kizin sananŋan ila iwal matan.
\v 19 Mi wal boozomen ta tikamam naborou na, timar raama ro kizin ta naborou kan sua izze i. To iwal biibi tirre, mi tiswiri sala you ma ikan ma imap. Beso titoombo tirobon ro kizin tana kadoono na, sorok som kat Ko irao kembei pat milmilŋan 50,000 ma iŋgi.
\v 20 Ina zaala tana ta Merere ipombol sua kini ma irak ma irao lele. Pa sua iloondo raama mburaana. Tabe zin wal ta tiurla i, timasak ma tiwe boozo.
\p 
\v 21 Uraata ti ilae, mana kaimer to Bubuŋana ipazal Paulus, mi ni ikam ŋgar be ipa ma ila pa lele pakaana ki Masedonia ma Akaia, tona imiili mini pa Yerusalem. Mi ikam ŋgar ta kembei. Iso: “Aŋla tiŋga muŋgu, mi kaimer to ko aŋla aŋre zin Rom kan tomini.”\x + \xo 19:21 \xt Ro 1:11+, 15:23\x*
\v 22 Tana iŋgo Timoti mi Erastus, gaabaŋana ru ta tiuluuli pa uraata i, be timuuŋgu ma tila Masedonia. Mi ni imbot ŋana ri isu lele pakaana ki Asia.
\s1 Malmal biibi ipet su Epesus
\p 
\v 23 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana, Merere zaala kini iwe uunu pa malmal biibi ma ipet su kar Epesus.\x + \xo 19:23 \xt 2Kor 1:8+\x*
\v 24 Tomtom ta, ni zaana Demitrius. Ni uraata kini be iurpewe zin koroŋ pa pat silba. Mi koroŋ ta, ta ni iurpewe zin na, ina urum ki merere Artemis kunun. \f + \fr 19:24 \ft Artemis, ni merere pakaamŋana kizin Grik. Mi ni moori.\f* Zin uraata kan kini timbelmbel pat kamŋana pa koroŋ ta tana.
\v 25 Tana Demitrius iboobo zin uraata kan kini ma timar, mi ziŋan tomtom pakan ta uraata kizin raraate na, tilup zin. To imaŋga na iso pizin.
\p Iso: “Ou, niom kuute, iti uraata kiti tiŋgi ta tayaryaaru pat boozo pa i.
\v 26 Mi Paulus tana, niom ituyom kere i mi keleŋi lup kek. Ni kwo mbolŋana, mi inoknok sua ta kembei: ‘Merere kunun ta tomtom tiurpe pa naman na, ina Merere ŋonoono som.’ Tana ipandelndel zin Epesus kan boozo ma titooro zin kek. Mi iŋgi be ikam Asia ka tomtom bizin ma timap i.\x + \xo 19:26 \xt Mbo 115:4; Yesa 44:10+; Ŋgo 17:29; Tur 9:20\x*
\v 27 Tana aŋso kere iti kek? Pa iŋgi be toporou sala pataŋana i. Pa to tana ko ikam ikam ma tomtom tirepiili uraata kiti. Mi tina men som. Ko ikam pataŋana pa merere kiti zaanaŋana Artemis tomini. Pa ina kola ikam ma urum kini iwe koroŋ sorok. Mi Artemis zaana ta kembena. Koozi zin iwal biibi ki Asia mi toono ta boozomen tipakuri. Tamen Paulus ko ikam ma iwe koroŋ sorok.”
\p 
\v 28 Zin tileŋ sua tana, to ipas keten ma tau timaŋga ma kalŋan izalla ma tiso: “Artemis, ni merere kiti Epesus. Ni ta zaana biibi tau!”
\p 
\v 29 Molo som na, orooro isala ma irao kar biibi. To keten malmal mi titeege lae pa Gaius ziru Aristakus. Pa ziŋan Paulus tiwwa tau. Wal ru tina, zin Masedonia kan. Karau lae pizin mi tiyaaru tataata zin ma tila lele tau iwal biibi tiluplup zin su pa i.
\v 30 Paulus, ni iso ila ipet iwal biibi matan be iso sua pizin. Tamen wal pakan ta titoto Yesu i tipeteke i.
\v 31 Mi guraaba pakan ki Paulus ta timborro lele pakaana ki Asia na, zin tomini tipeteke la pini be ila iso ruŋguunu pizin iwal biibi tana pepe.
\p 
\v 32 Mi iwal biibi ta timbotmbot na, tikamam orooro ma kalŋan izalla ta kor a. Tomtom pakan kalŋan izalla pa koroŋ ta, mi pakan tizzo len sorok pa sua toro. Pa zin boozo ta timar tilup zin na, tiute lupŋana tana ka uunu som.
\v 33 To zin Yuda timaŋga na tipusuk Alisande ma ila ta mataana a. Mi tomtom pakan tire i, to tiso ko ni ta iwe uunu pa malmal tana. To Alisande iur namaana pizin iwal biibi be lele ikam kiŋ mibe isope zin.
\v 34 Tamen zin matan ila na, tikilaali kembei ni Yuda. To tilup kwon mi kalŋan isala ta kor a. Tiso: “Artemis, ni merere kiti Epesus. Ni ta zaana biibi tau!” Tinoknok ta kembei ma irao mazwaana moloŋana ri.
\p 
\v 35-36 Tana kuskus ki Epesus imaŋga, to zin timaane mi tiŋgun talŋan pini. To ni iso: “O niom tomtom ki Epesus, toono ta boozomen tiute iti makiŋ. Iti tiŋgi ta tomborro merere zaanaŋana Artemis urum kini ramaki kunuunu ta imbot saamba, mi itop ma isu na. Tomtom sa irao izooro iti pa koroŋ taiŋgi na som. Tana kakam mbulu kankaanaŋana pepe. Kamane!
\v 37 Pa wal ta kakam zin ma timar i, zin tipasaana urum ka kosa sa som. Mi tikam sua repiiliŋana sa pa merere Artemis som.
\v 38 Sombe Demitrius mi waene bizin ta ziŋan tikamam uraata na len sua sa pa tomtom sa, na irao timbot ma ni ka aigule. Pa zin bibip ki titirtiiri sua i, ta timbotmbot i. Tana zin irao tila kizin, to ziŋan tiurpe sua.
\v 39 Mi sombe sua pakan sa ta leleyom be koso, na kuur la lupŋana ki kar namaana be titiiri mi tiurpe. Naso koto tutu kiti.
\v 40 Pa koozi iti tososor pa mbulu kek. Tere na, orooro tiŋgi ka uunu sa som. Mbulu ta koozi kakam na, sombe tiwi iti pa ka uunu, ko tepekel be parei?”
\v 41 Tana iso makiŋ, mi kaimer mana iso: “Kala leyom!” To timureege ma tila len.
\c 20
\s1 Paulus ila ire zin Masedonia kan mi zin Grik
\p 
\v 1 Orooro biibi tana imap, mana kaimer to Paulus iboobo zin wal ta titoto Yesu i ma tila tilup zin, mi isotaara zin kembei ni be izem zin. Tila mi ni ipombol zin pa sua pakan, to izem zin ma timbot, mi imaŋga ma ila pa Masedonia.
\v 2 Iwwa ma ila beso ipet lele sa mi indeeŋe wal pakan ki Krisi, to ipombol zin pa sua boozo, mana ipa mini. Iwwa ma ila mi ipet lele pakaana kizin Grik,
\v 3 to imbot pa puulu tel. To iso imaŋga mi ikam wooŋgo be ila lele pakaana ki Siria. Som mi ileŋ kembei zin Yuda timbuuru kana. To itoori mini be ipa pa lele pakaana ki Masedonia.\x + \xo 20:3 \xt 2Kor 11:26; 1Tes 2:15+\x*
\v 4 Mi wal ta ni ziŋan tila ta zan tis: Sopata ta Pirus lutuunu i, ni ki kar Berea, mi Aristakus ziru Sekundus ki kar Tesalonika, mi Gaius ki kar Derbe, mi Timoti, mi Tikikus ziru Tropimus ki Asia.
\v 5 Zin tina timuuŋgu ma tila tizza yam su kar Troas.
\v 6 Mi niam pakan na, ambot kar Pilipai pa lupŋana biibi ki narabu ta yis somŋana i. Ina imap, to amla ma amkam wooŋgo. Amkowo pa aigule lamata, mana amlela Troas. To amdeeŋe zin. Mi ambot Troas pa aigule lamata mi ru.
\s1 Paulus ipei Yutikus ma imaŋga mini
\p 
\v 7-8 Indeeŋe aigule mataana kana na, niam amlup yam pa kini kanŋana mi suŋŋana lela ruumu leleene ta imbot kor. Mi Paulus ziŋan zin tomtom tizzo pa sua ki Anutu ma ila mbeŋ lukutuunu. Pa aigule toro to pai. Mi titun lam boozomen.\x + \xo 20:7-8 \xt Yo 20:1+; 1Kor 16:2\x*
\v 9 Mi naŋgaŋ ta, ni zaana Yutikus. Imbutultul se miiri kwoono mi iŋgungun talŋaana pa sua. Paulus ziŋan zin tomtom tizzo ma tizzo be molo som na, Yutikus mata ŋenŋeene. To itur ma som mi imbot. Ta kembei men ma ikanamaala itunu risa som. Tabe imalaala to iwwa. Itop pa ruumu leleene ta kor a ta iwe tel pa i, mi isula ta toono a. Wis ma tila be naman su pini na, Yutikus ni imeete ma kup kek.
\v 10 Tamen Paulus isula toono, to isala ŋwaana mi isou i. To iso pizin. Iso: “Leleyom ipata pepe. Ni mataana iyaara mini kek.”\x + \xo 20:10 \xt 2Kin 4:32+; Ŋgo 9:40\x*
\v 11 Paulus imiili ma isala mini, to titete narabu ma tikan, mi ni izzo sua pizin ma berek su. To izem zin mi pai.\x + \xo 20:11 \xt Lu 22:19\x*
\v 12 Mi Yutikus na, tikami ma tila ruumu kini mi lelen ambai kat. Paso, ni mataana yaryaara ma imbot.
\s1 Paulus izem kar Troas mi ila kar Miletus
\p 
\v 13 Paulus iurpe zaala piam be amse wooŋgo, mi amuuŋgu ma amla kar Asos, to amsa i isu tana. Mi itunu na, ipa toono.
\v 14 Imar ma indeeŋe yam su Asos, to amkami mi amkwai ma amla mutu Mitilene.
\v 15 Amkeene ma aigule toro na, amla amdeeŋe mutu Kios. Kozeere na, amar ampet mutu Samos. Mi kozeere mini na, kaŋkaŋ ma amla amkam kar Miletus.
\v 16 Paulus ipiyar. Pa leleene be ila Yerusalem, mana lupŋana biibi ki Pentekos ipet. Tana leleene be ilela ta kar Epesus som. Pa imoto: Kokena ilela, to imbotmbot ma molo su lele pakaana ki Asia.
\s1 Paulus ipombol zin mboroŋan ki Epesus pa sua pakan
\p 
\v 17 Tana Paulus imbot kar Miletus, mi ikam sua ma ila pa lupŋana ki Krisi ta imbot kar Epesus na, be mboroŋan kizin timar.
\v 18 Timar tipet, to iso pizin. Iso: “Keleŋ. Indeeŋe aigule mataana kana ta aŋmar aŋpet lele pakaana ki Asia, mi imar imar ma indeeŋe koozi na, mbulu tio ta aŋkamam na, niom kere kek.
\v 19 Zin Yuda timbukmbuk koŋ kiizi totomen, mi tikamam pataŋana boozo pio, mi tomtom tipamiaŋ yo kat. Tamen nio aŋkototo ituŋ, mi aŋbesmbeeze pa Merere raama tiŋiizi.
\v 20 Mi niom kuute: Sua boozomen ta irao be iuulu yom na, aŋwatkaala sa piom som. Aŋzzo sua su mat keteene, mi aŋmama ruumu ma aŋzzo yom pa tomini.\x + \xo 20:20 \xt Mbo 40:10\x*
\v 21 Kwoŋ imbolmbol pizin Yuda, mi zin Grik tomini, be tizem sanaana kizin, mibe titooro ŋgar kizin ma ila ki Anutu, mi tiurla ki Merere kiti Yesu.\x + \xo 20:21 \xt Ŋgo 2:38\x*
\p 
\v 22 “Mi buri na, Bubuŋana Potomŋana imaŋga pio be aŋla Yerusalem. Mi aŋkankaana pa. Ko mbulu pareiŋana ipet pio su tana?\x + \xo 20:22 \xt Ŋgo 20:16\x*
\v 23 Nio aŋute men tau kar boozomen ta aŋlala pa i, na Bubuŋana Potomŋana izzo yo ta kembei: Ruumu sanaana, mi pataŋana boozo ta izza yo a.\x + \xo 20:23 \xt Ŋgo 9:16\x*
\v 24 Tamen nio aŋre ta kembei: Ituŋ mbotŋana tio, ina koroŋ sorok. Pa aŋkamam ŋgar men pa uraata ta Merere kiti Yesu iur mar nomoŋ i be aŋkiskis mi aŋposop kat. Uraata tana na, ta kembei: Uruunu ambaiŋana ta iso pa muŋaiŋana mi kampeŋana ki Anutu na, bela aŋso pizin tomtom mi kwoŋ imbol pa.\x + \xo 20:24 \xt Ŋgo 21:13; 2Kor 4:1; Ga 1:1; Pil 1:20; 2Tim 4:7; Tur 12:11\x*
\p 
\v 25 “Kere. Niom tiŋgi, muŋgu nio aŋbotmbot la mazwoyom mi aŋzzo yom pa peeze ki Anutu. Mi iŋgi buri na, aŋute kat tau tiom tasa ko irao ire motoŋ mini som.
\v 26 Tana koozi nio aŋso kat yom ta kembei. Sombe tomtom tiom tasa ila lene, ina uunu tio som.\x + \xo 20:26 \xt Ezek 3:17+; Ŋgo 18:6\x*
\v 27 Pa nio aŋwatkaala sua sa piom som. Ŋgar ta boozomen ki Anutu, ta aŋso yom pa ma imap lup.
\p 
\v 28 “Motoyom iŋgal ituyom, mi sipsip boozomen ki Anutu ta Bubuŋana Potomŋana iur yom be komboro zin na. Komboro kat lupŋana ki Anutu. Pa ni iŋgiimi zin pa itunu Lutuunu siŋiini.\x + \xo 20:28 \xt 1Tim 4:16; 1Pe 1:18+, 5:2+; Tur 5:9\x*
\v 29 Mi nio aŋute. Sombe aŋzem yom, inako wal pakan timar kembei ta me saŋsaŋŋan, mi tigaaba yom ma tipasaana Anutu wal kini.\x + \xo 20:29 \xt Mt 7:15; Yo 10:12; 2Pe 2:1\x*
\v 30 Mi niom ituyom tomini, tomtom tiom pakan kola timaŋga, to tipabogboogo sua ŋonoono, mi tiyaaru wal pakan ta titoto Yesu i be tito zin.\x + \xo 20:30 \xt 1Tim 1:3-19+; 1Yo 2:19\x*
\v 31 Tana kere yom pizin. Mi motoyom ŋgal ndaama tel ta itiŋan tombotmbot na. Mazwaana tana, nio aŋmaane piom som. Aŋzzopewe yom tataŋa pa mbeŋ ma aigule raama tiŋiizi.\x + \xo 20:31 \xt Mk 13:37; 1Tes 2:11\x*
\p 
\v 32 “Mi iŋgi buri aŋso aŋur yom la Anutu namaana. Tana kwoŋ imbol piom ta kembei: Motoyom iŋgal Anutu sua kini ta iso pa muŋaiŋana kini. Pa ina ko ipombol yom, mi iuulu yom be kakam matamur kini ambaiŋana ta ni imbuk sua pa be ikam pizin wal kini.\x + \xo 20:32 \xt Ŋgo 14:23; Ep 1:18; Kol 1:12; 1Pe 1:4+\x*
\v 33 Indeeŋe ta itiŋan tombotmbot na, nio motoŋ berber pa tomtom sa pat kini, som mburu kini sa be aŋkam leŋ i som.\x + \xo 20:33 \xt 1Kor 9:11+; 2Kor 2:17, 7:2; 1Tes 2:5\x*
\v 34 Niom ituyom kere kek. Koroŋ ta iuluulu yo raama zin gaabaŋoŋ ti, ina iwedet pa uraata ta ituŋ aŋkamam pa nomoŋ na.\x + \xo 20:34 \xt Ŋgo 18:3; 1Kor 4:12; 2Kor 12:14+; 1Tes 2:9\x*
\v 35 Aŋkamam ta kembei paso, aŋsombe aŋwe kin ambaiŋana piom. Pa iti sombe takam uraata ma biibi, nako lende koroŋ ma irao, mi tarao be tu'uulu zin wal ta len koroŋ somŋan i. Matanda ŋgal Merere Yesu sua kini ta iso: ‘Ŋonoono, iti sombe tikam lende koroŋ, na menmeen ti pa. Mi sombe itundu tu'uulu zin tomtom pa koroŋ kiti, nako ikam ma menmeen ti biibi kat.’”\x + \xo 20:35 \xt 2Kor 9:8; Ep 4:28; 1Tes 4:11+; 1Tim 6:18\x*
\p 
\v 36 Paulus iso sua tana ma imap to, ziŋan tilek kumbun mi tisuŋ.
\v 37 Tisuŋ makiŋ, to timaŋga mi tila tisou i, mi ziŋan titaŋ.
\v 38 Lelen isaana kat pa sua lwoono ri ta isombe zin ko tirao be tire mataana mini som. Tana titaŋ makiŋ, mi tiuri ila wooŋgo.
\c 21
\s1 Paulus ila Yerusalem
\p 
\v 1 Niam amparzem yam na, zin timbot mi niam ampet. Mi amkwai ma kaŋkaŋ ma amla pa mutu Kos. Kozeere mini na, amla mutu Rodos. To amla mi amlela Patara.
\v 2 Amlela Patara, to amdeeŋe wooŋgo toro tabe ikakat ma ila pa lele pakaana ki Ponisia. Tana amlu yam se mi amla.
\v 3 Amkowo amkowo ma amre la pa mutu Saiprus. To amzem ma imborene, mi ampa ndapet men, mi amkoŋuru toono biibi Siria. Amla na amlela kar Tiro. Pa kar tana, ta gorgori wooŋgo tana izemzem mburu su pa i.
\v 4-5 Amla amru zin wal ki kar tana ta titoto Yesu i, to niamŋan ambot pa aigule lamata mi ru. Pa amzza wooŋgo tau. Mi Merere Bubuŋana ipatooŋo zin pa mbulu tabe ipet pa Paulus i, tabe tibiigi i be imbot. Kokena isala Yerusalem. Niamŋan ambotmbot, to amzem zin mi amla. Wal boozomen ta titoto Yesu i, ziŋan waen bizin mi lutun bizin, ta timap tiur yam ma amzem kar mi ampera tai. Ampera tai na, amlek kumbuyam mi amsuŋ su peende. \x + \xo 21:4-5 \xt Ŋgo 20:36\x*
\v 6 To amparzem yam mi niam amla ma amsala wooŋgo, mi zin ra, timiili ma tila kar.
\p 
\v 7 To ampet mini, mi wooŋgo iko ma amla mi amlela kar Tolemais. Amre toŋmatiziŋ pakan, mi niamŋan ambot pa aigule ta.
\v 8 To kozeere mini na, amzem zin, mi amla ampet kar Sisarea. To amla ambot ruumu ki Pilip. Ni tomtom ki izzo uruunu ambaiŋana. Wal lamata mi ru ta muŋgu tiur zin be tiuulu zin ŋgoŋana pa uraata na, kizin ta ta tiŋgi. \x + \xo 21:8 \xt Ŋgo 6:5, 8:5\x*
\v 9 Ni lutuunu moori bizin paŋ ta tiwoolo zen. Mi zin tiwe Anutu kwoono bizin. Pa ni ipatoŋtooŋo zin pa koroŋ pakan.
\p 
\v 10 Niamŋan ambot pa aigule pakan, mana Merere kwoono ta, zaana Agabus, ni imbot Yudea mi isu.
\v 11 Imar tiam, to ikam lae pa pus ki Paulus, mi ipo itunu namaana ma kumbuunu pa, mi iso: “Bubuŋana Potomŋana iso ta kembei: Mbulu raraate men ko ipet pa pus ti katuunu. Pa zin Yuda ta timbot Yerusalem a kola tipo namaana ma kumbuunu, mi tiuri la kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i naman.” \x + \xo 21:11 \xt Ŋgo 20:23, 21:33\x*
\p 
\v 12 Amleŋ sua tiŋgi to niamŋan waeyam bizin tana leleyam be Paulus isala Yerusalem pepe. Tana amtoombo be amruuti.
\v 13 Tamen ni iso piam ma isombe: “Ah, tiŋiizi tiom tiŋgi parei? Koso kakam be kaparru kopoŋ pa pataŋana tiŋgi? Sombe tipo yo su Yerusalem, na tipo yo lak! Mi sombe tipun yo ma aŋmeete pa Merere Yesu zaana, ina ambai tomini.” \x + \xo 21:13 \xt Lu 9:51; Ŋgo 20:24\x*
\p 
\v 14 Tana amso ma som. Pa ni itunu imbol. To leyam sua sa mini som, mi amso: “Ambai, imbot la ki Merere itunu leleene tau.”
\p 
\v 15 Sua tana imap tona, amkam mburu tiam mi amsala pa Yerusalem.
\v 16 Wal pakan ki Sisarea ta titoto Yesu i, tiurur yam, mi niamŋan amap ma amla ruumu ki Nason, to ambot. Nason tana, ni tomtom ta kizin wal mataana kan ta titoto Yesu i. Mi ni tomtom ki mutu Saiprus.
\s1 Paulus ila ipet Yerusalem
\p 
\v 17 Amsala Yerusalem mi zin toŋmatiziŋ ta timbot tina tire yam, to lelen ambai kat mi timar tikam yam ma amla.
\v 18 Kozeere mini na, niamŋan Paulus amla be amre Yems. Mi amla na, zin mboroŋan kizin ta boozomen timar timbotmbot tomini.
\v 19 To Paulus ila ma ire zin, mi ipit mbol pa uraata boozomen ta Anutu ipomboli pa ma ikam la zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mazwan na.
\p 
\v 20 Tileŋ to tipakur Anutu zaana pa. To tisu mini mi tiso pa Paulus. Tiso: “Toyam, re. Zin Yuda boozo kat ta tiurla ki Yesu i. Mi zin timap timbol kat pa tutu. \x + \xo 21:20 \xt Ŋgo 15:1,5\x*
\v 21 Mi urum na, imar ma zin tileŋ kek. Pa tomtom pakan tipiŋgisŋgis sua ku ma tiso zin Yuda ta timbotmbot la zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i mazwan na, nu zzo pizin be tipizil ndemen pa tutu ki Mose mi mbulu kiti muŋguŋan, mibe tireete lutun bizin pepe. \x + \xo 21:21 \xt 1Kor 7:18+; Ga 3:10+, 5:2+, 6:15; Kol 2:16+\x*
\v 22 Tana iŋgi ko takam parei mi tupunmeete sua tana? Pa tomtom ko tileŋ urum kembei nu mar kek, to dudut ma timar mi tikam mbulu sa.
\p 
\v 23 “Tana leŋ la sua tiam ti mi kam ta kembei. Tomtom paŋ ta timbotmbot i. Zin timbuk sua pa Anutu kek.
\v 24 La kizin ma niomŋan kuurpe yom be kewe ŋgeezeŋoyom pa Anutu mataana, mi uulu zin mi giibi pat pa uten ruunu pupŋana. \f + \fr 21:24 \ft Zin Yuda tikamam mbulu ta kembei: Sombe tomtom sa imbuk sua mbolŋana pa Anutu, na ni, tipupi som ma ila ila beso sua kini iur ŋonoono, to ikam patoronŋana pa mbili pakan. Tana zin urlaŋana kan ki Yerusalem lelen be Paulus iŋgiimi zin mbili pa tomtom paŋ taiŋgi. Naso iswe kembei ni itoto men tutu.\f* Naso tomtom ta boozomen ki kar ti tire mi tiso: ‘O, to ti uruunu ta imar ma teleŋ na, ina pakaamŋana. Pa iŋgi ni itoto men tutu ki Mose.’ \x + \xo 21:24 \xt Ŋgo 18:18; 1Kor 9:20\x*
\p 
\v 25 “Mi wal urlaŋan ta Yuda somŋan i na, niam amur zaala pizin kek mi ambeede ro ila pizin, mi amso pizin be tikan kini ta tipakur zin merere pakaamŋan pa i pepe, tikan siŋ pepe, tikan buzur siŋŋana pepe, mi timolo ula ka tutu pepe.” \x + \xo 21:25 \xt Ŋgo 15:29\x*
\p 
\v 26 Tikeene ma aigule toro to, Paulus ila ikam tomtom paŋ tana, mi ziŋan tila be tiurpe zin ma tiwe ŋgeezeŋan pa Anutu mataana. Ni ila Urum Merere, to iur sua sotaaraŋana kizin ise: Ko tikam aigule piizi be tiurpe zitun ma imap, mana tikam patoronŋana ma ikot zin.
\s1 Zin Yuda titeege Paulus su Urum Merere
\p 
\v 27 Aigule lamata mi ru tana be imap. Som mi, Yuda pakan ta timar pa lele pakaana ki Asia na, tire Paulus imbotmbot Urum Merere kwoono. Tabe tila tikuru zin iwal lelen, to tila mi tikiskis lae pini.
\v 28 Mi kalŋan izalla ma tizzo: “Ou, niom tomtom ki Israel, kamar mi ku'uulu yam lak! Tomtom tau iwwa pa lele ta boozomen mi ikamam sua pizin tomtom ta munŋaana men kembei iti ramaki tutu kiti mi Urum Merere potomŋana tiŋgi na koroŋ sorok, ta itunu tis! Mi buri ŋonoono, ni ikam mbulu toro ma isala ki. Pa iyo Grik pakan ma tilela Urum Merere potomŋana ti ma tau tipasaana ma isaana kat. \x + \xo 21:28 \xt Ŋgo 6:13, 24:5+\x*
\v 29 (Zin tiso ta kembei paso, muŋgu tire Tropimus ta ki kar Epesus i ziru Paulus tiwwa pa Yerusalem. Tana tikam ŋgar sorok ma tiso ko Paulus ikami ma ziru tilela Urum Merere ka siiri.) \x + \xo 21:29 \xt Ŋgo 20:4\x*
\p 
\v 30 To zin Yerusalem kan timap ma timaŋga ma kalŋan isala. Mi tilonloondo ma timar tile urum lene, to tiyasasaara Paulus mi tiyaaru tataati ma tipera mat, mi tikotkaala kataama pataaŋa.
\v 31 Tiso tikam be tipuni ma kup. Tamen sua ikam biibi ŋonoono ta imborro zin malmal kan ki Rom i. Tiso pini ta kembei: Zin Yerusalem kan ta timap ma tikamam malmal biibi.
\v 32 Tabe tikamam, mi biibi ŋonoono tana wis ma isu raama zin malmal kan kini mi zin bibip kizin. Zin Yuda tipunun Paulus, mi tire biibi tana ziŋan zin malmal kan kini tuŋ sula, to tizemi.
\p 
\v 33 Biibi tana ila ipet kizin, tona iso ma tikiskis Paulus, mi tipo namaana pa re ru. To iwi zin. Iso: “To tiŋgi, ni asiŋ? Mi ikam so mbulu i?” \x + \xo 21:33 \xt Ŋgo 20:23, 21:11\x*
\v 34 Iwal biibi ta timbotmbot i, pakan timaŋga ma tiso pa sua uunu ta. Be pakan timaŋga, to tiso pa uunu toro. Tabe tikam ma biibi tana ipas kat sua ŋonoono sa som. Pa tiso sua ndelndelŋa, mi orooro kizin isala mete. To biibi tana iso ma tikam Paulus mi tiuri lela ruumu mbolŋana ta zin malmal kan timbotmbot pa na.
\v 35 Zin malmal kan ziŋan Paulus tipa ma tila ndeete uunu, to tikwaari. Pa iwal biibi tau tiso tikam be tiyatuti.
\v 36 Mi iwal biibi tana titoto zin ma tila, mi timap ma kalŋan izalla ma tiso: “A, ila lene. Kupuni ma imeete!” \x + \xo 21:36 \xt Lu 23:18,21; Ŋgo 22:22\x*
\s1 Paulus iso sua pizin iwal biibi
\p 
\v 37 Zin malmal kan be tikoki Paulus ma tilela ruumu kizin mbolŋana. Som mi, Paulus iwi lae pa biibi kizin. Iso: “Irao be aŋso sua pu muŋgu?” To biibi tana iso: “Wai! Mi nu zzo Grik kalŋan?
\v 38 Pa nio aŋkam ŋgar pa tomtom ki Aikuptu ta uriizi ŋonoono ipese wal zigzikŋan munŋaana paŋ (4,000) mi iyaaru zin ma tila pa lele bilimŋana be tikam malmal na. Tabe aŋso ko nu tau.”
\p 
\v 39 To Paulus iso: “E-e, nio ti Yuda. Aŋmar pa Tasus, ta kar zaanaŋana ki Silisia na. Parei? Irao yok pio mi aŋso sua pizin iwal tiŋgi muŋgu?”
\p 
\v 40 Biibi tana iyok pini, to Paulus imender sala ndeete, mi iur namaana be iso sua. Iwal biibi tire i, to lele ikam kiŋ. Mi ni iso sua pizin ila zitun kalŋan ta Iburu i. Iso:
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 “O atoŋan ma tamaŋan, kuŋgun talŋoyom. Pa nio leleŋ be aŋso uunu tio ma keleŋ kat.”
\p 
\v 2 Tileŋi iso Iburu kalŋan, to lele ikam kiŋ.
\p 
\v 3 Mi ni iso: “Nio ti Yuda. Tipeebe yo su kar Tasus ta ki Silisia na. Tamen nio musaari mi tikam yo ma aŋmar aŋbot kar tiŋgi. Mi aŋkan su tiŋgi ma aŋwe kaibiŋoŋ. Mi tutu ki tumbundu bizin na, Gamalielbi ipaute yo pa ma imap. Mi nio aŋkam kinkiini be aŋto kat mbulu ki Anutu kembei ta koozi niom ta boozomen kakamam i. \x + \xo 22:3 \xt Ŋgo 5:34+; Ga 1:13+; Pil 3:5+\x*
\v 4 Zin wal ta titoto zaala popoŋana tiŋgi na, muŋgu aŋbelmbel matan seezeŋana. Mi tomtom kizin pakan na, aŋpun zin ma timetmeete. Mi pakan na, aŋyaryaaru zin ma aŋla aŋurur zin lela ruumu sanaana. Zin tomooto, mi moori tomini. \x + \xo 22:4 \xt Ŋgo 8:3; 1Kor 15:9; 1Tim 1:13\x*
\v 5 Biibi kizin patoronŋana kan ziŋan zin peeze kan ta boozomen tiute mbulu tio. Zin tirao be tipombol sua tio ti. Pa zin ta tiyok mi tikam ro imar tio, to aŋkam ma aŋso aŋla kizin toŋmatiziŋ kiti ta timbot kar Damaskus na. Pa aŋso aŋla be aŋkam zin tomtom ta titoto zaala tiŋgi na, mi aŋyo zin ma timar Yerusalem be tiseeze matan.
\s1 Paulus iso pa mazwaana ta itooro leleene
\r (Ŋgo 9:1-18, 26:9-18)
\p 
\v 6 “Tana aŋmaŋga pa pai, mi aŋwwa ma aŋla aŋgarau kar Damaskus. Zoŋ mataana ikam kembei aigule palakuutu mi molo som na, azuŋka imbot saamba mi ikelyaara su ma iliu yo ma kembei ta lele ikimit i.
\v 7 To aŋtop su toono mi aŋleŋ sua ta isu pio ma iso ta kembei. Iso: ‘Saul, Saul, parei ta nu noknok motoŋ seezeŋana?’
\v 8 Mi aŋpekel ma aŋso: ‘O Biibi, nu asiŋ?’ To pekelŋana imar. Iso: ‘Iŋgi nio Yesu ki Nasaret ta nu seseeze motoŋ na.’ \x + \xo 22:8 \xt 1Kor 15:8; Ga 1:15+\x*
\v 9 Sua tana, waeŋ bizin ta niamŋan amla na, tileŋ som. Tigeede men, pa tire azuŋka men.
\p 
\v 10 “To aŋwi. Aŋso: ‘Biibi, kenako aŋkam so?’ Mi Merere ipekel kalŋoŋ ma iso: ‘Maŋga mi lela Damaskus, to leŋ sua pa uraata boozomen ta leleŋ iur pa kek be kam i.’
\v 11 Waeŋ bizin timar na, titeege nomoŋ mi amlela kar Damaskus. Pa azuŋka mburaana mete. Tabe ikam yo ma aŋrao aŋre lele som.
\p 
\v 12 “Kar tana, tomtom ta imbotmbot, zaana Ananias. Ni iur kat leleene pa Anutu, mi itoto tutu. Mi Yuda ta boozomen ki lele tana matan ise kini.
\v 13 Ni ikoŋuru yo ma imar, to imender lae zilŋoŋ uunu mi iso: ‘O tiziŋ Saul, motom kam pak lak!” To karau men mi motoŋ iyaara mi aŋre i.
\v 14 To imaŋga mi iso: ‘Anutu ta ki tumbundu bizin, ta itunu ipeikatu be ipaute u pa ŋgar kini mi leleene, mibe re kat Tomtom Ndeeŋeŋana, \f + \fr 22:14 \ft Tomtom Ndeeŋeŋana na, Yesu tau.\f* mi leŋ sua ila ni itunu kwoono. \x + \xo 22:14 \xt Ga 1:12+; Ep 3:2+\x*
\v 15 Mi nu be pombol sua kini ila wal ta boozomen matan, mi so zin pa koroŋ ta nu leŋ mi re kat pa motom na. \x + \xo 22:15 \xt Ŋgo 23:11, 26:16\x*
\v 16 Tana maŋga ta buri, kam yok, mi suŋ pa ni zaana be ipusu pa sanaana ku ma ila ne.’ \x + \xo 22:16 \xt Ro 10:13; 1Pe 3:21\x*
\p 
\v 17 “Uraata tana imap, tona aŋmiili ma aŋla Yerusalem mini. Aŋbot mi aigule ta na, aŋlela Urum Merere be aŋsuŋ. Aŋzuŋzuŋ na,
\v 18 aŋkeenetondo mi Merere iso sua pio. Iso: ‘Loŋa mi zem Yerusalem ta buri. Pa wal tina, re beso swe uruŋ pizin, na irao tileŋu som.’
\p 
\v 19 “Nio aŋsu to aŋso: ‘Biibi, wal tiŋgi, zin tiute: Muŋgu nio aŋlonloondo pa lupŋana murin ta boozomen, mi aŋtekteege zaaba pizin wal ta tiurla ku na, mi aŋyyo zin ma aŋurur zin lela ruumu sanaana.
\v 20 Mi indeeŋe ta tipun Setepan ma imeete, mi siŋiini ireere paso, izzwe nu urum na, nio aŋbotmbot mi aŋyok pa mbulu tana. Mi aŋmendernder raama mburu kizin wal ta tipununi.’ \x + \xo 22:20 \xt Ŋgo 7:58, 8:1\x*
\p 
\v 21 “Tamen Merere iso pio. Iso: ‘Maŋga. Pa iŋgi aŋgo u be la pa lele ta molo kat. Nu ko la kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i.’” \x + \xo 22:21 \xt Ŋgo 9:15, 26:17+; 1Tim 2:7\x*
\s1 Paulus iso ni ki Rom
\p 
\v 22 Iwal biibi tiŋgun talŋan ma ilala, beso tileŋ Paulus iso ta kembei, to timaŋga na kalŋan isala. Tiso: “A, to na, kala kupuni ma imeete lak! Imbot ko ikam so?” \x + \xo 22:22 \xt Ŋgo 21:36\x*
\v 23 Mi tiboboobo ma tiwirri mburu kizin, mi titiyaryaara toono zalla kor. \f + \fr 22:23 \ft Zin Yuda, sombe tileŋ sua ta ambai som kat, to tikam mbulu ta kembei.\f*
\v 24 Tana biibi ŋonoono kizin malmal kan iso ma tikam Paulus mi tilela ruumu mbolŋana ta zin malmal kan timbotmbot pa na. Mi iso pizin be tilela to tibalis Paulus pa wooro matanmatanŋana, mi tiwisese i bekena ipeeze kat uunu tau zin iwal biibi kalŋan izalla pini pa i.
\p 
\v 25 Tana tilela mi tipo i be tibalisi. Som mi, Paulus iso la pa biibi tau imborro zin malmal kan i. Iso: “Parei? Tomtom ta ni ki Rom na, sombe kendeeŋe le uunu sa som, ko irao kabalisi sorok?” \x + \xo 22:25 \xt Ŋgo 16:37\x*
\v 26 Biibi ileŋ sua tana, to ila mi iso pa biibi ŋonoono kizin malmal kan. Iso: “Iŋgi ko parei? Pa tomtom taiŋgi, ni ki Rom.”
\p 
\v 27 Tabe biibi ŋonoono tana ila ma iwi Paulus. Iso: “Ai, so kat. Nu tina, tomtom ki Rom?” Paulus iso: “E. Nio tomtom ki Rom.”
\v 28 Biibi tana imaŋga to iso: “Nio ti aŋgiibi pat zaanaŋana be aŋwe tomtom ki Rom.” To Paulus iso: “Mi nio na, aŋgiimi som. Pa tamaŋ ta ipeebe yo na, ni ki Rom.”
\p 
\v 29 Tabe zin ta timar mi timendernder be tiwi Paulus i, timilmiili ma timar tila len. Mi biibi ŋonoono tana ire ma imoto kana. Pa Paulus, ni ki Rom. Mi ni iso pizin ma tipo i sorok.
\s1 Paulus imender su zin bibip keren uunu
\p 
\v 30 Kozeere mini na, biibi ŋonoono kizin malmal kan iso ipas kat sua uunu. Parei ta zin Yuda tiŋgal sua pa Paulus? Tana iboobo zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan ziŋan zin peeze kan ta boozomen ma tilup zin. To ila ma iputke Paulus, mi ikami ma ila ipamenderi su keren uunu.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 Paulus ire la pizin peeze kan mi iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, ta muŋgu mi imar indeeŋe koozi na, nio aŋyamaana ituŋ kembei aŋkam ŋoobo mbulu sa pa Anutu mataana som.”\x + \xo 23:1 \xt Ŋgo 24:16; 1Kor 4:4; 2Kor 1:12; 2Tim 1:3\x*
\v 2 Biibi kizin patoronŋana kan, zaana Ananias, ileŋ sua tana, to iso la pizin wal ta timender kolouŋana i ma tipeeze lae pa Paulus kwoono.\x + \xo 23:2 \xt Yo 18:22+\x*
\v 3 To Paulus iso pini. Iso: “Nu tina, Anutu ko ipunu tomini. Nu kembei didi ta ibuuzu kek, mi timusmus pen kokouŋana ma ise sorok. Pa mbulu ku mat kana men ta iŋgeeze. Mi lelem na som. Nu mbulem su tina be tiiri yo pa tutu tau. Tamen itum molo tutu kek. Pa so pizin ma tipun yo sorok.”\x + \xo 23:3 \xt Lo 25:1+; Mt 23:27+\x*
\p 
\v 4 Zin wal tau timender kolouŋana pa Paulus na, timaŋga to tiso: “Wai, kwom pasom biibi kizin patoronŋana kan paso? Ni sa Anutu tomtom kini na!”
\p 
\v 5 Paulus ipekel ma iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, nio aŋkilaala kembei ni biibi kizin patoronŋana kan na som. Mibe aŋkilaali, so aŋso sua ta kembei som. Pa sua ki Merere imbot pataaŋa kek ta kembei:
\q1 Tomtom peeze kana ta imborro yom na, piri sua sananŋana sa pini pepe.”\x + \xo 23:5 \xt Kam 22:28\x*
\b
\p 
\v 6 Paulus, ni iute zin peeze kan tana lup kek. Zin timbot la uunu ru. Pakan na, zin sadusi. Mi pakan na, zin tutu kan. Tabe Paulus kalŋaana mi iso la pizin. Iso: “Niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, keleŋ. Nio ti tutu koŋ tau. Mi tamaŋ ma anaŋ tomini na, zin tutu kan. Nio aŋurur motoŋ pa maŋgaŋana kizin meeteŋan, tanata tipamender yo pa i.”\x + \xo 23:6 \xt Ŋgo 24:21, 26:5+; Pil 3:5\x*
\p 
\v 7-8 Paulus ipiri sua ti, to zin peeze kan tana timureege pataaŋa. Pa zin sadusi na, tiurla ta kembei: Sombe tomtom sa imeete, na irao imaŋga mini som. Mi tiso aŋela sa imbot som, bubuŋana sa som. Mi zin tau tutu kan i na, urlaŋana kizin toro. Pa tiso zin meeteŋan kola timaŋga mini, aŋela timbotmbot, mi bubuŋan tomini timbotmbot.\x + \xo 23:7-8 \xt Lu 20:27\x*
\v 9 Tana kalŋan izalla kat ma tiparzorzooro ma ila to, wal ŋgarŋan pakan tau tutu kan i kalŋan sala ma tiso: “Ai, niam amtiiri na, tomtom ti, ni ikam mbulu sananŋana sa som. Ko bubuŋana sa, som aŋela sa iso sua sa pini ma iŋgi.”\x + \xo 23:9 \xt Ŋgo 25:25\x*
\p 
\v 10 Biibi ŋonoono kizin malmal kan ire ma ambai som. Pa sua iporou mete. Tabe iso pizin malmal kan kini ma tila tikoki Paulus la zin peeze kan tina naman, mi tikami ma tilela ruumu kizin mbolŋana. Pa imoto: Kokena tiyatut Paulus.
\p 
\v 11 Mbeŋ na, Merere ipet ki Paulus mi ipomboli. Iso: “Paulus, moto pepe. Mender mbolŋana. Pa uruŋ ta swe su Yerusalem, inako swe su Rom tomini.”\x + \xo 23:11 \xt Ŋgo 18:9, 27:23+\x*
\s1 Zin Yuda timbuuru Paulus kana
\p 
\v 12 Kozeere mini na, Yuda pakan tila tilup zin be timbuuru pa Paulus. To timbuk sua mbolŋana kat pa Merere zaana be tikan kini som, tiwin yok som ma irao tipun Paulus ma imeete.
\v 13 Zin wal ta timbuuru pini na, zin kembei tomtooru mi kwoono sa.
\v 14 To timaŋga na tila tire zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan mi zin mboroŋan. Tila to tiso: “Ou, niam taiŋgi ambuk sua mbolŋana kat pa Merere zaana kek ta kembei: Koozi mi ila na, kwoyam ko iteege kini sa som ma irao ampun Paulus ma imeete.
\v 15 Tana niomŋan zin peeze kan pakan kala ki biibi ŋonoono kizin malmal kan, mi koso pini ta kembei. Koso: ‘Kam Paulus mi kusu. Pa niam amsombe ampas kat sua kini uunu.’ Niom koso kakam ta kembei, na niam ti ko amzaŋzaaŋi. Beso isu to loŋa ampuni. Mi irao imar ipet lele tiŋgi na som.”
\p 
\v 16 Tamen Paulus woono, ni talŋaana ikam kiizi kizin kek. Tana ila ma ilela ruumu mbolŋana kizin malmal kan mi isotaara Paulus.
\v 17 To Paulus iboobo la pa biibi tau imborro zin malmal kan na ma imar, mi iso pini. Iso: “Kam naŋgaŋ ti ma ila ki biibi tiom ŋonoono. Pa ni le sua ri be iso pini.”
\v 18 Ikami ma tila ki biibi ŋonoono tana, to iso: “Paulus ta imbotmbot ruumu sanaana na, iso pio, tabe aŋkam naŋgaŋ tiŋgi ma niamru amar. Pa ni le sua ri be iso pu.”
\p 
\v 19 Biibi ŋonoono ila to iteege naŋgaŋ tina namaana mi ziru men tilae. To iwi i. Iso: “Parei, nu lem so sua i, ta mar pio pa i?”
\p 
\v 20 To naŋgaŋ tina iso: “Zin Yuda tilup lelen ma iwe tamen, mi tiso tipun Paulus ma imeete. Iŋgi ko molo som to sua ikamu be berek, to kam Paulus ma kusula pa lupŋana biibi kizin peeze kan be tipas kat sua kini uunu. Mi ina sua ŋonoono som.
\v 21 Tana leŋ zin pepe. Pa zin kembei tomtooru mi kwoono sa, ta ko tizaŋzaaŋi su zaala. Mi timbuk sua mbolŋana kat pa Merere zaana kek be tikan kini som, tiwin yok som ma irao tipun Paulus ma imeete. Iŋga tiurur matan ta timbotmbot a. Beso yok pizin, to tikam mbulu tana.”
\p 
\v 22 Biibi ŋonoono ileŋ sua tana to kwoono imbol pini. Iso: “Sua ta so yo i. Kozo so pa tomtom toro sa pepe. Kokena wal pakan tiute kembei nu ta mar mi so yo na.” Iso ta kembei, mi iso pini ma ila lene.
\s1 Tikam Paulus ma isula Sisarea
\p 
\v 23 Biibi ŋonoono tana imaŋga to iboobo bibip ru kizin malmal kan ma timar, mi iso pizin. Iso: “Kala ma kere zin malmal kan tomto laamuru (200), mi zin hos kan tomto tel laamuru (70), mi izi kan tomto laamuru (200) be tisula pa Sisarea pa mbeŋ ta koozi.
\v 24 Mi kere hos pakan pa Paulus tomini. Kozo komboro kati ma imbot ambai men ma irao ila ipet ki gabana kiti Peliks.”
\v 25 Mi ibeede sua sotaaraŋana ta kembei. Iso:
\p 
\v 26 “O biibi tio ŋonoono, gabana Peliks. Nio Klodias Lisius aŋkam aigule tio ima ku.
\p 
\v 27 “Tomtom taiŋgi, zin Yuda tikisi mi tipasaani mabe imeete. Tamen nio aŋmar raama zin malmal kan tio, to amkamke i pizin. Pa aŋleŋ kembei ni tomtom ki Rom.\x + \xo 23:27 \xt Ŋgo 21:30+, 22:25+\x*
\v 28 Mi nio leleŋ be aŋpas kat uunu kini. Parei ta zin tikamam sua boozo pini. Tana aŋkami ma ila pa lupŋana biibi kizin peeze kan.
\v 29 Tamen aŋla ma aŋdeeŋe kembei, ni le uunu sa tabe ilela ruumu sanaana, som imeete pa i som. Zin kwon ikanani sorok. Mi ina tiparzorzooro pa zitun tutu kizin tau.\x + \xo 23:29 \xt Lu 23:14+; Ŋgo 18:14+, 25:25, 26:31\x*
\v 30 Mi aŋleŋ kembei wal pakan tikamam to tiŋgi kuziini, tana loŋa men mi aŋseri ma ima ku na. Mi aŋur sua pizin Yuda be tima ku, to ziŋan tikam sua su ta kerem uunu na.”
\p 
\v 31 Tana zin malmal kan tito sua ki biibi kizin, mi ziŋan Paulus timaŋga pa mbeŋ. Tila tila ma ta Antipatris a.
\v 32 Tikeene ma aigule toro to, zin tau tipa toono i timiili mini ma tila ruumu kizin mbolŋana ta Yerusalem a. Mi zin tau tise hos i, ziŋan Paulus tila.
\v 33 Tikami ma tila tipet kar Sisarea, to tisara ro ila ki gabana, mi tiur Paulus ila kini.
\v 34 Gabana ipaata ro makiŋ, to iwi Paulus: Ni imar pa lele pakaana swoi? Mi Paulus iso ni imar pa Silisia.
\v 35 To gabana iso pini. Iso: “Ambai. Mbot mi zin tau tiŋgal sua pu na timar muŋgu, toinabe aŋtiiri sua tiom.” To gabana iso pizin menderŋan be tikam Paulus ma tila ruumu biibi ta muŋgu Erot ipo na, mi timboro i isu tana.
\c 24
\s1 Paulus ziŋan zin Yuda timender su Peliks kereene uunu
\p 
\v 1 Aigule lamata ilae to, Ananias ta biibi kizin patoronŋana kan na, ziŋan zin mboroŋan pakan, mi tomtom ŋgarŋana ta ni zaana Tertulus, tisula pa Sisarea be ziŋan Paulus timender la gabana kereene uunu, mibe tiŋgal sua pini. Tertulus tana, ni iute kat tutu ki Rom. Mi uraata kini be iuluulu zin tomtom pa sua kizin.
\v 2-3 Tana tiboobo Paulus ma ilela kizin, to Tertulus imaŋga mi iso sua kini. Iso:
\p “O biibi tiam Peliks, niam tiŋgi leleyam ambai kat pu. Pa mazwaana ta kamam peeze pa lele tiŋgi na, niam ambot ambai men. Mi koroŋ boozomen ta muŋgu isaana, ta iŋgi nu pazalzal mabe ambai lup. Tana lele pakaana ti, niam amap ma leleyam pu. Pa nu uluulu yam pa koroŋ matakiŋa boozo.
\v 4 Tamen ko irao aŋyaaru sua ma molo som. Tana aŋwi u be leŋ sua tiam katŋana ri ti.
\p 
\v 5 “To ti, niam amre i na, mbulu kini ambai som kat. Ni kembei ta mete sananŋana i. Pa ipeyei malmal boozomen ma tiwedet la zin Yuda mazwan irao toono ta boozomen. Mi zin wal ta titoto Yesu ki Nasaret mi tipabogboogo sua ki Merere na, ni ta imuŋmuuŋgu pizin. \x + \xo 24:5 \xt Ŋgo 16:20, 17:6, 21:28\x*
\v 6 Mi itoombo be ipasaana Urum Merere tomini. Iŋgi tabe amkisi. [Mi niam amso ituyam ampamenderi mi amtiiri mbulu kini pa tutu tiam.
\v 7 Tamen biibi kizin malmal kan Lisius imar, to imaŋga piam mi isani la nomoyam mi ikami ma ila.
\v 8 To Lisius iur sua piam be amar ku i.] Tana nu itum wi i, to re kat uunu ta niam ampamenderi pa i. Pa sua tiam ti, pakaamŋana som. Ŋonoono men.”
\p 
\v 9 Tertulus iso sua tana makiŋ to, zin Yuda pakan timaŋga mi tipombol sua ta ni iŋgal pa Paulus na.
\s1 Paulus iso sua kini
\p 
\v 10 To Peliks iyembut sua kizin, mi iur namaana pa Paulus be iso sua. Paulus imaŋga to iso:
\p “O gabana Peliks, nio aŋute: Ndaama ndaama ta nu mbel sua urpeŋana pa lele ti kek. Tana nio leleŋ ambai mi aŋso sua tio ti ima ku.
\v 11 Sua tiŋgi ipata pu som. Nu rao ute karau men. Re. Uriizi, aigule laamuru mi ru men ta ila kek na, nio aŋsala pa Yerusalem be aŋsuŋ.
\v 12 Mi niamru tomtom sa amparzooro lela Urum Merere som, mi aŋkuru tomtom lelen lela lupŋana muriini kizin, som kar leleene ma iŋgi som tomini. Zin wal ta tiŋgal sua pio i, tomtom kizin sa ire yo aŋkam mbulu ta kembei na som.
\v 13 Tana sua kizin, ina zin tiso. Mi sokorei toro tabe ipombol? Som.
\p 
\v 14 “Tamen sua kizin koroŋŋana ri, ta aŋyok pa. Zaala ki Krisi ta zin tizzo be pakaamŋana, ina nio aŋtoto. Mi ina nio aŋzuŋzuŋ men pa Anutu ta muŋgu tumbuyam bizin tizuŋzuŋ pini na. Mi sua ta Merere kwoono bizin tibeede na, ramaki koroŋ ta munŋaana men ta indeeŋe tutu ki Mose, ina nio aŋurla men i. \x + \xo 24:14 \xt Ŋgo 26:22, 28:23; 2Tim 1:3\x*
\v 15 Nio niamŋan zin wal tiŋgi amur motoyam pa koroŋ tamen tau. Pa amso Anutu, ni kola ipei zin tomtom ma timaŋga mini pa naala be tikam kadoono kizin. Wal ndeeŋeŋan, mi wal sananŋan tomini. \x + \xo 24:15 \xt Yo 5:28+; Ŋgo 23:6, 26:6+; 2Kor 5:10\x*
\v 16 Tanata nio gorgori aŋkamam kinkiini be leleŋ iŋgeeze, mibe aŋkam kat mbulu pa Anutu mataana mi tomtom matan tomini. \x + \xo 24:16 \xt Ŋgo 23:1; 1Kor 4:4; 2Kor 1:12; 2Tim 1:3\x*
\p 
\v 17 “Nio aŋzem Yerusalem mi aŋbot lele pakaana toro pa ndaama boozo kek. Tanata iŋgi aŋla mini be aŋur nomoŋ ila pizin wal tio, mibe aŋkam patoronŋana pakan tomini. \x + \xo 24:17 \xt Ro 15:25+; 2Kor 8:1+; Ga 2:10\x*
\v 18 Mi nio aŋto mbulu mi aŋurpe ituŋ ma aŋgeeze muŋgu, mana aŋlela Urum Merere lene be aŋkam uraata tiŋgi. Mi nio ituŋ tamen kat ta aŋlela. Tomtom toro sa igaaba yo som. Mi aŋkam orooro sa som, kosa sa kembena som. \x + \xo 24:18 \xt Ŋgo 21:26+\x*
\v 19 Aŋkamam uraata tiŋgi ma aŋbotmbot, mi Yuda pakan ta timar pa lele pakaana ki Asia na, tindeeŋe yo. Ina zin ta tiwe uunu pa sua tiŋgi. Mi wal tina, sombe len sua pio, na ambai be zitun timar mi tiso kat sua kizin isu kerem uunu ma leŋ.
\v 20 Mi sombe som, na zin wal tiŋgi ta niamŋan amendernder i, zitun irao tiso kat uunu tio ma teleŋ. Nio aŋkam ŋoobo so mbulu i? Pa uriizi, indeeŋe ta tipamender yo ila zin peeze kan matan ta Yerusalem na, zin timbotmbot.
\v 21 Nio aŋso ko tikamam pa sua lwoono ta, ta kalŋoŋ biibi pa ma tileŋ. Sua ta kembei: ‘Koozi, nio sua indeeŋe yo mi aŋmar amender su kereyom uunu ti paso, aŋurla kembei zin meeteŋan kola timaŋga mini.’” \x + \xo 24:21 \xt Ŋgo 23:6+\x*
\p 
\v 22 Peliks, ni ikankaana pa zaala ki Krisi som. Tana ileŋ, to ipeteke sua ma imbot mi iso: “Kezem su tana. Tombot ma biibi kizin malmal kan Lisius itunu imar, toinabe aŋtiiri sua tiom.”
\v 23 To iur sua pa biibi kizin malmal kan be iur Paulus lela ruumu sanaana mi mataana pini. Mi irao ikam pataŋana biibi pini pepe. Sombe wal kini tila ma tiso tire i pa kopoono ma koroŋ, na irao iyok pizin. \x + \xo 24:23 \xt Ŋgo 27:3, 28:16\x*
\s1 Paulus izzo pa zaala tabe tuurla ki Yesu Krisi i
\p 
\v 24 Aigule pakan ilae mi kaimer mana, Peliks ziru waene Drusila timar. Drusila, ni Yuda nan. Tana Peliks iso la pa Paulus ma imar, to Paulus izzo sua pa zaala tabe tuurla ki Yesu Krisi i, mi ni ileŋleŋ.
\v 25 Beso Paulus kwoono iyabakes lae pa mbulu ndeeŋeŋana, mi mbulu ki tagabiizi itundu, mi kadoono urŋana tabe ipet pa mbeŋ kaimer i, na sua iŋgal Peliks ma imoto. To iyembut sua. Iso: “Ambai. Irao ta ti. La muŋgu. Mi ko aŋre lwoono toro sa, to aŋboobu mini.”
\v 26 Mi Peliks, ni iurur mataana pa Paulus. Pa iso ko ni ikam le pat sa. Tiŋgi tabe iboboobi ma ilala kini be ziru tizzo sua.
\p 
\v 27 Ndaama ru ilae, tona Peliks isu mi Porsius Pestus ikam muriini. Mi Peliks, ni leleene be zin Yuda lelen pini. Tana izem Paulus ma imbotmbot lela ruumu sanaana, mi ni imap pa uraata.
\c 25
\s1 Paulus imender su Pestus kereene uunu
\p 
\v 1 Pestus imar ipet Sisarea be iteege uraata kini. Mi aigule tel ilae mana, izem Sisarea mi isala pa Yerusalem.
\v 2 Isala to, zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan ziŋan zin bibip pakan kizin Yuda tila kini mi tiŋgal sua pa Paulus.
\v 3 Tila to loŋa mi tikuru leleene bekena ilae kizin, mibe ikam Paulus ma isala pa Yerusalem. Pa timbuk Paulus ka kiizi kek be tipunke i su zaala lwoono.
\v 4 Tamen Pestus iso pizin. Iso: “Paulus, ni imbotmbot ruumu sanaana leleene ta Sisarea a. Mi nio iŋgi be aŋsula i.
\v 5 Sombe ni ikam ŋoobo mbulu sa, na zin bibip tiom pakan timar ma niamŋan amsula, tona tiso ka sua isu tiŋga.”
\p 
\v 6 Pestus ziŋan timbotmbot ma aigule ko laamuru sa ma iŋgi, mana isula Sisarea. Kozeere mini na, ila ma mbuleene su sua urpeŋana muriini, mi iso be tikam Paulus ma imar.
\v 7 Paulus imar ipet to, zin Yuda tau timbot Yerusalem mi timar i, tila ma tiliu i. Mi tigiibi sua boozo pini. Tiso ni ikam mbulu ta sananŋana kat. Tamen sua kizin tana, ka pombolŋana sa som.
\p 
\v 8 To Paulus ipekel kalŋan ma iso: “Nio ti aŋkam ŋoobo mbulu sa pa Yuda tutu kizin som, Urum Merere som, mi Kaisa som tomini.” \x + \xo 25:8 \xt Ŋgo 24:12, 28:17\x*
\p 
\v 9 Mi Pestus, ni ikamam be Yuda lelen pini. Tana imaŋga to iwi ten lae pa Paulus. Iso: “Parei, ko irao se Yerusalem, mi mender su kereŋ uunu ta tiŋga?”
\v 10 Paulus iso: “Wai, mi lele tabe aŋla ma aŋkam sua isu pa i, ina ruumu ki Kaisa ta iŋgi aŋbotmbot pa i. Som nu re kembei nio aŋkam ŋoobo mbulu sa pizin Yuda? Lak, ina tina, nu itum ute kek.
\v 11 Mi sombe aŋkam mbulu sa ta sananŋana kat ma irao be aŋmeete pa i, na tipun yo lak. Irao aŋko pa kadoono tio na som. Tamen sombe zin Yuda ti, sua kizin ŋonoono som, na tomtom sa irao iur yo sorok la naman na som. Ambai. Nio aŋso aŋre Kaisa itunu mi ni itiiri sua tio.” \x + \xo 25:11 \xt Ŋgo 28:19\x*
\p 
\v 12 Pestus ileŋ Paulus iso ta kembei, to ila ma ziŋan zin ŋgarŋan kini pakan tizzo sua. Mana iso pa Paulus. Iso: “Nu sombe la mi re Kaisa tau. Tana ko la ma re i.”
\s1 Pestus isope king Agripa
\p 
\v 13 Timbot ma king Agripa ziru lunuri Benis timar tipet Sisarea be tilou Pestus.
\v 14 Ziŋan timbot pa aigule pakan, tana Pestus izzo pa sua ta tikam pa Paulus na, ma king Agripa ileŋleŋ. Iso: “Tomtom ta, tau Peliks iuri lela ruumu sanaana ma imbotmbot, mi ni imap pa uraata.
\v 15 Mi indeeŋe ta nio aŋsala Yerusalem na, zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan ziŋan zin mboroŋan kizin Yuda tiŋgal sua pini, mi timaŋmaŋ yo be aŋur kadoono pini.
\v 16 Mi nio aŋpekel sua kizin ta kembei. Aŋso: ‘Keleŋ. Niam Rom koyam na, mbulu tiam ta kembei som. Sombe wal pakan tiŋgal sua pa tomtom sa, na irao amuri sorok ila naman na som. Bela ni ziŋan tiso sua pa, mi itunu iso uunu kini muŋgu.’
\p 
\v 17 “Tana nio aŋmiili ma aŋsula mini na, niamŋan mi amar. Be ampet Sisarea na, aŋnaunau som. Ambot ma aigule toro, to mbuleŋ su sua urpeŋana muriini, mi aŋboobo Paulus ma ilela pataaŋa.
\v 18 Beso ka koi bizin timaŋga be tiŋgal sua pini na, aŋso ko tiso pa mbulu pakan ta sananŋan ŋonoono. Som mi som.
\v 19 Tiso kat sua sa som. Ziŋan Paulus tiparzorzooro pa urlaŋana kizin, mi tizzo pa tomtom ta, zaana Yesu. Zin na, tiso ni imeete kek. Mi Paulus izzo be ni imbot mata yaryaara men i.
\v 20 Tana aŋleŋ na, ŋgar tio sa ambai som. Irao be aŋkam kat ŋgar pa sua ti be aŋurpe na som. Tana aŋwi i beso parei na, isala Yerusalem, tonabe imender mini pa sua tiŋgi.
\v 21 Tamen ni ipemet sua, mi kwoono imbol be Kaisa itunu itiiri sua kini. Tana aŋur sua pizin menderŋan be timboro i ma irao aŋuri la ki Kaisa.”
\p 
\v 22 To Agripa iso pa Pestus. Iso: “Mi nio ti leleŋ be ituŋ aŋleŋi tomini.”
\p Tabe Pestus iso: “Ambai. Gaaga to leŋi.”
\s1 Tipamender Paulus su king Agripa kereene uunu
\p 
\v 23 Aigule toro na, king Agripa ziru Benis timar ma ziŋan zin wal zanŋan ki kar tana mi zin bibip kizin malmal kan tilela ruumu leleene biibi ta zin bibip tiluplup zin pa i. Mi tikam mbulu boozo be tipakur Agripa ziru Benis. To Pestus iso, mi tikam Paulus ma imar ilela. \x + \xo 25:23 \xt Lu 21:12+\x*
\v 24 Pestus imaŋga to iso: “O king Agripa mi niom tau kamar ma itiŋan tombot tiŋgi, koozi kere mar pa tomtom tiŋgis. Tomtom tiŋgi, ta zin Yuda ta boozomen timaŋmaŋ yo pini isu Yerusalem mi isu tiŋgi tomini. Timap ma kalŋan sala ma tisombe to ti, ni imbot pepe. Imeete ma ila ne. \x + \xo 25:24 \xt Yo 19:5+\x*
\v 25 Mi nio na, aŋre kembei ni ikam mbulu sananŋana sa tabe imeete pa i som. Tamen ni itunu isombe ila ki Kaisa be ni itiiri sua kini. Tanata aŋsombe aŋuri ma ila Rom.
\v 26 Tamen aŋdeeŋe sua ŋonoono sa pa tomtom ti bekena aŋbeede se ro ma ila ki Kaisa i na som. Tanata aŋkami ma imar imender su kereyom uunu bekena kitiiri uunu kini. Pa aŋso nu, king Agripa, niomŋan zin wal tiŋgi koso ka sua, tonabe aŋbeede uunu kini ise ro.
\v 27 Pa sombe sua izal som, mi tuur sorok tomtom sa ma ila ki Kaisa, ina mbulu kankaanaŋana. Bela tebeede kat uunu kini ise ro mi ni ipa raama, to ambai.”
\c 26
\s1 Paulus iso sua su king Agripa kereene uunu
\r (Ŋgo 9:1-18, 22:3-16)
\p 
\v 1 Tana king Agripa iso pa Paulus. Iso: “Iŋgi be nu kadoono so sua ku.”
\p Tana Paulus iur namaana, mi imaŋga to iso uunu kini:
\v 2 “O king Agripa, koozi nio leleŋ ambai. Pa aŋmar ma aŋmender su nu itum kerem uunu be aŋpekel sua boozomen ta zin Yuda tiŋgal pio na.
\v 3 Pa mbulu tiam Yuda mi sua pakan ta amparzorzooro pa i, na nu ute lup kek. Tana aŋsombe aŋwi u ten. Ko irao be ŋgun talŋom mi leŋ mar pa kalŋoŋ? Pa sua tio ko moloŋana ri. Kokena nim gesges ma iŋgi.
\p 
\v 4 “Mbulu tio tau naŋgaŋŋoŋ mi imar indeeŋe koozi na, zin Yuda ta boozomen tiute lup kek. Mbulu tio ta aŋkam su ituŋ kar tio, mi kaimer aŋkam su Yerusalem na, ike pizin som.
\v 5 Tana indeeŋe ta taŋga mi tamar i na, zin tiute yo lup kek. Mi sombe lelen pa, na irao tipombol sua tio ti. Indeeŋe ta nio naŋgaŋŋoŋ mi imar na, aŋgabgaaba zin wal tutu kan ta timbol kat pa tutu mi suŋŋana tiam i. Amlip pizin Yuda pakan. \x + \xo 26:5 \xt Ŋgo 23:6; Pil 3:5\x*
\v 6 Mi koozi na, tipamender yo su tiŋgi paso, nio aŋurur motoŋ pa koroŋ ambaiŋana ta Anutu imbuk sua pa ila ki tumbuyam bizin tau. \x + \xo 26:6 \xt Ŋgo 23:6, 28:20; Ro 15:8; 2Kor 1:20\x*
\v 7 Sua mbukŋana tana, ta niam Yuda uunu laamuru mi ru amurur motoyam pa, mi amzuŋzuŋ Anutu pa ikot mbeŋ ma aigule be iur ŋonoono. O king, nio aŋurur motoŋ pa koroŋ ambaiŋana tana, tanata ikam ma zin Yuda tiŋgal sua pio.
\v 8 Lak, parei ta niom tina kere kembei Anutu ni irao be ipei zin meeteŋan ma timaŋga mini som?
\p 
\v 9 “Muŋgu, nio tomini aŋkamam kaisiigi be aŋpasaana Yesu ki Nasaret uruunu. Mi aŋdemeere aŋso ko mbulu ta aŋkamam, ina ambai. \x + \xo 26:9 \xt Ŋgo 8:3; 1Kor 15:9; Ga 1:13; 1Tim 1:13\x*
\v 10 Mbulu tana, aŋkam su Yerusalem muŋgu. Zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan ta tiyok pio, tanata aŋzebzeebe Anutu wal kini potomŋan boozomen lela ruumu sanaana. Mi nio ti aŋyok be tipun zin ma timetmeete tomini.
\v 11 Tana aŋwwa pa lupŋana murin ta boozomen, mi aŋkamam pataŋana pizin wal tau tiurla ki Yesu i, mi aŋseseeze matan. Mi aŋmaŋmaŋ zin be tipasaana Yesu zaana. Aŋmalmal pizin biibi kat. Tana aŋwwa pa karkari ta lele molo na tomini be aŋru zin.
\p 
\v 12 “Uunu tina ta aigule ta, nio aŋpa ma aŋso aŋla ta kar Damaskus a. Uraata ta aŋso aŋkam su tana, nio zoŋ pa. Pa zin bibip kizin patoronŋana kan tipombol sua ma tiyok pio tabe aŋla.
\v 13 O king, nio aŋwwa pa zaala lwoono ma zoŋ mataana ikam kembei palakuutu. Mi molo som na, aŋre azuŋka ta imbot saamba mi ikelyaara su ma iliu yo raama waeŋ bizin ma kembei ta lele ikimit i. Mi mburaana biibi kat. Ilip pa zoŋ mataana.
\v 14 Ikam ma niam iwal mi amtoptop su toono. To aŋleŋ sua ta iso la Iburu kalŋan ma isombe: ‘Saul, Saul, parei ta noknok motoŋ seezeŋana? Zooroŋana ta kamam, ina ipata pu. Pa ina kembei urur itum ila zaaba kwoono.’
\v 15 Tabe aŋwi: ‘Biibi, ina nu asiŋ?’
\p “To Merere iso: ‘Mi iŋgi nio Yesu ta nu seseeze motoŋ na.
\v 16 Burup ma maŋga mender. Iŋgi aŋpet ku be aŋuru ma kam uraata pio. Koroŋ ta buri rre i, ramaki koroŋ pakan tabe aŋswe ma ku pa kaimer i, nu ko so zin tomtom pa, bekena pombol sua tio.
\v 17 Nio ko aŋkamke u pa wal ku, mi zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i tomini. Mi iŋgi aŋgo u be la kizin tomtom mi pei ŋgar kizin
\v 18 ma matan ikam pak. Nu be tooro zin ma tipizil ndemen pa zugut mi tipet mat, mi kam zin ma tizem Sadan mburaana, mi tiur lelen ila ki Anutu. Naso aŋreege sanaana kizin, mi timar tigaaba zin wal tau tiurla tio mi tiwe wal potomŋan ta ki Anutu i.’ \x + \xo 26:18 \xt Yo 8:12; Ŋgo 2:38; Ep 1:18, 5:8; Kol 1:13; 1Pe 2:9\x*
\p 
\v 19 “O king Agripa, re. Koroŋ ta kar saamba iswe mar tio na, irao aŋzooro na som.
\v 20 Tana mataana mi aŋzzoyaryaara ka sua isu Damaskus. To isu Yerusalem, to isu lele ta boozomen ki Yudea. Mana ila kizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i tomini. Nio aŋzzo pizin tomtom be tipizil ndemen pa mbulu kizin sananŋana, mi tiur lelen ila ki Anutu, mi tikam kat mbulu. Naso tiswe kembei titooro kat lelen. \x + \xo 26:20 \xt Mt 3:8; Ŋgo 9:20+\x*
\v 21 Iŋgi uunu tiŋgi ta zin Yuda tikiskis yo la Urum Merere kwoono, mi tiso tikam be tipun yo.
\v 22 Tamen nio aŋre ulaaŋa biibi kat imarmar pa Anutu, ma irao indeeŋe koozi. Tanata aŋmendernder mbolŋana, mi aŋpombolmbol sua ki Yesu ila zin wal ta boozomen matan. Zin zanŋan, mi zin sorrokŋan tomini. Mi sua ta aŋkamam i na, popoŋana som. Ina aŋto men Mose mi Anutu kwoono bizin kalŋan. Pa sua ta muŋgu tiso, ta iŋgi iur ŋonoono kek. \x + \xo 26:22 \xt Lu 24:27,44+; Yo 5:46; Ŋgo 10:43; Ro 3:21\x*
\v 23 Pa tiso Mesia, ni ko ire yoyouŋana, mi iwe mataana pa maŋgaŋana kizin wal meeteŋan. Mi ni ko isoyaara sua tabe ikam zin Yuda mi zin wal ta Yuda somŋan i ma timbot mat.” \x + \xo 26:23 \xt 1Kor 15:20,23; Kol 1:18\x*
\p 
\v 24 Paulus iso sua kini ma indeeŋe tiŋgi, to Pestus imaŋga mi kalŋaana biibi ma iso: “Ai Paulus, nu kankaanaŋom kat. Kam ŋgar biibi mete ta ipatalli u na!” \x + \xo 26:24 \xt Yo 10:20; 1Kor 2:14; 2Kor 5:13\x*
\p 
\v 25 To Paulus iso: “O biibi tio Pestus, nio ti kankaanaŋoŋ som. Nio aŋzzo sua ŋonoono men raama ŋgar tau.
\v 26 Tanata aŋmototo som, mi aŋzzo katkat sua. Sua ti, king Agripa ni iute ma imap. Pa mbulu ta boozomen ti, sa ike som.
\v 27 Lak, king Agripa, nio aŋwi u. Nu urla Anutu kwoono bizin kalŋan, som som? E, nio aŋute. Nu urla.”
\p 
\v 28 Tabe king Agripa iso: “Wai Paulus, iŋgi so tooro yo karau men be aŋwe Krisi lene ta buri?”
\p 
\v 29 Paulus iso: “O, so buri, buri. Miso kaimer, kaimer. Mi nio aŋsuŋ Anutu pu mi zin wal ta tileŋleŋ sua i tomini be kuurla mi kewe kembei ta nio i. Mi tamen nio leleŋ be tipo nomoyom ma kumbuyom ma tiur yom lela ruumu sanaana kembei ta tikam pio na pepe.”
\p 
\v 30 To king ziŋan gabana Pestus mi Benis mi zin tau timbotmbot na burup ma timaŋga.
\v 31 Tiyooto ma tila na, tiparzzo pizin. Tiso: “To ti, ni ikam ŋoobo mbulu sa tabe ilela ruumu sanaana, som imeete pa i na som.” \x + \xo 26:31 \xt Lu 23:14+; Ŋgo 23:9, 25:25\x*
\p 
\v 32 To Agripa isu na iso pa Pestus. Iso: “Tomtom ti, ni iso ila ki Kaisa ma ni itiiri sua kini. Pepe so tezemi, mi iyooto ma ila ne.” \x + \xo 26:32 \xt Ŋgo 25:11\x*
\c 27
\s1 Paulus ikam wooŋgo be ila pa Rom
\p 
\v 1 Zin timbuk sua be niam amkwai ma amla Itali. Tana tikam Paulus ziŋan wal pakan ta timbot lela ruumu sanaana na, ma tiur zin la Yulius namaana. Yulius, ni biibi kizin malmal kan. Imborro zin malmal kan tomto lamata ki Kaisa itunu tau.
\v 2 Amla ma wooŋgo ta ki kar Adramitium imar. Mi iŋgi iso imiili mini ma ila pa kar pakan ki Asia. Tana amse mi le isala ma amla. Mi tomtom ta ki kar Tesalonika ta imbot la lele pakaana ki Masedonia na, igaaba yam ma niamŋan amla. Zaana Aristakus.
\p 
\v 3 Aigule toro na, amlela kar Sidon. Mi Yulius leleene ambai pa Paulus, tana izemi ma ila kizin guraaba kini bekena tire i pa kopoono ma koroŋ. \x + \xo 27:3 \xt Ŋgo 24:23, 28:16\x*
\p 
\v 4 To amzem Sidon mi ampet mini na, amko pa mutu Saiprus leleene ta miiri ilonloondo pa som i. Pa amseebe miiri biibi tau.
\v 5 Amko ma ampa ndapet men, mi amla Silisia ma Pampilia. To amyembut ma amlae na, amlela kar Mira ta imbot lele pakaana ki Lisia a.
\v 6 Amlela tina, mi biibi kizin malmal kan ire wooŋgo kizin Aleksandria ta isombe ila Itali. To iso piam ma ŋes lae wooŋgo tina.
\p 
\v 7 Wooŋgo iko riŋariŋa. Tabe amko amko ma molo mana, amso amlela Nidus. Som mi, miiri biibi kat ma amselaala na amrao som. Tana amko pa toono uunu ma amla, to ambeleu pa mutu Krit zuruunu ta iyaara ma ipera. Tipaata be Salmone. To mutu tana ipakaala miiri.
\v 8 Amkosal toono, mi amkowo riŋariŋa, mi amla amla ma sor lela lele ta tipaata be ‘Maata Ambaiŋana’ na. Imbot kolouŋana pa kar Lasea.
\p 
\v 9 Indeeŋe tana, ambel koŋana kek. Mi iŋgi be lele isaana ma irao kwaiŋana mini som. Pa aigule biibi ki Sanaana Urpeŋana ila ne kek. \f + \fr 27:9 \ft Aigule tana, ina suŋŋana biibi kizin Yuda. Iwedet pa Septemba. \f* Tana Paulus imaŋga mi isope zin. Iso:
\v 10 “Keleŋ. Nio aŋre tai iŋgi be isaana i. Sombe tepet mini, inako tendeeŋe pataŋana biibi. Kokena wooŋgo mi mburu kiti ila ne, mi iti itundu tomini.”
\v 11 Tamen biibi kizin malmal kan, ni iurla sua ki Paulus som. Mi ikanan la ki ni ta itekteege peeze ki wooŋgo i mi wooŋgo katuunu.
\v 12 Timbot ma som mi miiri swoono ipet. Tabe lele ta wooŋgo ipot pa i, ambai som. To iwal biibi lelen be tila pa maata toro ta imbot kar Peniks a. Pa lele tina na, miiri pe som. Irao timbot pa ma miiri isu. Maata tina, ina imbot ta mutu Krit a. Imbot la ki pakaana ta zoŋ isula na.
\s1 Miiri biibi ma lele isaana
\p 
\v 13 Miiri riŋariŋa ta ipa ki meleeba mi ise. Tabe zin wooŋgo kan tindemeere ma tiso ko ambai pizin. Tana tiyaaru pat ise, to amko ma amsal men pa mutu Krit.
\v 14 Molo som na, miiri biibi imaŋga. Ipa ki ndalea mi ipet ma indeeŋe yam.
\v 15 Miiri imar ma amtoombo be amkunyaara duubu. Tamen som. To amsur men.
\v 16 Amla ma amko pa mutu musaana ta zaana Kauda na ndemeene, to ipakaala miiri. Tana amso amyaaru wooŋgo musaari ta timbit la wooŋgo mbuleene i ma ise. Mi miiri mburaana men. Tabe ambel uraata pa wooŋgo musaari tana.
\v 17 To amyaaru ma ise, mi zin pakan tipo wooŋgo biibi pa re pakan bekena tipombol. Mi timoto: Kokena duubu ipiri wooŋgo ma isala magat biibi ta igarau Aprika na. Tabe tipun le, mi wooŋgo itunu rukruk ma ilala.
\v 18 Lele isaana kat ma tau ruŋguyam isaana lup. Tabe kozeere to tipiri mburu pakan ila ne.
\v 19 Aigule iwe tel pa na, tikam mburu wooŋgo kana pakan, mi tipiri sula len tai.
\v 20 Mi lele na, isaana kat. Aigule boozo, zoŋ iyaara risa som. Mi pitik ta kembena. Sa imbot mat som. Tabe ikam ma amso ko irao ambot na som. Amla leyam.
\p 
\v 21 Zin tomtom tikan kini som, mi timbot sorok men pa mazwaana molo kek. Tana Paulus imaŋga na iso pizin. Iso: “Kozobe niom kakan mar tio ma tezem Krit pepe, so iti irao tendeeŋe pataŋana tiŋgi som, mi mburu kiti sa irao ila ne som.
\v 22 Mi toŋgo. Nio aŋso aŋpombol yom ta kembei. Komoto pepe. Pa iti ti, tasa ko irao ila ne na som. Wooŋgo men ta ko ila ne.
\v 23 Pa mbeŋi, Anutu tio ta aŋbesmbeeze pini i, iŋgo aŋela kini ta ma imar imbot su ta zilŋoŋ uunu mi iso pio. \x + \xo 27:23 \xt Ŋgo 23:11; Ro 1:9\x*
\v 24 Iso: ‘Paulus, moto pepe. Nu kola la ma pet ki Kaisa. Pa Anutu leleene iur ta kembei. Mi Anutu, ni muŋaiŋana katuunu. Tana ni ko mataana pa wal boozomen ta niomŋan kamar i ma irao tasa ila lene som.’”
\v 25 To Paulus iseeŋge sua kini mini ma iso: “Tana nio aŋso piom: Komoto pepe. Pa nio aŋurla ki Anutu. Koroŋ ta ni iso yo pa, inako iur ŋonoono.
\v 26 Tamen iti ti kola tala ma tosoolo sala mutu sa.”
\s1 Wooŋgo isaana
\p 
\v 27 Amzurzur ma aigule laamuru mi paŋ imap, to amla tai pakaana ta tipaata be Adria na. Indeeŋe mbeŋ lukutuunu na, zin wooŋgo kan tiso ko amgarau toono kek.
\v 28 Beso tikin yok na, tire kembei mozo biibi imbot. Timbot rimen mi tikin mini, to tire ise.
\v 29 Tabe timoto ma tiso ko wooŋgo ila ma ituti sala patmbu sa ma iŋgi. Tona tila wooŋgo mbuleene, mi tipusuk pat bibip paŋ ta re ikan ma tuŋ i, ma tisula tai bekena tibiigi wooŋgo. Mi tizuŋzuŋ be loŋa mi berek.
\v 30 Mi zin tau tikamam uraata pa wooŋgo i, na tila ta wooŋgo zuruunu, to tiputke wooŋgo musaari mi tipeleŋ ma isula be tiko ma tila len. Pa matan iŋgal zitun men. Tana tipakaam zin tau tise wooŋgo na, mi tiso tila be tipusuk pat pakan isula ki muŋga bekena tibiigi wooŋgo.
\v 31 Tamen Paulus imaŋga to iso pizin malmal kan ziŋan biibi kizin. Iso: “Kere zin wal ta tikamam uraata pa wooŋgo ti. Sombe tizem wooŋgo mi tila len, tona niom ko irao kombot ambai som.”
\v 32 Tabe zin malmal kan timaŋga na tiyembut wooro pa wooŋgo musaari, mi itop ma ila ne.
\p 
\v 33 Berek zen mi Paulus iso pizin ta boozomen be tikan kini. Iso: “Ou, niom ti kakan koyom kini. Pa iti toporou sala pataŋana ti ma kombotmbot ki kopoyom men ma iŋgi aigule iwe laamuru mi paŋ i.
\v 34 Tana aŋsombe kakan koyom kini sa ta buri be ipombol yom. Pa iti ta boozomen ko tombot ambai. Tomtom tiom sa ko irao uteene ruunu sa ipas ma ila lene na som.” \x + \xo 27:34 \xt Lu 12:7\x*
\v 35 Iso pizin makiŋ to, ikam narabu mi isuŋ pa Anutu ila iwal biibi matan. To ite kana ma ikan. \x + \xo 27:35 \xt Mt 15:36; 1Tim 4:4+\x*
\v 36 Tanata ipombol ŋgar kizin pa, to lelen ambai mi timap ma tikan kini.
\v 37 Niam tomto laamuru tomto tel lamoro mata mi ta (276), ta amse wooŋgo i.
\v 38 Tikan irao zitun lelen ma kopon bokbok, to tila ma tipiri mburu pakan ila ne tai, bekena wooŋgo ipot ma ise ŋana.
\p 
\v 39 Berek su na, matan lae toono uunu. Tamen tikilaala lele som. Mi tire lele lumbuunuŋana tau, to matan ito ma ila na, tire la pa maaŋga. Tana tiso tikam wooŋgo ma tilela.
\v 40 Timaŋga na tiyembut re pa zin pat ta tibiigi wooŋgo pa i ma titoptop sula len. Mi tiyembutmbut lae pa re ta timbit peeze pa i ma putput. To tiyaaru le ma isala. Pa tiso tilela pa toono uunu.
\v 41 Tamen wooŋgo iko ma ila, mi wooŋgo ndomoono isoolo sala magat. Mi mbuleene na iwwa. Tabe duubu ipun ipun ma imapaala la ki mbuleene. \x + \xo 27:41 \xt 2Kor 11:25\x*
\p 
\v 42 To zin malmal kan timaŋga na, tiso tipun zin tomtom ta ruumu sanaana kan i. Kokena tiyaago ma tila, to tiko ma tila len.
\v 43 Mi biibi kizin malmal kan na, leleene be tipun Paulus ma imeete pepe. Tana ipeteke zin ma tikam mbulu tina som. Mi iso pizin be zin tau tiute yaagoŋana na, loŋa tilu zin sula mi tiyaago ma tila toono uunu.
\v 44 Mi wal biibi na, zin be tire len ke pakanpakan tau duubu ikiili pa wooŋgo i, tona tizze mi tiyaago raama ma tilela toono uunu. Amkam ta kembei, tabe niam ta boozomen mi amla amsala toono ma ambot ambai.
\c 28
\s1 Amla amse mutu Malta
\p 
\v 1 Amlela toono uunu, tona amleŋ kembei mutu tiŋgi zaana Malta.
\v 2 Zin tomtom tau timbot mutu tiŋgi, kampeŋana kizin ilip pa wal pakan. Timar mi tire yam, to tindou you ma ilo yam. Pa yaŋ tomini ma lele ilomo.
\v 3 Paulus ila iyo ke ma iliigi, mi ikam ma imar, mi iur sala you mataana be ikut. Molo som na, mooto sananŋana pus ma ipet pa ke liigiŋana, mi ila ma iŋakiskis lae pa Paulus namaana.
\v 4 Zin mutu tana tire mooto imbotmbot la Paulus namaana, to tiparso pizin ma tiso: “Wai, to ti ko ipun tomtom sa ma imeete som? Ŋonoono, miiri ma duubu na, ni iko pa. Mi merere kiti ta ipokotkot mbulu i na, \f + \fr 28:4 \ft Wal taiŋgi, zin Kristen som. Merere ta tiso pa na, ina Merere Anutu som. Ina zin zitun merere kizin.\f* irao ileeli na som.”
\v 5 Tamen Paulus itirke mooto tana isala le you ma you ikani, mi kosa sa ipet pini som.\x + \xo 28:5 \xt Mk 16:18; Lu 10:19\x*
\v 6 Ikam ma zin tomtom tiurur matan pini. Pa tiso ko izarzar ma iŋgi, som itop su ma imeete. Tamen kosa sa ipet pini som. To tisu na titooro ŋgar kizin ma tiso: “Wai, to tiŋgi ko merere sa.”\x + \xo 28:6 \xt Ŋgo 14:11\x*
\p 
\v 7 Biibi ki mutu tana, ni zaana Publius. Mi lele kini igarau. Imar ma ire yam, to ikam yam ma amla ambot ruumu kini pa aigule tel.
\v 8 Publius tamaana, ni ibayyou ma kopo suruunu ramaki siŋ. Tabe ikenne men ta muriini. Tana Paulus ila to ilela ma ire i. Mi imaŋga to iur namaana isala ŋwaana, mi isuŋ pa Merere, to niini ndabok.\x + \xo 28:8 \xt Mk 16:18; Ŋgo 3:2+; Ŋgo 9:34, 14:8+; Yems 5:14+\x*
\v 9 Zin mutu kan tire mbulu tana, to tila tiyo zin meteŋan ta boozomen ma timar. Mi Paulus isuŋ pizin ma nin ndabok lup mi tilala.
\v 10 Tabe koroŋ ta boozomen tau tipakur yam pa men. Beso amparaŋraŋ koroŋ tiam be ampet na, zin timar ma tiuulu yam pa koroŋ boozomen ta leleyam pa i.
\s1 Amla ampet Rom
\p 
\v 11 Indeeŋe ta miiri biibi mi imar na, wooŋgo ta kizin Aleksandria imbot su mutu tana. Wooŋgo ndomoono na, merere boogo ru kunun imbot la. Zan Kasto mi Poluks. Tana niam ambot pa puulu tel ma miiri imap, mana kaimer to, amkam wooŋgo tana ma amla.
\v 12 Amla amla ma amlela Sirakus, to ambot pa aigule tel.
\v 13 To amzem kar tina, mi amko mini ma amla amlela Regium. Amkeene ma aigule toro na, miiri ipa ki meleebe mi ise. Aigule ru ta amkowo amkowo ma amla ampet kar Puteoli.
\v 14 Amlela tina, to amdeeŋe toŋmatiziŋ pakan ta ki Krisi i. To tikam yam ma amla, mi niamŋan ambot pa aigule lamata mi ru. Mana amaŋga mini pa pai be amla Rom.
\p 
\v 15 Mi waeyam bizin ta timbot Rom a tileŋ uruyam kek. Tana tomtom kizin pakan tizem kar, mi tipa ma timar tau nol muriini ki kar Apius na. Mi pakan timar pa kar toro ta ruumu tel kizin leembe timbotmbot pa na, mi tizza yam su tana. Amar mi Paulus ire zin, to ipakur Merere pa kampeŋana kini. Pa kembei mbulu tana ipomboli.
\v 16 Amla ampet kar biibi Rom na, tiyok pa Paulus be itutamen ila imbot ndel. Ziru menderŋana tamen be mataana pini.\x + \xo 28:16 \xt Ŋgo 24:23, 27:3\x*
\s1 Paulus ikam uruunu ambaiŋana isu kar biibi Rom
\p 
\v 17 Aigule tel ilae mana, Paulus iso la pizin bibip kizin Yuda be timar. Timar ma tilup zin, to ni iso pizin. Iso: “O niom toŋmatiziŋ tio, keleŋ. Nio ti, aŋzooro zin wal kiti pa kosa sa som, mi aŋzooro mbulu sa ta ki tumbundu bizin na som. Tamen titeege yo sorok isu Yerusalem, mi tiur yo la zin Rom naman.\x + \xo 28:17 \xt Ŋgo 21:33\x*
\v 18 Mi zin Rom titiiri yo ma som, to tisombe tizem yo ma aŋla leŋ. Pa tire yo na, kembei aŋkam ŋoobo mbulu sa tabe aŋmeete pa i som.\x + \xo 28:18 \xt Ŋgo 26:31+\x*
\v 19 Tamen zin Yuda tinoknok sua ŋgalŋana pio, tabe leŋ zaala sa som. To aŋso: ‘Kena nio aŋso aŋla aŋre Kaisa itunu be itiiri sua tio.’ Mi nio ituŋ na, leleŋ be aŋgal sua sa pa wal tio som.
\v 20 Iŋgi uunu tiŋgi ta aŋboobo yom ma kamar, bekena aŋre yom mi aŋso sua ma keleŋ. Pa koroŋ ta iti Israel boozomen tuurur matanda pa i, ta nio aŋurla tomini. Nio, tipo nomoŋ mi tiur yo lela ruumu sanaana pa uunu ta tiŋgi.”\x + \xo 28:20 \xt Ŋgo 2:31+, 26:6+; Ro 15:8; 2Tim 2:8+\x*
\p 
\v 21 To zin tiso: “Ambai. Mi zin Yudea kan tibeede sua sotaaraŋana sa pu ma imar piam som. Mi tomtom sa imbot Yudea mi imar be iŋgal sua pu i som.
\v 22 Mi iŋgi itum mar na ambai. Pa amso amleŋ kat sua ku. Pa niam amute men ta kembei: Lele ta munŋaana men kan tomtom bizin tiwirri sua sananŋana pa lupŋana tiom ta tiŋgi.”\x + \xo 28:22 \xt Ŋgo 24:5; 1Pe 2:12, 4:14\x*
\p 
\v 23 To tiur len aigule toro tabe ziŋan tilup zin mini. Aigule tana, zoŋ ise na, tomtom boozomen timeke ma timar, to tila ruumu tau Paulus imbotmbot pa i. Mi ni ipaute zin pa sua, mi ilala leleene pa ma tileŋleŋ ma ila mbeŋ. Izzo zin pa peeze ki Anutu, mi izzo zin pa tutu tau imar pa Mose mi Anutu kwoono bizin na. Iso ikam be ipatooŋo Yesu pizin, mibe ikam zin ma tiurla.\x + \xo 28:23 \xt Lu 24:27+\x*
\v 24 Tomtom pakan tileŋ sua kini ma iŋgal zin, to tiurla. Mi pakan na, tiurla som.
\v 25 Zitun timaŋga na tiparzorzooro pa sua ma burupburup be tiyooto. To sua kaimer kana ta Paulus ipemet pizin mi timureege i, na iso ta kembei. Iso: “O, sua ta Bubuŋana Potomŋana ipazal Anutu kwoono Yesaya pa mi iso pa tumbundu bizin, ta iŋgi indeeŋe kat yom. Pa iso ta kembei. Iso:
\q1 
\v 26 La kizin wal tiŋgi mi so zin. So:
\q1 Niom ti ko kuurur talŋoyom ma keleŋleŋ sua. Mi ko kakam ŋgar pa ka uunu som.
\q1 Ko kerre ki motoyom. Tamen ŋgar tiom ko ipet som.
\q1 
\v 27 Pa wal ti, ŋgar kizin imbol kat.
\q1 Zitun tizeeze talŋan mi tipumun matan.
\q1 Pa lelen be tikilaala som,
\q1 mi lelen be matan ire mi talŋan ileŋ som.
\q1 Pepe so ŋgar kizin ipet,
\q1 mi titooro lelen,
\q1 mi timar tio be aŋurpe zin.’\x + \xo 28:27 \xt Yesa 6:9+; Mt 13:13+; Ro 11:18\x*
\p 
\v 28 “Tana nio leleŋ be niom kuute kat ta kembei: Zaala tau Anutu ikamkewe zin tomtom pa i, na uruunu ila pizin wal ta Yuda somŋan i kek. Mi zin ko tileŋ la.”\x + \xo 28:28 \xt Mbo 67:2; Lu 3:6; Ŋgo 13:46+; Ro 11:11\x*
\m [
\v 29 Paulus iso makiŋ, mi zin Yuda tiyotyooto na, tiparzorzooro pa sua mi tilala.]
\p 
\v 30 Mi ndaama ru kat, ta Paulus imbotmbot ruumu tau itunu iŋgiimi be imbotmbot pa, mi irre wal boozomen ta timarmar kini na.
\v 31 Ni imototo som. Izzokatkat sua pa Anutu peeze kini, mi ikamam sua pizin tomtom pa Merere Yesu Krisi. Mi tomtom sa ipeteke i som.\x + \xo 28:31 \xt Ep 6:19\x* 
